{
	//==============================================================================================
	//==== F I S H M O N G E R =====================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Gifttastes.Love": "Holy carp! Thank you for this ex-squid-sit gift!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Gifttastes.Like": "Fin-tastic.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Gifttastes.Dislike": "What a load of pollocks!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Gifttastes.Hate": "Alright...this is so bad I can't even think of a proper pun anymore...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Gifttastes.Neutral": "That seems a bit fishy to me...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Aye, be sure to wash yer hands afterwards. The stuff in there can get pretty sticky sometimes...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Yer think yer real slick, huh? I'm gonna show ye a real boulder...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Um...nice flowers ye got there.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "...need me one of those if I ever find someone...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Ah...maybe another day, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Aye...I wonder if you could use that rain to naturally dye your pets...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "...turns out my ferrets go nuts in that rain, huh.$5",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Scurvy tends to go wild during this rain... so I got her a little leash so she can feel important when going out with the others.#$b#Hm? Oh, she is the one holding the leash actually. Likes to wiggle it around and stuff, heh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Oh? You're giving this to me?#$b#Thank you! It has such a nice aroma, I'll cherish every drop, heh! $1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.PinkMermaidScale": "Is that...?$7#$b#...a mermaid scale! It has such a nice color...the pink reminds me of the color of salt emmer.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.SunsetMermaidScale": "Is that...?$7#$b#...a mermaid scale! It has such a nice color...it's vivid colors remind me of the late evenings at the island when the sun is setting.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.MossyMermaidScale": "Is that...?$7#$b#...a mermaid scale! It has such a nice color...lush green like the islands foliage.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.SummerMermaidScale": "Is that...?$7#$b#...a mermaid scale! It has such a nice color...it makes me think of the evenings when you sit outside the docks drinking iced tea in the sweltering summer heat.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.CharcoalMermaidScale": "Is that...?$7#$b#...a mermaid scale! It has such a nice color...dark like charcoal, it almost feels warm to the touch.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.FrostMermaidScale": "Is that...?$7#$b#...a mermaid scale! It has such a nice color...is it me or does it give a cooling sensation?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.BloodstainedRoseTea": "Holy Carp! I was actually getting quite parched from all the fishing, thanks a bunch.#$b#A great strong flavor with a vivid color, ex-squid-sit!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.SunsetRoseTea": "Holy Carp! I was actually getting quite parched from all the fishing, thanks a bunch.#$b#A warm tingle with an intense flowery flavor, ex-squid-sit!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.LoversStar": "...that name...? What an intriguing thing!#$b#Thanks a bunch for this fin-tastic gift.",
	
	// MOVIE REACTIONS 
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Spring0.Before": "Hm, I can get the message behind this. Sometimes it's nice to satisfy your inner child.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Spring0.During": "I can't help but to root for him...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Spring0.After": "I can't believe I got this invested in this after all. Ah, I think I got something in my eye.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Spring1.Before": "It's admirable to always want to learn more about nature and the world around you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Spring1.During": "So fascinating...I normally mainly think about aquatic life but...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Spring1.After": "This really broadened my horizon. Maybe I'll ask Gunther later about some books related to the topic.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Summer0.Before": "Oh, it's so interesting that the game got a movie. I wonder how it'll be.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Summer0.During": "%Constance seems to be really invested in the fighting scenes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Summer0.After": "Now, that is what I call a nice gun fight, heh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Summer1.Before": "Hm, you're into this? Okay, I'll try and see how it is.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Summer1.During": "...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Summer1.After": "...I'll be honest. This wasn't really my thing, I'm sure kids will really like it tho.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Fall0.Before": "Oh...now this is an interesting one.$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Fall0.During": "%Constance seems to be too invested, almost forgetting to eat her snack.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Fall0.After": "Wow...I could watch this again.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Fall1.Before": "The plot reminds me a bit of my youth, heh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Fall1.During": "What a twist...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Fall1.After": "Not a movie I'd usually pick, but I am glad you asked me to go, heh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Winter0.Before": "Mhm...I'm not really the sappy type of person.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Winter0.During": "...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Winter0.After": "...yeah, as I thought. Wasn't really my thing. Thanks for the invite tho.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Winter1.Before": "A great piece of movie history...can't wait to watch it again.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Winter1.During": "%Constance nibbles on her snack as she intensely watches the movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.MoviesReactions.Winter1.After": "What a great movie! I'm really glad that you took me to watch it today. $1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.Introduction": "I see a new face around here...the name's Constance. I live around here as you can see.#$e#What is it? Need something?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "A gift? How did you know it was my birthday? This is great, thank you!$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "That's a great find, thank you! I really enjoy this!$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thanks for the gift, I appreciate it.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "A gift for little ol' me?$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "So you really think you did something with this, huh?$6",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Yikes...uh, thank you?$6",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Hm....well, at least you tried. Thanks.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "...my Pops always said to say 'thank you' for a gift no matter what, so...............'thank you'.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.BirthdayFish": "Fish for a Fishmonger. Hm, good catch.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_TheFishmonger": "A movie? Oh, wasn't expecting that.#$b#I'll gladly come, can't wait to see which movie you've picked.$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPRING
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_1": "New year, new me they say....I've got nothing to improve. I actually like myself enough to just let casual change happen over time.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Mon": "Did you know, some shrimps can be very noisy with their pincers.#$b#We're talking gunshot and jet engine levels of noise. It's fascinating.#$b#Guess that's why Pops never let me keep a pistol shrimp.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Mon2": "Hey @, what have you been up to? Any favorite fish so far?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Mon4": "I make fish puns just for the Halibut.$1#$b#If you can think of a betta pun just drop me a line.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Mon6": "I've found some really nicely colored clams and such at the shore today. There was also a sea urchin...I tried really hard to not put a hat on it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Mon8": "Sometimes I hear the seagulls cry loudly...I'll throw them a fish or two, that usually makes them really happy and they'll relax at the pier.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Mon10": "Hey Farmer, everything good? Caught all the fishes out there yet? What if I tell you that there are even more out there?$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Tue": "I've visited Birdie a bit ago, she seems to be in a good mood today. Maybe I'll ask her if she knows some mermaid stories.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Tue2": "Spider crabs use sponges, seaweed, and anything that will let them blend in, as camouflage that they stick to their carapace. That way they can increase their chance or survival.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Tue4": "Sea cucumbers help clean the ocean. Their diet consists of anything that sticks to sand at the bottom of the ocean and once they've digested everything they need they just poop out the clean sand. Fascinating.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Tue6": "I really liked when Pops took us out for long boat trips visiting all the different islands...there were a few he never took us to though. I wonder why...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Tue8": "Have you heard about the lava eel? Swimming around in such a hot environment...fascinating. I'd love to get one of them one day...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Tue10": "Hm....to fish or not to fish....that is the question...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Wed": "Empty dogfish egg cases sometimes wash up onto the beach...#$b#...some people call them mermaid purses.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Wed2": "%Seems like she's too much in thoughts mumbling about mermaids and having seen the prettiest scales ever...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Wed4": "I've been maintaining this boat all on my own. In the past Pops and big bro used to help me but since I left for Ginger Island I am on my own.#$b#...partly by choice.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Wed6": "Did you know that fish can still drown? They don't actually breathe water, they just filter the dissolved oxygen from it.#$b#That's why aquariums have machines filtering oxygen into the tanks!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Wed8": "The eggs of scorpion fish only take two days to hatch.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Wed10": "DJ’s aren’t allowed to work at fish markets because they’re always dropping the bass.#$b#Cod that was bad, eely bad!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Thu": "Hey @, just found this laying around, it might be of help to you. [162]",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Thu2": "The water bear may only be one millimeter long but it can survive in outer space. It can also withstand radiation up to a thousand times more than most animals.#$b#You can even bring it back when it was dried up for ten years.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Thu4": "A fish does not add new scales as it grows, the scales it has increase in size instead. In this way, growth rings are formed and these rings reveal the age of a fish.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Thu6": "How do you like fishing? I hope big bro got you into it.#$b#Fishing is a wonderful thing where you can relax but also find out your limits if you decide to do so. No matter what, it puts my heart at ease when the younger generation picks up a pole and continue the tradition.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Thu8": "The Bobbit Worm can grow to a length of 10 feet and it attacks with such a force that it can split a fish in two.#$b#Hm? Oh, just thinking to myself...would make for an interesting party trick, no?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Thu10": "Farmer! Good to see you. $1#$b#I've been thinking about taking a little journey out far into the ocean. I'm still curious about what I've been seeing the other day...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Fri": "#$q 310/311 fishorgan_followup#Hey Farmer! What is the name of the organ used by fish to obtain oxygen from water?#$r 310 25 fishorgan_right#Gills#$r 311 0 fishorgan_wrong1#Fins#$r 311 0 fishorgan_wrong2#Lungs#$r 311 0 fishorgan_wrong3#Cilia",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fishorgan_right": "I knew you'd get the answer right, good job!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fishorgan_wrong1": "Nope, fins are external appendages used for balance, steering and protection. The right answer was gills.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fishorgan_wrong2": "Wrong, an obvious choice since that's what it's called in human anatomy, but the right answer was gills.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fishorgan_wrong3": "Nope, the right answer was gills. Cilia are hair-like projections that move microbes and debris up and out of the airways and are part of the bronchus in the lungs.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fishorgan_followup": "$p 310 #Maybe I should come up with more interesting fish questions, you seem to know a lot. $1 |Maybe you'll get it right next time, don't worry about it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Fri2": "Bees seem to love this tropical climate....I might get myself a bee house on the ship#$b#....sweetening tea with honey is a delight.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Fri4": "You know what I can't stand? When I fish and catch a lot of trash. It's a real shame what people do to the ocean...how hard is it to keep the water clean?$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Fri6": "Electric eels can actually  release up to a full ampere of electric current, interesting, right? Even moreso when you know that it only takes 0.2 amperes for it to be deadly for a human.#$b#What a shocking fact.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Fri8": "Did you hear about the shark ghost?#$b#It vanished into fin air!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Fri10": "What did the romantic fisherman want?#$b#A gill-friend.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sat": "The Halichoeres bivittatus is a species of wrasse native to tropical waters with their thin, elongated bodies they easily slip out of a person's hand.#$b#They're also referred to as 'Slippery Dick' because of that.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sat2": "Hey @, have you heard the fisherman’s anthem? Osetra can you sea by the dolphin fish bite…",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sat4": "Apparently we only have discovered around 1% of the ocean so far. That leaves a lot of room for imagination on what mysteries still lie ahead of us...#$b# ...maybe there's a whole town of mermaids out there after all?$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sat6": "Pops used to tell me that I shouldn't say anything when I've got nothing nice to say.#$b#... #$b#...well, guess you're a swell mate then.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sat8": "You know how they say...Keep your friends close and your Anemones closer.#$b#The saying goes different? Oh, well...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sat10": "In the past lobsters were referred to as the cockroaches of the sea. They were mainly fed to prisoners and such as they were considered bottom of the food chain.#$b#Time surely changes, huh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sun": "...not one of my best mornings. I ran out of my favorite tea and couldn't get the water kettle to work.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sun2": "Another name for the Trigger fish is Humuhumunukunukuapua’a which mean ‘the fish with the pig-nosed face’.#$b#...funny, right?$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sun4": "Sometimes you just gotta agree to disagree....you cannot please everyone and there will always be different opinions. I mean, people aren't a hivemind after all, right?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sun6": "I swear....on some days I've seen someone out in the sea that I did not recognize.#$b#...I wonder who she was...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sun8": "A nice morning for me includes a good cup of tea sweetened with honey, some multi-grain bread and dill mustard spread topped with salmon and crab.#$b#Of course alongside fishing for some lunch later on, heh. I like sharing my haul with Birdie, she has some nice recipes I really enjoy.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_Sun10": "Birdie gave me a sweater the other day that had little fishes at the front looking all cute and stuff.#$b#I love it!$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE SUMMER
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_1": "Ah, the official start of warm weather even at Pelican Town. How's your farm doing?#$b#Some melon wine would surely quench the summer heats thirst, huh. I personally tend to go for cool refreshing teas instead.$1#$b#Nothing against a glass of good wine though.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Mon": "I've made my ferrets some fresh kibbles this morning. They also enjoy the occasional meat supper...#$b#Hm? Oh, I'd never dress them up like dolls. Well, they sometimes want to wear a little hat but that's it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Mon2": "Have you ever considered putting a hat onto a sea urchin? They're adorable wearing those tiny hats.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Mon4": "Monday shmonday...I dreamt about catching the biggest fish I've ever seen. We're talking 'bout as big as me here.#$b#...then I woke up and was wrestling my pillow. Well, at least I didn't eat it this time.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Mon6": "%Constance notices you but is distracted writing down notes in a small notebook.#$b#%You decide to leave her in her thoughts.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Mon8": "The Salema porgy is a species of fish that can cause hallucinations when eaten. Be sure to always check carefully what you're catching and eating.#$b#Don't want you to go around doing silly things or anything.#$b#...I'll body slam you to cut down the damage in case that happens so don't worry.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Mon10": "I miss the times when Pops bough us some sparklers and we lit them late at night, watching them crackle like a tiny star...#$b#...we'd grill some fish and enjoy the warm weather. I miss those times...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Tue": "I don't really care making big money to be honest. I prefer the freedom that comes with being my own boss. I mean, fish is always on demand so I will at least not struggle.#$b#There are other riches I prefer, like-...hm. Maybe that's for another time.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Tue2": "I've all kind of things to sell, you know?#$b#If you need anything just check out my stock.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Tue4": "The skin of a shark feels like sandpaper because it is covered in tiny little teeth that are called dermal denticles.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Tue6": "Hey, did you know that the poison of the puffer fish is 1200 times more poisonous than Cyanide?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Tue8": "Hello @, do you sometimes think about where you'd be now if you didn't do a certain thing?#$b#Regret can be awful sometimes...and the longer it goes on the more it poisons you. It can make it really hard changing things finally.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Tue10": "Warhammer, Alkemy...hm? oh, I was just thinking about a name for my new sea urchin.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Wed": "Sometimes I just like to take one of my ferrets and rub my face against them. Is that weird?#$b#Well, their fur is just so soft and I love them very much.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Wed2": "Some one once said that the greatest attraction of a fishing trip is that it allows washing one's soul with pure air and I think there's something true about that.#$b#I can't even begin to describe how it feels to just sail away with your trusty fishing rod ready to catch some fish...$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Wed4": "Ahoy! Have you seen a particular man on the island before? He wears neat shades and seems rather blue...#$b#From him I know that there are all kind of odd and interesting things out there. It gets me curious.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Wed6": "I am fine out here alone. I admit, sometimes I wish I had someone to call my own but...never mind. I'm probably too old for this.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Wed8": "Many species of fish start their lives as females and when a male is needed the lead female will become one.#$b#In other instances males can change into females as well.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Wed10": "Say, how is my big bro treating you? Good? Yeah, thought so. I always wondered why he never found anyone when he's such a swell mate...#$b#Then again he is saying the same thing about me every time we talk, hm.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Thu": "I've stayed on this island for years. No, I've my reasons....anyway. Don't you have some coconuts to find?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Thu2": "I've got a rotating stock, you can make a good deal now and then, you know? Always worth a shot to come by. Even if it's just for a cup of tea.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Thu4": "Summer time always means great weather to fish. I do enjoy the all year around warm weather of Ginger island. Sometimes the heats getting to me though.#$b#A nice cool drink in the shade is a welcoming change then. Remember to not overdo things.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Thu6": "How's %farm doing for you?#$b#I'd assume well, since you got the time to talk to me of all people.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Thu8": "Ugh, Sorry about last time. I don't really like talking about myself and here I go randomly dumping things onto you.#$b#Maybe one of these days I'll tell you more if you want to hear me out.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Thu10": "Roses are red, the ocean is blue-....huh? Wait, how long have you been standing there?#$b#I, uh....you heard nothing.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Fri": "Most fish reproduce by laying eggs, though some fish, such as great white sharks, give birth to live babies called pups.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Fri2": "Summer is a great time, right? Are you enjoying yourself in the warm summer heat or do you live the work-a-holic life?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Fri4": "Hey @, there's something I've been thinking about.#$q 305/306 willyquestion_followup#Do you think it's odd when you cannot look at someone anymore because they remind you of someone else?#$r 305 15 willyquestion_yes#There's nothing wrong in needing some space to process...#$r 306 0 willyquestion_sorry#Sorry, what is this about?#$r 306 -10 willyquestion_no#Don't be so sensitive!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.willyquestion_yes": "Thanks for understanding...I know I should be over this but...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.willyquestion_sorry": "Ah, well, never mind...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.willyquestion_no": "Wow, alright. Now I know who NOT to ask for sympathy in the future.$6",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.willyquestion_followup": "$p 305 #A loss can be hard sometimes, I know..It's been a good while but there's something just keeping me from being able to approach him again...$3 |Yeah, I don't know what I expected...just leave.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Fri6": "I spent this morning catching my ferrets one after another.#$b#Why? Oh, sometimes they just decide they want to play so they take my hat and make me chase them.#$b#I know I should scold them but it's pretty funny to be honest.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Fri8": "One of my favorite things to eat is fried calamari. I really enjoy it in the summer as it reminds me of the times Pops took us all around the island and one had a summer festival with many food stalls.#$b#They'd fry the food right in front of you in a playful way, heh.$1#$b#Well, I guess children are easily excited by simply things.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Fri10": "%You see Constance holding a trash bag full of random wet tidbits as she's grumbling about water pollution.$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sat": "...don't say anything. I've seen him peek past the railing when you arrived here.$3#$b#...shush. I'm over it, don't worry.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sat2": "I swear, one of these days I'll go out and talk to him...well. How am I supposed to even start the conversation?#$b#...'Sorry I kinda stopped existing for you after Pops died but you were too much like him'......yeah....sounds swell.$3#$e#Sorry, I am not in the mood to talk right now...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sat4": "I might head to the other side of the island later, up towards the volcano. There's a few goodies there I like to collect.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sat6": "There is a lot of old bones and alike to get here in the island. It makes you wonder what kind of creatures must've roamed around here long ago...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sat8": "I've been collecting clams and such for a while now. There's this little project that I am working on but I don't wanna spoil you so I'm not gonna say what it is about.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sat10": "Oh! Hey, Farmer, great to see you.#$b#I think today I might go and take it a bit slower and only fish for maybe 6 hours.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sun": "Did you know that fish have great memories? Some species of fish can even recognize and remember humans that give them food rewards.#$b#You can play them a little tune while you fed them and after some time they come back when you play it.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sun2": "How about sitting back and fishing a little? The weather is great for catching some fishes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sun4": "Sometimes I sit out in the rain late at night looking onto the vast ocean...maybe it'd because I'm tired by then but I swear I can hear someone whisper in the waters.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sun6": "Hey, @! Caught any fish lately?#$b#Maybe I'll show you some new moves to really get some more strength in your arms so you can fish for 10 hours straight.#$b#That's not normal? Oh, huh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sun8": "Now that summer is about to end how was it for you? I hope you made some good summer memories this year.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_Sun10": "When I was small I almost drowned in the sea once. It was a windless day and I foolishly decided to take a skiff and row all the way out till the coast was barely to be seen.#$e#I was so exhausted in the end and couldn't make it back when something bumped into me and I fell into the water...#$b#Don't worry, my big bro saved me in the end. I'm not a lost soul haunting you, haha!$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE FALL
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_1": "Ahoy, Farmer. Ready for the spooky season?#$b#It's time to get some pumpkins ready to carve and a costume to scare others, right?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Mon": "A warm fall morning is just right to enjoy the colorful leaves and a cup of tea. There's something about the change from summer to fall that seems magical...in some places they celebrate a big harvest festival and offer foods to the gods for next years bountiful harvest.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Mon2": "Imagine being a mermaid...I wonder how it's like to live all the way out in the ocean deep down below...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Mon4": "I might go on a little trip soon. I've heard there's a certain island out there which piqued my interest. Pops never mentioned anything to me about it...I wonder why.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Mon6": "Oh, tell me...how's Pelikan Town doing? I was think bout big bro the other day...ah, never mind. Just silly little anecdotes bout the youth anyway.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Mon8": "One of these days I'll show you some tricks my ferrets learned. It's really funny watching them do their thing. It's like a little choreography.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Mon10": "What I think of Joja?#$b#...$3#$b#...how is that even a question? I've seen more hermit crabs with joja cola cans as a home than I ever wanted to see.#$e#Zero. It's zero. I wanted to see zero hermit crabs with joja cola cans as a home.#$b#This is just really sad...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Tue": "Did you know that moray eels are not aggressive when they open and close their mouth, they are actually just breathing?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Tue2": "The speed of sound in water is 1,435 m/sec which is nearly five times faster than the speed of sound in air.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Tue4": "Big Bro used to tell me that I should take some time off and not overdo it.#$b#Needless to say that I didn't listen to his advice and fell asleep on the boat once I was out fishing during the day.#$b#...yet again he had to go and find me. I guess I was a lot of work back then, huh.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Tue6": "Hey @, ready to rake up some leaves on your farm yet? Maybe I'll come visit one of these days to see all this progress you've been talking about.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Tue8": "Believe it or not but I've been talking quite a lot to big bro lately.$1#$b#Ok, maybe I should think twice about bringing my ferrets with me next time I visit him though...$3#$b#...they tried to steal his fresh catch last time. Funny to look at until you have to clean up the mess.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Tue10": "Ahoy! Nice to see you again @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Wed": "%Constance mumbling something about pumpkins and spices.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Wed2": "Ah, hello Farmer. Gone fishing lately? There's a lot of good fish to catch on the island.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Wed4": "Sorry, I am a bit busy today. There's a few things I want to get done early so there's no troubles on the boat.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Wed6": "A group of sea urchins are called a herd.#$b#Now I really want to give them little cowboy hats and a lasso.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Wed8": "The crisp night air during fall is really lovely. Though I do prefer the warmth. I guess everything has their pros and cons, huh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Wed10": "Thanks for always dropping by. I always told myself that being on my own was fine but now I realize that my heart does ache for company now and then.#$b#You may not have realized it but you're really good in helpings others.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Thu": "Fishing or farming...what do you prefer?#$b#Hm? Oh, There's no wrong answer, I am just curious.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Thu2": "Fresh fish is great fish. Not so fresh fish is a monument to a wasteful spirit.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Thu4": "Oh, great timing Farmer. I've found this laying around and thought you might be able to use it somehow. [265]",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Thu6": "Birdie and I have been friends for a long while already. I enjoy hanging out with her in the evening when I'm done with my work.#$b# Sometimes we have little game nights too, she's got me every time so far.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Thu8": "Why I always wear the same sweater? Hm, this isn't the same one, that would be weird. I just like red as a color, I guess.#$b#Guess this turned into my work uniform, huh...oh. Yeah, I am always kind of working it seems, hm.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Thu10": "Coming back again for a visit?$1#$b#Drop by anytime you want, you're a welcomed guest on my boat.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Fri": "Please tell me you're making leaf piles to jump into on your farm.#$b#I've been thinking about it for a while but most the leaves around here don't get the nice crisp that is so lovely because of the heat...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Fri2": "There's a type of jellyfish out there that looks like a fried egg and honestly...it makes me hungry thinking bout it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Fri4": "I can't decide between jasmine tea and Ceylon Assam for today. Or should I go fancy with some flower tea? Hm...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Fri6": "Hey @, if you love bad fish puns, then let minnow!$1#$b#Whale, whale, whale...I'll be your ofFISHial fish pun supplier then.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Fri8": "Lucky Lunch...having that dish to eat makes you more than just lucky, heh. The taste is out of this world.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Fri10": "%You see Constance playing with her ferrets, she seems to not have noticed you.$5#$b#...alright, alright. You'll get some rainbow trout fillet today, you little rascals.$5#$b#Oh! Hey @, what's up?$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sat": "Have I ever bored you with my fish facts? I've been told before that I sometimes don't get social cues...#§b#I don't really get what the big deal is, everybody loves fish facts.#$b#...right?$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sat2": "%Constance seems a little aloof today.#$b#...#$b'Ah, oh? Sorry @, there's been a few things on my mind lately.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sat4": "My ferrets all have their own distinguished character. There's one who's a toe biter but I won't tell who it is. #$b#A little bit feisty, yes, but I don't shame them.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sat6": "What's the difference between a guitar and a fish?#$b#You can tune a guitar but you can't tuna fish.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sat8": "Ahoy, Farmer! Care for a little cup of tea with lil old me?[614]$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sat10": "Do you think there's a moment in time one grows too old for certain things? Like, I don't know...$3#$b#...finding true love, wanting harmony, dreams coming true, things like that.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sun": "Hey Farmer, come by my shop anytime. I've got quite a few things that may interest you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sun2": "Imagine armor that replicated the iridescent colors of fish scales...that would be a sight to behold...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sun4": "Sometimes I find really great stuff when going out with the boat and fishing in the deep sea.#$b#It ranges from mundane things like trash and random tidbits to even artifacts and odd things I am unsure are from human origins or not...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sun6": "Soon to be winter, eh?#$b#You could accept the cold or just come here during that season, it's up to you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sun8": "Ah, I've been thinking actually visiting big bro soon, but the thought of being in the cold is really off putting...$3#$b#Yeah, I know, I know...it's just some snow and ice...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_Sun10": "I still don't like the cold but....there's reasons out there where you accept going through things you don't like.#$b#Like, the people you care for as an example.$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE WINTER
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_1": "Bullocks...I don't particularly like the cold. Farmer, don't ever throw a snowball at me, I'd hate what would happen next...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Mon": "Why does the fish blush?#$b#Because it saw the bottom of the ocean.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Mon2": "Did you ever imagine what's out there in the deep ocean? Colorful reefs, exotic fishes, the vast salty sea...#$b#...and mermaids, heh.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Mon4": "Would it be weird trying to make fish candy? Hm? You wanna know if I meant fish flavored or fish shaped?#$b# Ah, yes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Mon6": "Yarr, shiver in me boots.#$b#...#$b#...How did you know I've spent too much time with the pirates?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Mon8": "I might talk to Gus one of these days. I've a few things in mind and want his opinion on it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Mon10": "Oh? I see you're in high spirits today as well, @. It's good to see you so lively despite the cold back home.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Tue": "Saltwater or freshwater fish? Or the all-rounders that can survive in wide range of salinity like eels, salmons or flounders? Hm, hard to choose...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Tue2": "Good to see you again, look what I found at the beach this morning wriggling around, I thought you might like it. [154]",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Tue4": "Leo has asked me before why my hair is so bright and honestly...I don't know how to answer that.$3#$b#I think it's been like this since I was a kid to be honest. Normally the sun bleaches the hair but, uh...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Tue6": "Hm, yeah. Pops called my bright hair a blessing because he could always see me from afar.#$b#Helped catch little ol' me when I was zooming around like a ferret on sugar.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Tue8": "Hah, I admit that I've had many instances of weird hair styles in the past.#$b#One time I all shaved it off and Pops was shocked.$1#$b#I should find the old photos to show you at some point, it was really funny.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Tue10": "I'm too old for going wild with my hair now. It was fun in my youth but I think I am content right now.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Wed": "What did the tuna say when he posted bail?#$b#I'm off the hook.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Wed2": "Fish moan, grunt, croak, boom, hiss, whistle, creak, shriek, and wail. They also rattle their bones and gnash their teeth.#$b#They don't actually have any vocal cords, interesting, huh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Wed4": "Last night I thought I heard someone sing at the docks...I couldn't see anything in the pitch-black darkness of the night...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Wed6": "Aha, Farmer!$1#$b#I got something for you, take a look.[128]$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Wed8": "Aye, would you greet Elliot from me? he's been writing me such sweet letters lately.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Wed10": "I don't really have any duck feathers laying around but I am sure Elliot would like some parrot feathers as well, right?#$b#I've been wondering what to add to my letters back to Elliot, is all.#$b#He's writing letters to me, little stories he's heard of about mermaids and such.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Thu": "Hey Farmer, escaping the cold and hide away at Ginger island?#$b#I can relate, the cold isn't really a favorite of mine.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Thu2": "Did you know that the oldest found fishhook dates back to about 42,000 years ago?#$b#It's fascinating how long fishing as we know it has been around.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Thu4": "Hook, line and sinker..hm?#$b#Oh, ahoy @. I've just been thinking about aquatic terms and the modern use of them, is all.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Thu6": "Oh, I've visited that blue fella some time ago. It's rare that I see him about though.#$b#He was talking about some odd things I didn't quite get but didn't want to elaborate.#$b#Some unique laugh he got as well.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Thu8": "That man's play with words is quite fascinating. I let him be thought, he seems more like a ghost from times gone by than a person.#$b#Maybe I am imagining things.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Thu10": "I might consider making snowmen with the kids.#$b#What? I can change my mind about the cold, okay?$3#$b#...I just really want to be more a part of the community again in some way.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Fri": "Come by to my shop any time, Farmer. I've always got useful bits and bobs around.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Fri2": "Thank you for the visit, Farmer. I feel like you're the change that was needed around here.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Fri4": "...#$b#...yesterday one of my ferrets stuck it's head into my mouth when I was yawning. That's the third time this month.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Fri6": "Today I think I mastered the arts of juggling 4 ferrets all at once while keeping my food safe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Fri8": "I couldn't imagine living further inside land. No ocean close-by would make me feel miserable, I think. There's just something about it that deeply calms me, even with it's vast unexplored areas.#$b#I've tried going to Zuzu City years ago and stayed at a hotel...I didn't sleep well at all. I missed the soft rocking waves and salty air...$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Fri10": "Friday is my day!$1#$b#What about my day? Huh, I guess it's like any other, but hey, I decide for myself what I want to do so it's awesome either way.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sat": "Hey Farmer, preparing for the end of the year yet?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sat2": "The end if the year is slowly creeping closer, will you celebrate it alone or with company?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sat4": "I am trying to convince Birdie to do some midnight fishing tonight. There's supposed to be rare fishes out there at this time of year.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sat6": "I was thinking letting my ferrets have a little dance party tonight. They love wiggling around.#$b#What it's bout? Well, it's just as it says: dancing, music, food. Having a good time.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sat8": "I've talked to Birdie earlier. Told her about new years eve.#$b#...maybe I've got some ideas for this year.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sat10": "I can't wait for tomorrow, the day is planned ahead and in the late evening I'll take Birdie and we'll visit big bro.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sun": "Don't you think there's better places to be than with me at this time of the year?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sun2": "I do think you should probably  get home and spend the end of the year with your loved ones.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sun4": "Ah, hey there @. One last errand to run before the clock hits midnight?#$b#Don't overwork yourself.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sun6": "Do you have any wishes for the new year?#$b#I hope the new year will bring some change.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sun8": "Ah yes, I think I will take Birdie with me to visit big bro for the new years celebration.#$b#He said Elliot would come as well. There will be grilled fish and stew alongside salads and more.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_Sun10": "I love celebrating the new year with Birdie, big bro and Elliot. It really feels like a little family gathering.$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "Running around finding painted eggs is still a thing, huh?#$b#I still remember how Pops kept hiding way too many eggs. Once big bro got older he helped and kept hiding them too well.#$b#God...that awful rotten smell in summer...$6",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Can't catch me dressed to the nines. I am no fan of that frilly stuff.#$b#Don't get me wrong, it's not that I dislike it in general but...I ain't delicate enough to wear something like that.$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_10": "Mhm...I really miss going to the Luau. Maybe I should go again, but...hm.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "I think I'll go fish some more for tomorrow. I want to catch something real good to add.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_27": "There's some Jellies floating around the water sometimes at the island. Not as much as at the coast of Pelican Town tomorrow, but more regularly.#$b#Still a sight to see...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "I actually can't wait to see the Jellies this year...#$b#Maybe I'll see something else peek from the water as well during this magical time.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_15": "I think it would be unfair to go to the fishing tent and dominate it, huh?#$b#Yeah....I don't do competition. My blood just starts to get heated when it comes to fishing.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "I...really won't do it again this year. No no...#$b#Maybe...just one round.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_26": "Hey @, are you in the mood to get spooky yet?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "Hey Farmer! I was thinking about going into the maze to scare the others a little bit in some good humor.#$b#What? I'd be too obvious when I approach? I never intended to be hidden away.$1",
	//"Dialogue.winter_7": "Yeah....no. I ain't even attempting to go when the cold can freeze the balls off a brass monkey. I prefer the tropical weather here on the island.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_7": "You ready to participate in the fishing contest?#$b#Don't get dressed too much for the cold, once you swing the pole you'll get all heated up anyway and it'll be more of a struggle to catch fish.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "I'll stay out of the contest, don't want a repeat from the stardew fair...I'll be a bit conflicted who to cheer on more, you or big bro.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_24": "Hm...you think it's a good idea to go? I'm not sure.#$b#I guess it's a celebration for everyone, huh...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "I wonder what reaction I'll get when I give my gift this year.#$b#Are fishes that weird to give?$3",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tea.000": "Hm~, nothing beats a good cup of tea, right?$1#$b#I do love all kinds of flavors honestly. It really depends on the mood that I am in, heh.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tea.001": "Ah, @. Want a cup of tea as well? I've made enough for several cups.#$b#Even in summer heat it's a delight. When it gets too hot I just drink it iced, it's really refreshing.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tea.002": "Tea at this time of the year is just as good as any. It's always tea time somewhere, heh.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tea.003": "A good way to warm up during colder days is to drink tea. I know I mainly stay at an all year round warm place, but...#$b#...tea can be drunk at any time. Good to take with you when you approach colder regions.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tea.004": "Hm, I'm deciding to stay inside today. A nice cup of tea while it rains soothes the soul.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tea.005": "I've been keeping in touch with some other tea enthusiasts in the valley via mail. It is fun to hear other peoples thoughts on tea.#$b#Some even send their own homegrown leaves sometimes. It's a delight.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.shop.000": "Hey @, care to buy anything? I've got a good chunk of fine goods that are waiting to find a new home.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.shop.001": "The weather is nice, right? It really itches me to go out and fish...#$b#...but here I am dutifully bound to serving the customer.#$b#Which is basically just you. Hm...but still.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.shop.002": "Aye, visiting during shop hours again? Anything interesting you find?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.shop.003": "Ahoy, Farmer. What business brings you in today?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.tooearly.000": "Huh? What are you doing here?#$b#You're not supposed to be here during this time of day...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.fishing.000": "Nothing beats fishing at the end of the day. It's calm and relaxing to me...#$b#If you asked me to give up fishing I'd severely question your sanity and willingness to live.$3#$b#Hm? Oh, nothing. I just love fishing.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.fishing.001": "Do you hear that? The nice faint calls of seagulls and the calm sound of the waves...#$b#...nothing is more relaxing. If I would add a cup of tea to this I'd be in a trance.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.fishing.002": "Big bro used to take me out on little journeys when pops was gone.#$b#He always promised me that mermaid island was real and that we'd go there one day...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.fishing.003": "Do you like fishing as well? Come and join me, it's really relaxing.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.pier.000": "Ah, sometimes I think about certain things....hm.#$b#Oh, never mind. I'm just rambling.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.pier.001": "Oh, hey Farmer. I was just thinking about some stuff. Nothing too important.#$b#Anything interesting happening around you?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.stock.000": "It's always important to check if ones wares are fresh and in perfect condition.#$b#Everything else gets marked down. Well, or my ferrets eat it.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.stock.001": "I enjoy tending to my shop. No boss or anyone telling me how to do things.#$b#Well, there's also a slight lack of customers but this is more of a hobby anyway.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.birdie.000": "I enjoy spending time with Birdie. She has a lot of stories to tell.#$b#Sometimes there is a mermaid story here and there as well.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.birdie.001": "I just hang out around here sometimes. There's this funky music I kinda like, tho I know better than to disturb without reason.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.birdie.002": "Watching the sun set has something magical. Sometimes I wish I had someone special to share this moment with. Oh well.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.birdie.003": "Ah...I've got nothing to say...#$b#Sometimes certain things will make you speechless, like a beautiful sunset in the heat of the island. Or pouring the perfect cup of green tea...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.troutderby.000": "Oh! I am getting ready to take part in the Trout Derby. Just taking a moment here to enjoy the view, heh. $1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.troutderby.001": "I'll be here all day. There's some Googans and Greenhorns here that chew me a good one off my ears but I'll just stuff em with bait and ignore em. $1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.squidfest.000": "Mhm, Another good time to fish me some squid in home waters.#$b#",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Schedule.Dialogue.squidfest.001": "Ah, nothing beats fishing. And to top it off I get to enjoy some good ol' squid with big bro later, heh! $1",
	"Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Hm, it's actually quite nice hanging out with a bunch of people.#$b#Plus, Barnabas really knows how to grill fish nicely.",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//==== M E R M A I D ===========================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Gifttastes.Love": "I really appreciate you thinking of me.$1#$b#You must've put a lot of thought into this gift!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you kindly.$1#$b#I'll treasure it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Maybe...someone else will like this...$7",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Gifttastes.Hate": "I...am disappointed...$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Gifttastes.Neutral": "There surely will be some use for this somehow, thanks.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Hm...I suppose this is another way of recycling.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Why...are you so cruel...$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Delightful! I am sure the person it is for will love it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Ah...I apologize, but...I prefer someone elses company.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "I'm sorry...maybe another time.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.GreenRain": "...I've heard about a similar phenomenon from a long time ago...I do not fear it though. It is part of nature's cycle, even if it appears frightening at first.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "All is well is the world. Looks like it was just another one of nature's wonders!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Again...I found myself oddly fascinated by the green rain actually. I might go and study it more...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.StardropTea": "I love this tea, thank you so much!$1#$b#I'll make sure to enjoy this!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.peach": "A peach! I love these fuzzy little things! I enjoy them a lot in my desserts and teas. Thank you so much!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.scallure": "Ohhh! I love this flower so much! It's great as a tea or made into a perfume!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.sunsetrose": "...!#$b#This rose...oh, the colors remind me of-...$9",
	
	// MOVIE REACTIONS 
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Spring0.Before": "Oh, I've heard quite a bit about this!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Spring0.During": "Oh! You can do it!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Spring0.After": "What a wonderful movie! I really liked it!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Spring1.Before": "I love these type of movies!$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Spring1.During": "%Calliope is really invested.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Spring1.After": "Ah, it feels like I learned so much from this! I did enjoy how easily digestible it is for everyone.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Summer0.Before": "It's based on a game? Interesting.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Summer0.During": "%Calliope silently watches the movie. She doesn't seem too invested into it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Summer0.After": "It was nice to watch. Though I think I am just not into these Western type of things.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Summer1.Before": "Hmh, it looks like a nice movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Summer1.During": "Huh, I see.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Summer1.After": "...I don't think I quite got the message of this movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Fall0.Before": "Ohhhh, I think I'm gonna like this!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Fall0.During": "%Calliope is sitting on the edge of her seat.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Fall0.After": "I loved it! Such a great movie, thank you for taking me to watch it!$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Fall1.Before": "I can't wait to see what this movie is about.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Fall1.During": "Huh? Wait.....oh! Fascinating!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Fall1.After": "It was quite a good movie! It gave me a few things to think about.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Winter0.Before": "A family movie? It's been a while since I've seen one.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Winter0.During": "%Calliope is wiping a few tears away during the sad scenes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Winter0.After": "...what a great movie. I could feel the emotions of the people really well...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Winter1.Before": "I always wanted to watch this movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Winter1.During": "%Calliope is blushing at the romantic scenes, she is really enjoying this movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.MoviesReactions.Winter1.After": "I think this is my new favorite movie!$3",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Introduction": "Greetings to you, fellow land walker!$1#$b#It is nice to make your acquaintance.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "For me?#$b#I can't believe you're remembering my birthday, @!$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Thank you so much!$1#$b#I didn't think you'd know that today is my birthday.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Oh!$1#$b#Thank you kindly for this birthday gift, @!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Much appreciated!#$b#It's always nice to know that there's someone out there remembering ones birthday.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm...#$b#....#$b#...it's the thought that counts.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "...#$b#...I'm trying to think of a good way to let you down easy but...#$b#...at least you tried.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Wow, that is quite a birthday gift you got me there, @. Thanks.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Ah, it's this time of year again, isn't it?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_MermaidCalliope": "A movie?#$b#Sure! I'd love to see one with you, @!$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.spring_1": "A breathe of fresh air, the beginning of a new year...this is the perfect time to start anew!$1#$b#I like to sit down and write in my journal what I would like to do and improve this year.#$b#Maybe picking up a new hobby or perhaps decluttering the house?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.summer_1": "I live in a place where it's always warm, but it's always interesting to see people from other climates yearn for the warmth of summer.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.fall_1": "I love to gather the leaves that fall down into the waters.#$b#They make for great decorations, heh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.winter_1": "Winter isn't too much to my liking but I know a few  mermaids who mainly live in the colder regions!",
	
	//DIALOGUE 0 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Mon": "Did you know that the tusk of a narwhal is actually a tooth?#$b#Packed with nerves and covered in holes that allow sea water to enter it's used to detect changes in their environment.#$b#That can be temperature, water's saltiness or other things!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Tue": "The islands seasons don't really differ from each other as it's in a tropical climate.#$b#I like to swim around and visit other shores to see the different seasons elsewhere sometimes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Wed": "In some regions Wednesdays are also called 'Bergfest'.#$b#As this day is seen as the middle of the week it is like being at the peak of the mountain with the next few days being the walk back down to start walking up the mountain coming Monday, heh.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Thu": "My brother is always out and about and sometimes hard to catch.#$b#Usually you can find him at the orchard though! He really loves to take care of the trees there.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Fri": "I often use Fridays to sit back and enjoy my time off.#$b#Sometimes though I have to admit not being able to sit still, haha! Then I roam around and see if I can help out someone.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sat": "How is your farm doing, @?#$b#Are you growing a lot of flowers this time around?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sun": "I usually don't really follow fashion trends or anything. Sometimes there are a few things I do think are cute.#$b#Usually I make my things myself though. This way I can fully customize them to my liking.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 2 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Mon2": "Collecting the beach forage around here is always exciting.#$b#There's fun things you can do with what you find, let it be from the beach or somewhere else!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Tue2": "I was thinking of maybe asking my brother to grow a few new crops around here.#$b#He agreed to look into it and find some fitting for the island!$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Wed2": "People always say that mermaids have some kind of magical properties. In some ways we do, I guess.#$b#I mean, I cannot speak for all but I sure can switch into a human and a mermaid form. There's...other things I can do but...people need to be careful keeping their fairytales apart from the real deal. We are all actual living beings after all...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Thu2": "Have you grown Scallures before? They look so pretty...$3#$b#I'd love to grow some here at some point.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Fri2": "I am thinking about making a gift to convey my feelings....sometimes it is hard to put things into words.$3#$b#I hope this way I can have an easier way into starting a conversation...hm...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sat2": "I've tried flowers, making something out of wood....somehow nothing proper comes to mind.#$b#...aam I approaching it the wrong way with making this gift?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sun2": "I have taken a break for a little while. Somehow my heads a little mess, I guess.#$b#It's alright, sometimes things like this happen. It's normal. It's just time to relax and take a step back.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE 4 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Mon4": "Oh...I went out earlier to go catch some fish. Their scales shimmer in such a nice way I was wondering if I could use them to turn it into some sort of paint...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Tue4": "Ginger Island is a nice place to be at. I can see why so many people go there. Especially with the old resort back up and running.#$b#That makes it harder for me to find a good moment to try and talk to-...hm...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Wed4": "I like to talk to my brother about all kind of things. You could say that we're pretty close.#$b#He was basically the one that raised me after our parents disappeared.#$e#...you know...sometimes I'be been wondering where most of us went. My brother told me that this island used to be fairly well populated, you know?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Thu4": "Hey, @.#$e#...do you believe in fate? Is there maybe a possibility that certain encounters were just meant to be...#$b#...#$b#...but that meant that certain tragedies are unavoidable as well, right...?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Fri4": "...Sorry, I was a bit lost in my thoughts.$1#$b#Hm? Oh! Did you know that my brother really likes taking care of plants and the likes?#$b#He could ramble about them for hours, haha!#$e#He said it all started when he found some books about botany when he was young. I think....they were pretty water-damaged as he found them in a shipwreck but it was enough to spark a life-long passion.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sat4": "I hope you enjoy your stay here. I'd like to think that this island is a place where everyone who comes here gets to enjoy themselves.$1#$b#Let me know if you need something, okay?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sun4": "Taken some time for yourself yet, @? It's important to relax now and again.#$b#Maybe I'll brew you a nice tea one of these days. $3",
	
	//DIALOGUE 6 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Mon6": "I can't believe what my brother told me earlier today, @.#$b#Peaches, pears, apricots, quinces, strawberries as well as apples are members of the rose family!#$e#Actually, this makes me like them even more, hehe!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Tue6": "Heh, I've been up and about for a while already. I think today I will collect some forage and alike for my next crafting project.#$b#Maybe I will make something to wear...or perhaps some decoration. Who knows!#$b#I will let you know how it'll turn out, heh!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Wed6": "Oh, @!$1#$b#Look! I found it earlier at the beach, isn't it pretty?#$b#%Calliope shows you a sea shell shimmering in an iridescent way.#$b#It was just sitting there right out of the water. Normally I'd have to dive pretty deep to find one like this.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Thu6": "Usually I sing alone but lately it was suggested to me to go out and find like-minded people and maybe form something like a choir or...band?#$b#What do you think? I normally just sing when I am alone or when my brother is around....#$b#...maybe I will think about it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Fri6": "If you told me I can only eat one thing for the rest of my life...I'd probably pick peaches.#$b#",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sat6": "Hehehe~$1#$b#Oh! Hey there, @!#$b#I was just thinking about, um...someone. You know...$3#$b#%Calliope fumbles around, hiding something she was holding away.#$e#Oh! Well...maybe...I am thinking about giving a gift to someone, hehe...$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sun6": "%Calliope seems absent-minded, humming a somber song as she observes the flora and fauna.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 8 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Mon8": "A wonderful day to you,@!$1#$b#Earlier I went to Constance and hang out with her!$3#$b#We talked about fish and the things I've seen while deep underwater.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Tue8": "I recently took interest in photography. I've been wondering for a while if there was a way to show the deep sea world to those who cannot venture down like us mermaid can...#$b#...I wonder who I can talk to about this.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Wed8": "My brother finally got around fixing up a few fences around the island. He is such a dedicated hard worker!#$b#Well, he more often than not will get distracted along the way but he gets the work done sooner or later.#$b#It's just part of him so I am used to it, heh.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Thu8": "%Calliope is lost in thoughts as she plays around with a sea shell in her hands while singing a song to herself.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Fri8": "@!$1#$b#Great to see you! How's farm life going for you? I've recently spotted some interesting  little things deep in the waters you might be interested in.#$b#I'll tell you about it later after asking my brother a few things about it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sat8": "%Calliope is humming a song about a certain fishmonger, upon noticing you she quickly stops with a blush.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sun8": "Have you ever wondered what else is out there? Is adventure calling for you, @?#$b#Or maybe you've found your place already in the world, perhaps?",
	
	//DIALOGUE 10 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Mon10": "Constance and I have been on a few boat rides lately. I've shown her some hidden favorite spots of mine and she was so eager to go!$3#$b#I asked her if she wanted me to show her some diving spots and I've never seen anyone agree so quickly, heh.#$b#I just really love that glimmer in eyes when she gets all excited.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Tue10": "I've been talking to some other friends of mine and we traveled around a bit to perform some music.#$b#I still remember when I got over my stage-fright, heh.#$b#Nothing better to get confidence in your voice when singing a love song to your partner, hehe~$4#$e#You know, when I performed that song for Constance it was the middle of the night, I was a bit of a mess because I was so nervous...#$b#...Constance was just so excited to see me though! Once I looked at her it just came out naturally. Ah...this is a bit embarrassing to admit, heh.$3#$b#Sorry, I am rambling too much.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Wed10": "I was thinking about asking my brother to maybe get some peach trees planted. He mentioned there being miniature versions of fruit trees...I wonder what's that about.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Thu10": "I enjoy diving down into the ocean to explore unseen areas. Sometimes I even bring a few things back. Mainly for Constance since she can't dive as deep as a mermaid sadly...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Fri10": "You know...Constance has those little dimples when she smiles brightly and I love it, heh.$3#$b#Hm? Ah...well. Hehe...sometimes I just like looking at her in silence...d-don't tell her though! Um...sorry, hehe...$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sat10": "%Calliope is lost in thoughts, petting a familiar looking ferret.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.Sun10": "Oh! I love babysitting Constance's ferrets!$4#$b#I often bring them fish and other things to enjoy, truly delightful to watch them play, heh~.$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "Finding eggs is a fun activity. We have something similar actually.#$b#My brother used to paint sea shells when we were younger and let me swim around deep underwater to find them.#$b#Depending on the pattern I always got a different price, heh.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Hm...I'd really like to dance with-...ah...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "My brother asked me to gather some forage so we could make a big hotpot tomorrow.#$b#I am excited!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "I've talked to the jellies many times before. They actually quite enjoy the night when the townsfolk gather at the beach.$1#$b#It makes them feel important and loved.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "I haven't really been to many fairs.#$b#I'd love to go to more though!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "People had commented on my appearance being a good costume on spirit's eve before....#$b#...I am not really sure what to think of that.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "I've seen many amazing ice sculptures done by the folks in the valley.#$b#It's always nice to see peoples ideas come to life.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "...I wonder if the people I got presents for will like them...",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "There's not that much to do here on the island. It is pretty peaceful I must say.#$b#That doesn't mean it gets boring here though! I try to think of fun ways to spice things up now and again, heh.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "I love feeling the warm sand under your feet...whenever I am at a beach I feel right at home.#$b#...Plus you can make fun sand castles!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "My brother built this little relaxation area for everyone!$1#$b#He's very talented with woodworking and anything related to plants and such.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.003": "Ah, hello, @!$1#$b#I like to sit at the beach and listen to the calm waves of the water. It never fails to give me inspirations for new songs.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.004": "Cawyn is a dear friend of mine. He's been around for quite a bit.#$b#My brother likes to bring him fresh fruits of his orchard now and again.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.005": "Oh! I love when my brother takes some time for himself.$1#$b#Of course he's a people person so he still wants to be around people, hehe!#$b#Can't complain tho. I do enjoy these gatherings myself.#$b#Do you have gatherings like these back in town as well?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.enchantedforest.000": "My brother put up this cart! I thought it was a nice idea to have a place where people can get fresh flowers without the need to tear them all out of the ground.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.enchantedforest.001": "We grow all our crops locally. The climate on this island is really nice to get a good variety and everything else we take from the ocean.#$b#My brother is really good in taking care of everything, I admire him a lot.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.orchard.000": "My big brother is always so diligent and thoughtful. He often believes to not be enough and lacking competence but I am looking up to him.#$b#I hope he one day realizes that he's always been a great guy. I'm really happy to call him my big brother!$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Mermaid.Schedule.Dialogue.library.000": ".........................#$b#...ah. Hm, sorry, I was kind of spacing out.$7#$b#...the library is open to anyone so I hope you'll find something that will interest you. I often come here to read the books myself.",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//==== COOLGAL =================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Gifttastes.Love": "Oh? You actually brought me something quite interesting, thank you~$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Gifttastes.Like": "Many thanks! I'll make sure to find good use for it.$5",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Huh...could've sworn you actually liked me. Guess I guessed wrong.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Gifttastes.Hate": "...............................$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Well, at least I can use it for throwing it against Joja Marts walls.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Oh! So you're into dumpster diving too, huh?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "*--/#!$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Thanks, but no thanks.  You should save that one for someone who's interested in  that kind of thing.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Not sure why you'd think to give me  this...take it to someone who's into that kinda stuff.$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Sorry, not today. I've got some other kind of heist planned~$5",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Hm...I wonder if I'll get mossy hair if I go out in that green rain...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, it's over already! I need to make sure to try it out next time, hehe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "So. Turns out that you CAN dye your hair with this odd rain, but...guess there's some sort of side effects, huh.$7",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.StardropTea": "Radical! This stuff is awesome.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.OceanFlaxCloth": "Awesome! This'll go nice with my new pants! Just need to add some personal touches once I've sewn the shirt...radical!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.PowderPinkPearl": "What a great gift! Thank you, @! I'll be turning this baby into some awesome jewelry.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.PinkMermaidScale": "Oh~! Let me know if you find more of these! I think I can make some great outfit out of em!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.PastelCottonCandy": "Hell yeah! I love Cotton Candy! That used to be my nickname when I was little actually, haha!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.RoseCandy": "Radical! The scent is lovely and the taste is sweet!",
	
	// MOVIE REACTIONS 
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Spring0.Before": "Hm, I'm not really into these kinda movies.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Spring0.During": "%Bernadette seems to look pretty disinterested.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Spring0.After": "...yeah, appreciate you inviting me and spending time with yout but this wasn't my thing.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Spring1.Before": "Hm, this looks pretty interesting. Let's see how they execute it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Spring1.During": "...huh, the more you know.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Spring1.After": "Actually, I quite liked this movie,@. Thanks for spending time with me!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Summer0.Before": "Ah, I've played the game before. Didn't know it had a movie adaption.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Summer0.During": "%It's not what Bernadettes expressions are right now, it's too dark to see.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Summer0.After": "...it was alright. There were parts I'd have loved to be done differently though.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Summer1.Before": "Hm! Now this is an interesting story, a bit odd tho.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Summer1.During": "...huh?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Summer1.After": "Gotta be honest...all in all an okay movie but nothing I'd go out to pick if there's other movies.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Fall0.Before": "Oooh! I love story! Gotta ask if I can take a movie poster home, it's really hitting my vibe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Fall0.During": "%Bernadette is on the edge of her seat, immersed into the movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Fall0.After": "I loved it! Yoba, these kinda movies are really my thing! Thank you for inviting me!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Fall1.Before": "Have you seen the poster for the movie? Ohh, this looks really radical!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Fall1.During": "%Bernadette is intensely watching the movie, almost forgetting to eat her snacks.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Fall1.After": "I love it! Actually, I think I might go another time I really wanna pick up on all the underlying hints and everything of the story!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Winter0.Before": "Hm, this movie has potential. What do you think, @?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Winter0.During": "%Bernadette looks like she isn't sure what to think of the movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Winter0.After": "All in all...it was alright. Personally tho I think I really gotta be in the right mind place for this, like, when I reeeally wanna get all that pent-up sadness out or something.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Winter1.Before": "Hm...$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Winter1.During": "%Bernadette looks distracted.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.MoviesReactions.Winter1.After": "...I know it's a classic but there's so many other great movies out there, sorry. It's just not my thing. Thanks for the invite tho.",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.Introduction": "My! now, who's this radical dude?$5#$b#Hi there! the name's Bernadette.",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Hm? You actually got me a birthday present? Thank you!$1",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Thanks, buddy! This is such a great birthday gift.",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "It's nice of you to remember my birthday, @.",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Rad, thank you for this birthday gift.",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm...is this some kind of sick joke to you?$2",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "...yeah, no. @, you can actually shove it.$2",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Well, you tried so there's that.",
	"Bernadette.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Uh, hm, well....$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_CoolGalBernadette": "Swell! Thanks for inviting me!$5",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.spring_1": "Spring's here and with the first little saplings growing so is my need for causing a little mischief, hehe!$5",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.summer_1": "Summer is one of the seasons I enjoy the most. That's why I like this island so much.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.fall_1": "With fall comes change, how has the year been treating you this far, @?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.winter_1": "One of the favorite things I like to do in winter is be out all day building snowmen and throwing snowballs to then later go to the bathhouse and enjoy a hot, steaming bath. Maybe even jump into the snow afterwards~.$5",
	
	//DIALOGUE 0 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon": "Hey, there! Anything I can help  you with?#$b#You seem like a new face so I figured you may need some help around here.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue": "Great to see you  again! Got any sand in your shoes yet?#$b#I jest. The sand on this island is really soft and nice not like having it in your shoes would be that bad anyway, hehe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed": "Have you visited the Quarry yet?#$b#There's some really neat gems out there if you got the right tools. I often see Barnabas go there and mine some for his  work and to grind up some to make dye.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu": "Point Melodia is a great place to relax.#$b#Sometimes even Merchants hang out there to sell some goods if you're interested in that.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri": "It's Friday! Gotta get down on Friday~#$b#Everybody's looking forward to the weekend.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat": "How's the farm life going? Hope you're taking some time  off now and again, don't want you fainting in the wild after all.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun": "A new week is about to start, let's see what it holds your us.#$b#What's your plan for the week?",
	
	//DIALOGUE 2 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon2": "I put the 'cute' in execute.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue2": "I asked Barnabas if  he could craft me some good slingshots but he questioned my motivations for acquiring some.#$b#I promised him to not blow up too much.$5",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed2": "There's nothing wrong with a little bit of chaos.  Running around causing some harmless mischief keeps everyone on their feet, hehe.#$b#Don't worry, I usually don't bother those who don't take well to these kind of jokes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu2": "I've been to Gotoro before...$4#$b#...I won't  get into details but it sure is 'something'.$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri2": "Hey, @. Fancy seeing you around, hope the island has been treating you well so far.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat2": "The  other day I stood at the pier lost in thought when Barnabas came around asking if I was fine. That silly little guy is always so concerned about everyones well-being.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun2": "I've been on the hunt for more patches for my jacket lately. I might make a few on my own though.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 4 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon4": "I've come around a lot of places, it's fun to travel the world. Though when I visited this place for the first time I fell in love  with it, that's why I  stayed.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue4": "I've met a girl once who everyone just called 'Food Gal'. She shared some of her recipes with me and I taught her a few 'this and  that's that I know. Like how to make bombs.#$b#Don't be alarmed, it was just the firework type of bombs, hehe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed4": "While I can fall asleep anywhere I do enjoy sleeping in a big bed. I toss  around quite abit in my sleep after all.#$b#I guess it's  still  some pent-upenergy from the day.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu4": "I like to play on my phone sometimes. Gacha games are pretty addicting but I do know how to keep my money.#$b#There's no  harm in  occasionally playing, right?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri4": "I enjoy going to the library pretty often. The librarian there is fun to talk to, she has a lot to share!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat4": "Have you ever thought about dropping everything in your life to run away to start somewhere new?#$b#Ah, silly thing to ask  you, @. You're probably a prime example for new beginnings, right?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun4": "Believe it or not but  I used to work for the government for a short while in my early  adulthood. It got pretty  boring after  a while and I didn't agree how things were handled.#$b#My boss wasn't too fond of me, but I do miss my colleagues sometimes. We still text each other regularly.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 6 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon64": "Hey, @! How's the farm life going? Came here to enjoy the island life for a while?#$b#One of these days I should really show you my favorite spots here.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue6": "When my dad was still around he'd always take me on little trips on his motorcycle. I really enjoyed these rides a lot.#$b#The close bond I had with him is something I treasure to this day.$1#$b#He's one of the main influences that shaped how I live my life today.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed6": "Believe it or not but I do enjoy the occasional tear-jerker movie. Even with a bad boy image I think it should be fine to show your vulnerable side now and again, don't you think?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu6": "Weekend is approaching, got any plans?#$b#I do like to take some trip to Point Memoria and check out what the merchant there has to offer. They come once a month since the traveling time for them is said to be really long....or so I've heard.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri6": "I've heard a few things about this island that makes staying here even more interesting. Have you ever heard the old tale of the late king of the merfolk, Llyr?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat6": "Saturdays are for bad decisions. You're free of the week and got some fun freetime to spend.#$b#Whereas Sundays are for regrets and sobering up after your silly ideas, hehe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun6": "Thought I'd do something silly? Nah, I stand by my words.#$b#If I pull a stupid stunt then I accept the consequences. Not that anything happened though, just for the record.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 8 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon8": "What's crackin'?#$b#I've been going around places to check out some locations for possible gigs. Not for now, but it never hurts having your stuff ready anytime, right?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue8": "I've been going through my old mans records lately. He really was onto something way back then.#$b#Never thought I'd feel so close to him again after his passing.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed8": "I'm brainstorming a few song titles right now.#$b#'My blood-curled screams keeping you up at night' and 'It's 3am time to annihilate my last few brain-cells are at the top spots right now.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu8": "I've seen people buy some shirt and throw it away after a few wears, what's up with that?#$b#If I find some holes in my clothes I turn it into a statement. Ripped jeans can only be rad when they were artificially torn? Ain't no way!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri8": "A couple of days ago Barnabas stopped by and brought me some nice crushed minerals.#$b#They're really great to make paint or make-up actually! He's always so kind.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat8": "Good day to you, @. Out here running some errands or enjoying the moment right now?#$b#For me it's a mix of both. Doesn't hurt taking a step back for a bit while you happen to be outside. Keeps you from going crazy, haha!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun8": "I've been wondering what genre to pursuit. On one side I do enjoy Funeral Doom Metal but Neoclassical Metal is nice too. Then again Symphonic Metal also has a really nice ring to it considering how ephemeral it can sound...$3#$b#On certain days I am more of a Blackened Doom kinda girlie tho. Hm...#$b#...Industrial is also nice....Mathcore too...$4",
	
	//DIALOGUE 10 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon10.1": "Mondays, eh?#$b#I woke up today and stumbled through my boat on my way to get something to drink. Knocked over half of the things on my way.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon10.2": "Mondays, eh?#$b#I just stepped outta my boat earlier and almost slipped on a fish. How did it get onto the pier? Beats me. Fact is that I almost swan-diven into the waters.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon10.3": "Mondays, eh?#$b#Some parrots just flew over my head and hit me with a mango. I appreciate the gesture, mangoes are delicious but...what the heck?$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon10.4": "Mondays, eh?#$b#I just ripped my favorite pair of tights. They just had the right amount of holes and now....they're JUST holes. UGH!$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Mon10.5": "Mondays, eh?#$b#I was practicing my guitar riffs and when I was shredding real nice one of the strings snapped. Almost got into my eye.$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue10.1": "Hey,@! Guess what!#$b#I just found another metal genre I got interested in! Sometimes you just want that itch in your head be blasted away by sick riffs and screams.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue10.2": "Hey,@! Guess what!#$b#I talked to Barnabas earlier and he showed me something underwater that made noises really fitting into a metal song. I might try to get a waterproof mic to record it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue10.3": "Hey,@! Guess what!#$b#There's actually quite some genres outside of metal I enjoy listening to. Sometimes you need something more somber that goes into Gothic, like the band 'The Theriac'! Richard Forger just knows how to fill your melancholic heart.", //This is a lame play on the band The Cure with lead singer Robert Smith
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue10.4": "Hey,@! Guess what!#$b#I met Caitríona earlier and she actually smiled at me! ...yes, I am pretty sure it was a smile. Alright, maybe a little smirk. For her that means a lot ok? It's all about the micro-expressions with her.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Tue10.5": "Hey,@! Guess what!#$b#I just saw a huge shadow deep in the water. I know there's mermaids and alike around but....it's the first time I saw something of that size! Whales don't go so close to land so I wonder what it was...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed10.1": "...when the sky breaks open and forth bursts a flood of tears,crumbling dreams torn apart by doubts and fears, huh....#$b#...oh! Sorry, @, I didn't notice you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed10.2": "...I tried to run yet here I am, tried to forget yet the same thoughts in my head again and again....#$b#...oh! Sorry, @, I didn't notice you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed10.3": "Bloody rivers, tears of fear, countless shivers, doom is near-...hm. ...Endless loop of deprivation, nothing new besides an amalgamation of-....#$b#...oh! Sorry, @, I didn't notice you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed10.4": "Let the water flow, you know you can't stop it anyway, be true to yourself or-no... ...Broken, unbroken, unravel in fear, forget what's been taken your end is near....#$b#...oh! Sorry, @, I didn't notice you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Wed10.5": "Show me your teeth, I wanna see how you bite, there's nothing deeper underneath if you- Ugh! ...It's now or never, you're running out of time, if there's nothing you can reach then a helping hand will be fine...#$b#...oh! Sorry, @, I didn't notice you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu10.1": "I had a dream last night, @. It was rather odd...#$b#...I was stranded on a rather desolated island ironically enough. It wasn't lush or exciting like this place though. There were no plants, no trees...only sand and stone.#$b#When I tried exploring I always got this uneasy feeling that I wasn't alone, but I never saw anyone. I woke up before anything happened, but now I am wondering why I was dreaming about something like this.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu10.2": "I had a dream last night, @. It was rather odd...#$b#...I sat in a mountain of skulls deep inside a dark cave. It smelled of sulfur and something else I couldn't quite put my finger on.#$b#As I tried climbing down this big mountain of skulls I found myself rather clumsy and now looking back at it...the skulls felt awfully small...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu10.3": "I had a dream last night, @. It was rather odd...#$b#...the sky was red and the ground an awful gray color as if all the color was sucked out of it. Trees withered and no one around...#$b#...even when I tried finding anyone it felt like I was all alone. When I reached the forest something seemed off...that's when I noticed the shadow of something HUGE behind me...that's when I woke up, damn!" ,
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu10.4": "I had a dream last night, @. It was rather odd...#$b#...the sound of string instruments and bagpipes...? The familiar feeling, no, maybe nostalgia? It's hard to say...#$b#...I don't remember anything visual, only the sounds and the feelings I had...something sad must've happened.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Thu10.5": "I had a dream last night, @. It was rather odd...#$b#...I heard the laughter of a child and the voice of a man. It felt pretty normal until-...you know how in a movie when all the music and stuff suddenly dies down and it feels like everyone is staring at you? Yeah, kinda like that.#$b#...well, it got all dark and it felt like I was stuck in quicksand. When I tried struggling free I heard the same child from before crying....that's when I woke up.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri10.1": "You know what would be a fun idea?#b#I take one of the old joja carts and you get inside while I take your tractor to drive around the forest pulling you behind me.#$b#Hm? That's actually pretty dangerous? Alright, fine. Then let's use the cart to drive down from the Northern Cliffs!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri10.2": "You know what would be a fun idea?#b#We climb onto the giant petrified tree back at the quarry and spray-paint a huge mural on top it!#$b#Hm? What? That would be vandalizing a deeply cultural spot? Hm, you're probably right. Let's go into town and spray-paint Lewis' mansion instead!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri10.3": "You know what would be a fun idea?#b#Jumping down into the water from the Northern Cliffs! We could even try out parachuting!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri10.4": "You know what would be a fun idea?#b#Barnabas showed my a spot with some geysers. We could take a small boat and put it on top to blast upwards!#$b#Huh? Too dangerous? Ah, right...geysers can be quite hot.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Fri10.5": "You know what would be a fun idea?#b#We should have a little gig at the Northern Cliffs! Could even make some snacks and stuff and jam out with some sick guitar riffs!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat10.1": "I went to the library a couple of days ago and got a pretty interesting book to read.#$b#'10,000,000 colors and every color you may can't see'. It's a bit odd to read when the pictured colors are the ones you, in fact, cannot see. Curse these human eyes.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat10.2": "I went to the library a couple of days ago and got a pretty interesting book to read.#$b#It talks about different types of mermaid scales and it's usage. Seems like Mermaids regularly shed them like when you lose old hair.#$b#Most of these informations come directly from mermaids themselves, at least according to this book, hm.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat10.3": "I went to the library a couple of days ago and got a pretty interesting book to read.#$b#'Roachard, Beeanca and other fun names for your pet'. These are all very creative! I was thinking about maybe taking in one of the ferrets at the Northern Cliffs and name them something fun like that, hehe!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat10.4": "I went to the library a couple of days ago and got a pretty interesting book to read.#$b#'Hot stuff and how to handle the responsibility of not caving in to eating them too fast'. Well, the title is a bit misleading but...it's really worth a read!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sat10.5": "I went to the library a couple of days ago and got a pretty interesting book to read.#$b#This books story is about a young child having to take on too much responsibility because of the loss of their parents. What a tragic story, I hope it'll have a good outcome.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun10.1": "I went and tidied up my ship today! You'd never guess what I found amongst all of my stuff.#$b#Several knives in varying sizes! Among them a Classic Bowie, two pressing daggers, a kukri, a filleting knife, several dozen wood carving ones that I totally need to give back to Barnabas...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun10.2": "I went and tidied up my ship today! You'd never guess what I found amongst all of my stuff.#$b#...some cat ears. I really don't know where those come from. I'm more of a rat type.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun10.3": "I went and tidied up my ship today! You'd never guess what I found amongst all of my stuff.#$b#A prismatic shard and some Qi gems. Really don't know where those came from, I might bring them to Barnabas, maybe he can incorporate them into his art.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun10.4": "I went and tidied up my ship today! You'd never guess what I found amongst all of my stuff.#$b#What feels like a years worth of torn tights. Can you believe it? To top it of they're in all the colors of the rainbows!#$b#I should wear them more, most times I pick black ones.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.Sun10.5": "I went and tidied up my ship today! You'd never guess what I found amongst all of my stuff.#$b#It's apparently an 'error item', whatever that means. Looks like a do-not-enter sign to me. Onto the wall it goes!",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "I do enjoy festivities like the Egg festival. It always reminds me of my childhood.#$b#My mother always brought dyes to paint the eggs ourself. It was a lot of fun activities, I miss those times...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Hm, the I've seen the flower dance of  Pelican town quite a few times by now but it's not too much  of  my thing. I prefer circle pits and headbanging.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "A day about eating food and enjoying the warm weather? Count me in! Can't wait to try this years food.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "Calliope has told me a few times what kind of things jellyfish talk about. Quite interesting creatures they are.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "I remember the last time I visited the fair. I snuck in a few rotten eggs to Pierre's stand. Since then I am laying a bit low, hehe.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "I love everything spooky. With Spirit's Eve approaching I use  the time to cook up some silly tricks I can play on the others.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "When winter approaches I take the time to visit the Valley to enjoy the snow.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "I'm not too sappy a person but the festival is quite nice to experience. Plus there's food so it's a win-win.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "...radical. Scoot over though, I need more space to sleep.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "What a nice morning for some tomfoolery.#$b#You think I can ask Barnabas for some fresh pigments?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "You ever thought about how everything in your life falls into place and you're in a really good spot but somehow there's something gnawing in the back of your head telling you something is wrong?#$b#No? Just me? Alright.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.003": "...I've been thinking bout giving Joja Mart a fresh coat of paint. Where you think would be the nearest one be? Might be time for a little traveling.#$b#I'll show you a few tags I did in the past, let's brainstorm.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.004": "I wonder if I can get this boat to go all the way back to Pelican Town.#$b#Hm? Oh, you're probably right. My arms will give out before I reach the shore, huh. I'll take ol' Betsy instead.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.005": "A cleaver is a girls best friend, didn't you know?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Bernadette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.006": "Love the hangouts on Sunday. We all got busy schedules for one reason or another. So if we don't see each other during the week this is the latest we can chat and have a good time.",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//==== PIRATELAD ===============================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Gifttastes.Love": "Hm...this is actually pretty nice.#$b#...$2#$b#...thank you for thinking of me.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Gifttastes.Like": "Thanks. I think I'll have some use for this.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Gifttastes.Dislike": "...#$b#...$1#$b#...well, I don't really know why you're giving me useless stuff like this...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Gifttastes.Hate": "...why did I even think you'd actually give me something nice? Am I your garbage can?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Uh...I guess...I should say 'thank you' at this point?#$b#...well. You gotta wait this one one, buddy.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Well. I trust in you really just taking things that are a waste to be thrown out and not-...anyway. Bye.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "...I've got a saber and a pistol. Just saying.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Sorry, I'm not really in the mood to watch anything. I've got a scheduled self-loathing evening in front of me.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.GreenRain": "The world is weird...can't really say if it's in a good or bad way.#$b#It's just....really weird. Sigh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "A fleeting moment...just like spending time with your loved ones.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Yet again I stand here wondering what is going on.#$b#...the way it changes for just one day is oddly soothing though. Like a wild child stepping into your life to kiss you on the cheek to just disappear into the night without giving you their name...sigh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.StardropTea": "Are you sure? ah, thank you. It tastes lovely...$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.bloodstainedrose": "This rose...it reminds me of long gone days...#$b#Thanks, @. I'll keep it safe with me.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.PowderOrangePearl": "This pearl has a really nice luster. I shall add it to my collections. Many thanks, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MossyMermaidScale": "Mermaids shed their scaled regularly. It's not too different from when skin lakes or hair falls out. Nature taking it's course.#$b#Either way...thank you, @. This one has a really nice tint.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.BloodstainedRoseTea": "Tea with a special blend...it has a sweet scent yet bitter undertones.#$b#Thank you, I quite enjoyed it.",
	
	// MOVIE REACTIONS 
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Spring0.Before": "Hey, @. Thanks for the invite.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Spring0.During": "%Caitríona is silently watching the movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Spring0.After": "Hm...I can relate to the sapling. Though it's not usually the genre I watch.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Spring1.Before": "@...I saw the movie poster earlier. I hope it's as good as what the advertisement says.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Spring1.During": "%Caitríona seems engaged and is intensely listening to the movie, silently nodding to herself.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Spring1.After": "I quite enjoyed this movie. Thank you kindly for inviting me to it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Summer0.Before": "...huh. It says it's a videogame adaption. @, have you heard of it before?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Summer0.During": "%It's hard to make out what Caitríona must be thinking.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Summer0.After": "...not sure about the source material but the movie was alright.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Summer1.Before": "I have seen the children walk around with these Wumbus toys before. Are you still a child at heart, @?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Summer1.During": "%Caitríona is looking more towards the children enjoying the movie than actually watching it. Though there does a rare smile hush over her face.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Summer1.After": "...not quite my taste but it is indeed a good movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Fall0.Before": "Thank you for the invite, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Fall0.During": "%Caitríona is silently watching the movie, she tilts her head now and again as if wanting to ask something but remains silent.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Fall0.After": "...not sure what to think about it. It has it's charm but...hm.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Fall1.Before": "Hm...$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Fall1.During": "%Caitríona doesn't seem to pay too much attention to the movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Fall1.After": "...what's out on the sea can be much scarier. I do not like to be reminded though, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Winter0.Before": "...a family movie?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Winter0.During": "%Caitríona does not pay attention.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Winter0.After": ".................$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Winter1.Before": "A classic. Wise choice, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Winter1.During": "%Caitríona is engrossed into the movie.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.MoviesReactions.Winter1.After": "Thanks for inviting me,@. I quite enjoyed it.",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Introduction": "...#$b#...$1#$b#...?#$b#...ah? You're actually talking to me? Hm...good day to you too, I guess. The name is Caitríona...",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Huh? You actually remembered my birthday? And you even got me something nice...#$b#Ah, sorry. It's just-...it's been a while.",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "This is...for me? Ah...thank you, @.#$b#It's a really nice gift.",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Ah, I didn't think anyone would even remember it...thank you, @.",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "A birthday gift? Oh...#$b#...thanks for thinking of me, @.",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm.#$b#...$1#$b#...mhm...no.#$b# You come in here, on my birthday, giving me this-...you call that a 'gift'...I see.#$b#Well, I don't.$3",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "%Caitríona looks at you with disgust and a hint of disappointment.",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Hm, well, alright. I appreciate you thinking of me at least...",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "You tried...that's all that matters...you tried.",
	"Caitriona.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_PirateLadCaitrionaOFlannagain": "You actually want to watch a movie with me? Ah...sure, why not? That...actually sounds nice right now.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.spring_1": "Spring is the time where life comes back from the cold clutches of winter...#$b#A fresh new start, eh?#$b#...$1#$b#...what are your plans for the new year, @?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.summer_1": "Summer is a time most look forward to. Do you as well, @?#$b#...the sweltering heat while you roam the sea...sometimes I miss it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.fall_1": "Harvest season is approaching...are you prepared?#$b#They say it's the time where the lines of the living and the dead start to blur as well...#$b#...I wonder if I might-...ah, never mind.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.winter_1": "The season of frost and death they say...I do not hold much ill thought about this season. However, the uniform whiteness and lack of foliage depresses me...so I stay in warmer climates to avoid it.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 0 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Mon": "...#$b#...$1#$b#...what do you want?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Tue": "...#$b#...sigh. Alright, I'll bite. What is it?#$b#Hm. Well...I guess talking to people isn't all that bad.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Wed": "...#$b#...$2#$b#...well, since you're here already, did you know that pirates actually don't bury their treasure? I'm not too sure where that came from but...never have I ever met one that buries all of their treasure.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Thu": "...#$b#...hm. @, what would you say if you were able to meet the people you miss the most but are long gone already?#$b#Ah, no real, uh, reason why I'm asking...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Fri": "What do you usually do on a Friday?#$b#I tend to stand at the docks and just blankly stare into the distance. It's really eye opening.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sat": "...#$b#...hm. I took a stroll the other day.#$b#...I saw Barnabas on his knees rummaging around some pile of stones.#$b#I wonder what he was up to...hm? I should've just asked him? No...I don't know.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sun": "Sunday is the day people usually look forward to the most, right?#$b#Hm...what have you planned for the day?",
	
	// DIALOGUE 2 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Mon2": "...#$b#...ah. Hello, @. I've not really got any witty thing to say today, sorry.#$b#...#$b#...well, nice to see you though.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Tue2": "Ah...@. Nice to see you.#$b#...$2#$b#Have you been to the library yet? There's a few interesting books there that might be of your interest.#$b#If not....I could show you the way there, maybe...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Wed2": "I've talked to Bernadette the other day...#$b#...she told me Barnabas would give her some gem dust now and again to make paint.#$b#...I get the idea but...all those gems, hm...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Thu2": "Another bright and sunny day...#$b#...$2#$b#...sorry, was I staring too much?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Fri2": "...#$b#...$1#$b#...do you think being a worm would be cool? Surely life would at least be easier...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sat2": "Bernadette brought me a new feather the other day.#$b#...I like to write with one, you know? Hm, maybe I'll show you some of my stuff at some point...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sun2": "Another week passed. Was it better than the last? Who knows...but seeing you did brighten my day.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 4 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Mon4": "...#$b#...hey, @. Have you ever wondered if you're actually doing something with your life?#$b#Hm, well...I was wondering about going out again. Been so long I've hidden myself here, y'know?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Tue4": "I was in the forest earlier. Just laying in the grass watching the clouds as one does.#$b#There was a cloud that reminded me of you, thought I'd let you know.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Wed4": "Been sorting through my old stuff the other day. I've found many old things from my old crew...$1#$b#...didn't think it would hit that hard. You think it'll get better one day?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Thu4": "I'm not really sure what to do today.#$b#Sometimes it's really hard to get out of bed so once you pulled that off you're left wondering what to do now.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Fri4": "I often tell myself that 'now' is the time to finally change things but then I just do nothing after all.#$b#You think there's some way to break through this cycle?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sat4": "Sorry, seems that I always rely on you lately.#$b#It's just...it feels so easy to talk to you somehow.#$b#When I talk to you things feel easier to pull off for some reason.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sun4": "Hey, @. How is the day going?#$b#...I think I might be ready to go among some people again soon.#$b#Well, I am with people on here right now but...you know what I mean.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 6 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Mon6": "Do you think there's life after death? Or maybe...ghosts...?#$b#...is it foolish of me to secretly hope there's a way to meet my crew one last time?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Tue6": "A sunny day gives a sunny mind. However, a rainy day makes ones wounds break open again...#$b#...thanks for always checking on me, @. It really means a lot to me.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Wed6": "Do you think we could hang out more often? Maybe I could show you my old ship at some point, that would be nice.#$b#I think...we've come to know each other to such a degree it feels like I can let you in more and, uh...#$b#...tell you a bit of what I used to be up to.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Thu6": "Can you believe that I used to be such a wild child?#$b#My crew always said I was thick-headed and set on my ways of handling things.#$b#...$1#$b#...maybe that's what cost them their lives...$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Fri6": "You think using my treasure to restore my ship could be a good way to work through things?#$b#I wonder...Barnabas is really good with working with all kinds of tools and materials....maybe I could ask him for some tips.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sat6": "I tell you, once I restore my ship we shall go on a grand sail around the island.#$b#Hm? Nah, not my lil boat. My actual ship is quite a bit bigger, that'll be much more fun.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sun6": "Sunday arrives yet again, but somehow I feel a bit more secure about my future.#$b#Maybe it's thanks to your influence, who knows.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 8 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Mon8": "@, my good buddy. It's good to see you.#$b#You think you got some time to spare later today? I got some writing to show you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Tue8": "You know, flowers aren't particularly my thing but a rose with a deep red color...now that tickles my fancy.#$b#It might be old-school but it reminds me of thee good old times.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Wed8": "You wanna know how I lost my eye?#$b#I tell you, it was a deep sea creature I fought tooth and nails with my crew. It almost got the ship but I shot it on time.#$b#It did grab me though, yeah. I can still shoot like I used to so whatever.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Thu8": "The hat always stays on. Would I really be a captain if I wasn't wearing this hat?#$b#Hm...am I even a captain when I don't have a crew?$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Fri8": "I've picked up knife throwing again.#$b#You don't happen to have some spare time later today, do you? Totally unrelated to what I stated just now.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sat8": "Always a sight to see, @.#$b#What brings you here today? I was just about to go grab my stuff and go to the Quarry for some ore. Barnabas actually agreed to showing me how to get some good stuff.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sun8": "Is it me or do the birds sing sweeter, the flowers smell  greater, the-...oh, am I coming down with some kinda flu?",
	
	//DIALOGUE 10 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Mon10": "%Caitríona looks away when your eyes meet.#$b#Hey there, @. Didn't think you'd come to me at this hour. Good to see you though.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Tue10": "I love watching your expressions.#$b#For example, when you're in deep thought you have this slight pout I really like. Makes me want to pinch your cheek.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Wed10": "Do you think I could steal you away for a little while?#$b#...nothing....important. I'd just like to have you for myself for a little while.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Thu10": "There's times when I feel down and wonder if what I do is right or if it actually matters.#$b#Then you come around and it feels like every worry just melts away.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Fri10": "You think you'll come to the hangout on Sunday? I'm sure it'll be fun when you're around.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sat10": "On the possibility of me getting a ship again...I wonder what I should name it this time...maybe you can brainstorm with me when the time comes?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.Sun10": "Even I believe in Sundays being a day one should use to relax and take a step back and reflect.#$b#...having company just sweetens it even more.",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "Walking around all day to find some eggs in the bushes and stuff, sure is something. I prefer my smoked fish though.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Time for the flower dance again, huh? Dancing ain't my thing but I hope you'll have some fun.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "Hm, I m almost tempted to go and see what nice food the townsfolk is dishing up tomorrow.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "Oh yeah, it's time for the jellies again, right? Don't miss out on it, it sure is a spectacle to behold.#$b#We might be spoiled here though since Calliope and Barnabas can just have the jellies dance around whenever they want.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "The fairs in again tomorrow, right? Ah, it tickles me to try out the fun games they have.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "With Spirit's Eve approaching I've been wondering if maybe there will be some actual ghosts...that surely would spice things up.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "Have fun fishing in the cold tomorrow. Ain't no way you can get me into the snow.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "Ah, it's that time of the year again, hm? Fancy telling me who you got this year?#$b#Don't worry, I won't do anything. I'm just curious what you'd get them.",
	"Festivals.FlowerDance.Caitriona": "...well, I thought I'd go to the flower dance at least since...it reminds me of good times. You made me curious after all.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Huh. I'll turn around again and pretend you're not here.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "...you better turn around while I change or else we gotta have a problem, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "...#$b#...there's things I want...hm.#$b#...sometimes it's hard to get them anywhere you can reach normally.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.003": "Smoked fish is the best. it lasts long and you can season it in many ways so it doesn't get boring.#$b#...I used to eat it a lot when I was still actively sailing the seas.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Caitriona.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.004": "Ah...I tend to be a loner but...#$b#...Barnabas has his way of convincing people.#$b#...#$b#...well, it's not too bad.",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== SEADUDE ==================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Gifttastes.Love": "Wait! You're giving this to ME?$2#$b#Thank you so much, I love it!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Gifttastes.Like": "Gasp! You're giving this to me? Thank you!$3",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Aw...barnacles.$7",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Gifttastes.Hate": "Why...are you giving this to me?$8",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Hm, oh! Let's bet I gonna find some use for this.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Creative! Make sure to not waste anything but keep in mind to stay safe!#$b#You never know what others throw away.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Why did you do this...?$2",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "I'm sorry...yeah....no...well. Not this time, @.$8",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Rain! And it's green!$1#$b#While a lot of people tend to get really weirded out or scared about the unknown I do enjoy something new and get curious wanting to get to know about it more! Believe me that it's completely natural fearing what you do not know and don't worry I am here to keep you safe in case something odd might happen!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "See? Nothing to worry about!$1#$b#Now if you excuse me I gonna grab all the moss that I can get to make some really comfortable beds for the great guys at the Orchard!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Another time of green rain!#$b#Collecting the rain water actually gave me a good basis for some nice tea, can you believe it?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.StardropTea": "Holy Red Snapper! Where did you get this, it's great!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MermaidsDelight": "Gasp! That's for  me?$1#$b#Thank you so much, @! I usually eat pretty healthy but now and again I do crave a little sugar rush and this is really hitting it, heh!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.StarlightFruit": "One of my favorite fruits to eat! Especially in the summer heat I do enjoy them sliced or as sorbet! Thank you so much!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.petrichor": "When I was small my dad took me to a spot where these grew everywhere. Any time I see them they remind me of that time.#$b#Thank you, @!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.PowderGreenPearl": "I do like all pearls but the ones with a green tint I love the most!#$b#Thank you for thinking of me, @.",
	
	// MOVIE REACTIONS 
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Spring0.Before": "@! Thank you so much for inviting me!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Spring0.During": "%Barnabas seems to enjoy this movie a lot.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Spring0.After": "It was great! That brave little sapling is such a strong guy!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Spring1.Before": "Thank you for inviting me, @! I can't wait to see the movie!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Spring1.During": "%Barnabas is intensely watching the movie, occasionally looking over to you when something he think is cool comes up.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Spring1.After": "I liked watching the movie! There were so many interesting things, maybe I gonna try and film some stuff underwater too to make a movie like that!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Summer0.Before": "I am here and I am ready to watch a movie with you!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Summer0.During": "%Barnabas is a bit lost in the plot but seems interested enough to not get distracted.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Summer0.After": "Huh, not sure what this was about but the story was nice.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Summer1.Before": "I can't wait to watch the movie, @! Thank you for asking me to come along!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Summer1.During": "%Barnabas is enjoying the movie quite a bit.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Summer1.After": "I liked that little Wumbus guy! Maybe I gonna get one of those soft ones they sell.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Fall0.Before": "@! Thanks for inviting me!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Fall0.During": "%Barnabas appears to be confused about the movie plot.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Fall0.After": "Huh, I didn't really get it. It was quite an interesting movie though! Even if I don't understand it I can appreciate the work that was put into it.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Fall1.Before": "Heard this one is kind of scary, I'm looking forward to it!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Fall1.During": "%Barnabas' reactions are honest and rather obvious but he appears to enjoy the movie. Despite clinging to you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Fall1.After": "Wow! I did quite like it! Reminds me of the deep sea and it's inhabitants in a way.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Winter0.Before": "It's a movie about a ranch! ...I think? Well, I tend to not read the synopsis to keep the surprise going, heheh!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Winter0.During": "%Barnabas is thoroughly enjoying the movie, openly sobbing at the sad parts.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Winter0.After": "Ugh! This was sooo good! Thank you so much for inviting me, @!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Winter1.Before": "@! Over here! I can't wait to see the movie!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Winter1.During": "%Barnabas watches happily, nomming his snacks.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.MoviesReactions.Winter1.After": "...wow! This was really good, @. Did you enjoy it as well?",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Introduction": "Hey there! The name's Barnabas and when it comes to anything related to Woodwork, Metallurgy, Gardening, Carpentry-...well! If you need ANYTHING at all just let me know! I really like helping people!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "...! You-!$2#$b#You actually thought of my birthday! -AND you're giving me such a great gift!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "GASP! Thank you so much! I can't believe you're giving me such a great gift on my birthday!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Aw, you thought of me! Thank you a lot, @!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Yay! Birthday gift!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Aw, why would you give this to me...and of all days it had to be today...$8",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "...?#$b#...$7#$b#...man, this is really sad.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Huh, not quite sure what to do with this but...thank you for remembering my birthday!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Hm! Thanks for thinking of me, even if I am not too sure what to do with this...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_SeaDudeBarnabas": "A movie! And you're inviting me! Can I pick the seat?",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.spring_1": "Spring is such a wonderful time of the year! Everything blooms and the bees start getting busy!#$b#It's a great time to get out of the winter blues and clean up your place and welcome the spirit of life into your home!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.summer_1": "Summer! I highly enjoy this season, not just because I live in a tropical climate, hehe!#$b#With the sun shining it's brightest and the clear sky smiling at you it just gives you this fuzzy feeling of joy all around!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.fall_1": "For some fall is a season of change while for others it brings sadness and bleakness.#$b#I do enjoy the leaves changing and harvesting all the crops I have worked so hard for in the previous months.#$b#Don't you think this is the greatest time to share some of your bountiful harvest with the ones you care for?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.winter_1": "Winter isn't just the season of death and the end of the year.#$b#It gives an opportunity to reflect on the past year and huddle up together an enjoy the closeness with your loved ones while the world gets covered in a soft blanket of snow.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 0 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Mon": "Salutations! Have you gotten enough sustenance today?#$b#If not I can guide you to my Orchard and you can have some of the fruits that I am growing.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Tue": "When I think about what I like to the most I cannot decide. There are so many fun and interesting things to do in the world!#$b#Sometimes I want to plant new seeds and till the ground but other times I like crushing boulders with my legs! It's a good workout!#$b#Oh! don't tell anyone but sometimes I like to just sit around in the sun and nibble on some iridium ore. It has a nice flavor, heh!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Wed": "The sky is clear, the sun is shining and my chest is bursting with joy! What a great day! And I get to see you too!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Thu": "I looove finding smooth stone and taking my chisel to free the beauty lying within! When I work with stone to create my piece it is more of me helping the stone be it's best! Like helping a chick break free from it's shell!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Fri": "If you cannot find me anywhere on the island the chances are high I am underwater. I like to make sure that down there everything is in order as well!#$b#...there's some troubles here and there but nothing I cannot deal with!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sat": "Occasionally I will grind some gemstones into dust. They can be used as pigments for either cosmetics or paint. Naturally some of them are not light-fast but I found ways to increase the light-fastness!$1#$b#This way we can use natural ingredients to create something beautiful that will last for generations!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sun": "There's days where I do wonder if I am doing a good job...$7#$b#Calliope always insists that I am doing things well, but I guess it's natural to doubt yourself now and again, right?",
	
	// DIALOGUE 2 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Mon2": "Do you think that the waves of the sea can carry the thought of lost souls to you?#$b#There's so much unknown in the world and I want to believe that even when you lose someone you can somehow reach them. You know...to show them you're doing well and that you still love them...and stuff...$8",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Tue2": "Sometimes I wonder if I've tried hard enough. Life can be hard and responsibilities can bring someone down in one swoop if you're not careful.#$b#@, remember to take things slow and not overwhelm yourself, okay?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Wed2": "It's a nice day, isn't it?#$b#Flowers are blooming, birds are singing...on days like these...someone like you should lay at the beach enjoying a cool drink, @. All work and no relaxation makes for a dull mind after all. ",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Thu2": "Did you know that groups of aquatic life get classified depending on whether they are a single type or mixture of species, or whether they are fish or mammals?#$b#Shrimp, fish or other aquatic creatures swimming together in a loose cluster is what we call a shoal!#$b#A group of the same fish species swimming together is a school, often moving together in synchrony.#$b#Herds of marine mammals is called a pod. Dolphins, whales, walruses and seals count to that!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Fri2": "People always say how calm and silent the ocean is and use the sea as a spot for relaxation.#$b#Did you know though that the ocean can get pretty noisy too?#$b#There are a handful of recorded noises scientists still cannot explain to this day or so I've heard!#$b#They reach from high pitched wails to big bloop sounds. Ah, but...well. I don't want to destroy the beauty of mysteries but some of them are just as simple as an iceberg breaking away from a glacier.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sat2": "There are things in the world one cannot explain. Yet here we are in this odd moment, sharing it together...#$b#Ah...sorry! I was just thinking about a few things and how vast the world is.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sun2": "Hey there! How are you doing today?#$b#I've recently harvested a few crops if you'd like to have something to eat.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 4 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Mon4": "I really enjoy fixing things up! There's just something really fulfilling when you're able to make someones life better!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Tue4": "Salutations!$1#$b#I've went ahead and cleaned up the shores at Point Melodia earlier! There were quite a few flotsam and jetsam scattered around.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Wed4": "Sometimes I get inspired by the most random things.#$b#The other day I was cleaning up the shores and stared at a sea urchin for a while and got a really cool idea for an art installation!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Thu4": "What's up! You're looking especially well-toned today.#$b#Farm-life sure gives a good workout, right?$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Fri4": "One of these days I'd like to restore the house in the forest. We used to spend a lot of good times there, Mom, Dad and I...$8",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sat4": "Shells or no shells....#$b#Hm?#$b#Oh! Hey there, @! I was just thinking about some decorations, how's your day?#$b#Oh? Well, you see, I want to use shells, pearls and some other things to make nice decorations for tables and such. I was asked about it and thought it would be a nice thing to pass time today.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sun4": "Would you believe it when I say that there's mermaids out there bigger than a house?",
	
	//DIALOGUE 6 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Mon6": "Bioluminescence is a fascinating thing. Through a naturally catalyzed chemical reaction organisms can emit light.#$b#Heh, I can do that too but around others I tend not too. Calliope is able to do it as well but for me it's not really fitting since I take more after our dad...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Tue6": "I often find interesting things at the shores. I either use them for my art or turn them into something useful, like clothes and the like.#$b#What I wear right now I found too! Can you believe it?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Wed6": "When it gets dark and the jellies come out it is really a magical place.#$b#They're pretty shy though so you have to be really lucky to find them.#$b#Maybe one of these days I will show you a secret spot where they often come to.$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Thu6": "Caitríona asked me the other day where I found the gems that I use for my pigments and jewellery. I showed her the quarry. There's some underwater spots I find more but they aren't really accessible for land dwellers...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Fri6": "Have you ever wondered if what you do has any meaning? That your 'trying hard' is actually meaning something?$7#$b#...ah, maybe it's just 'one of these days', sorry.$8#$b#I didn't mean to, uh...put your vibe down or anything.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sat6": "A seals skin is slick and really smooth. I really like to pet them because it feels nice.$1#$b#There's some surfaces out there that make me feel all weird and stuff and I don't know why. Makes me want to pull my hand straight away...#$b#...it just gives an ick feeling, you know?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sun6": "Do you got some time later? I'd love to play fetch with you!#$b#It's especially fun in the water!",
	
	//DIALOGUE 8 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Mon8": "@! It's good to see you!$2#$b#I'd love to show you what I've done around the island when you got time. There's some spots I'd especially love to show you!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Tue8": "Would you like to hang out with me later?$1#$b#I could show you what I've been working on and we could brainstorm a few ideas together.#$b#Maybe...I could make something for you as well, if you'd like?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Wed8": "I had this really interesting dream last night.#$b#You were in it and we were underwater, you were helping me with something but I can't remember what it was, hm...#$b#...oh. Um, we also uh, well,...anyway! What was your last dream about?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Thu8": "I am always happy when I get to see you, @! You're such a great person to be around and I love talking to you!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Fri8": "Last night some things broke around the island and I stayed up all night to fix them.#$b#I'm kinda really tired but...I still got so much to do...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sat8": "%Barnabas gives you a warm smile as he juggles several logs of wood and some bags  he carries with his mouth. He seems really eager to see you but whatever he says just comes out as gibberish.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sun8": "You know how sometimes you say you'd like to control the weather...yeah.#$b#There may or may not be people out there who can actually do that.#$b#Well, I mean with no tools or magic potion or something.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 10 HEARTS
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Mon10": "%Barnabas looks at you like an excited puppy.#$b#@! Hey, @! I found this stone that reminds me of you! Look!$1#$b#%He hands you an oddly shaped stone with a few small holes in it.#$b#Look! I found it at the beach the other day and water naturally formed these holes in them. It reminds me of you because I couldn't lay my eyes off of it!$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Tue10": "Any day spent with you automatically turns out to be a really great day!#$b#It's really weird but you somehow always lift me up and it makes me all giddy thinking about you, heh.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Wed10": "Do you think there's a way sea urchins can look even cooler than they already do?#$b#Wait...y<ou put hats on them?! You gotta show me! Do you think we can raise a bunch of them and let them wear funny hats?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Thu10": "I came up with a genius idea!$1#$b#...unfortunately it was right after I woke up and I forgot to write it down....but it's at the tip of my tongue, I swear!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Fri10": "I've had a spurt of making art lately and way too many have you in it in some way....seems like I really can't get you out of my head.$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sat10": "%Barnabas shifts around as he sees you approach, it's really hard to contain his excitement.#$b#@! Oh, @!#$b#Do you think you got some time later? I just found this new gem and a really great spot to top it off. I think you'd really like it!$4",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.Sun10": "Would you still love me if I was a worm?$2",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "You run around looking for eggs and get a price...us mermaids actually got something similar!#$b#I hope you'll be having a lot of fun tomorrow!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Dancing...it's not my forte but I can manage. Though...I'm not too comfortable dancing in front of stranger, heh.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "Make sure to eat lots of stuff tomorrow! It's always the most fun and tastes the best when you share food with others, heh!$1",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "The jellies have their own things going on and it's really a spectacle to see.#$b#Let me know if you want to see them again, I can talk to a few to maybe meet with you.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "So...a day to do fun games and compete to see who has the best crops and stuff? Sounds fun!#$b#If it weren't just me doing all the farming here most times I'd suggest something like that for the island too, haha!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "The times when the veil of living and dead becomes thin is a delicate time.#$b#I fear it....I'm not scared of ghosts but...$8",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "Make sure to pack up and wear warm clothes when you go ice fishing! I don't wanna see you get sick...#$b#...but if you do, don't hesitate to ask me for help. I'll nurse you back to health!#$b#I've got a really good recipe that's packed with vitamins and stuff!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "Gift giving...? Hm...#$b#...mermaids do have a time they come together to celebrate the death and rebirth of nature when they exchange homemade gifts too. Hope you're going to have some fun tomorrow!",
	"Festivals.FlowerDance.Barnabas": "Hey!$1#$b#I love how dedicated they were with decorating it all with flowers.#$b#This is such a lovely festival!$1",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Umm, hey there! How did you get here? Are you tired as well?",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "When I get a piece of stone I like to just look at it for a long time.#$b#Slowly it will tell me it's story and I will be able to carve out it's beauty.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "I like tending to the island. Let it be the Orchard, the forest or any other part!#$b#When I get to see how everything is flourishing it just fills me with joy.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.003": "%Barnabas doesn't seem to notice you. He is peacefully snoozing away as he is taking a break from all his chores.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.004": "I always make sure that everything is regularly checked. It's important to secure basic needs to ensure everyones able to flourish!",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.005": "...$8#$b#.........$8#$b#...ah! Sorry, I was in thoughts. Hello there, @.",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.006": "Hm...these stories from long gone-by eras are fascinating...",
	"VoidWitchCult.CP.TheFishmongerNPC.Barnabas.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.007": "I enjoy when we come together and hang out on Sunday!#$b#It helps with catching up on things and having a moment to just relax and do silly stuff, heh!$1",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== LIBRARIAN ==================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Gamayun.Gifttastes.Love": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Gifttastes.Like": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Gifttastes.Dislike": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Gifttastes.Hate": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Gifttastes.Neutral": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Hm...do make sure to properly disinfect yourself after dumpster diving. One does not want you to catch anything.",
	"amayun.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Most devious. One shall include you in ones next hex.$2",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "One does not have time for moving pictures. The books are calling ones name instead.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Most fascinating. It is always a pleasure to see natures curious ways.",
	"Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, regretful. One was going to collect some rainwater for a few spells...",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "One enjoys these downpours. Like a super moon a rare occasion with special magic properties.",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Introduction": "Most pleasing to meet one such as yourself. One goes by many names but your humble self can use the name 'Gamayun'.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "One is antisocial, you shouldn't be able to give one gifts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_LibrarianGamayun": "...",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.spring_1": "Ēostre greets you. The spring Equinox shall bring renewal and rebirth from the death of winter.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.summer_1": "The suns zenith is approaching...a vibrant celebration of light, abundance, and the flourishing of nature.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.fall_1": "While you celebrate your bounty o' plenty do not forget to mourn the lost and forgotten as well. One keeps that which gives life and those whose life has runs it's course both in mind when it is time to pay ones toll.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.winter_1": "A time of quiet introspection and setting intentions...make sure to celebrate the return of the light in the end to welcome a new year.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Mon.0": "How do you like to categorize your books? One enjoys spending all day finding the most intricate system to file them by.#$b#One has been given the task by the olde king and one enjoys it quite much.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Mon.1": "Hm...when one looks too much into the void it does not simple stare back. It tends to ask how one is doing and if the weather is nice...",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Mon.2": "One knows of another witch that lives in seclusion. They barely ever show themself to others...#$b#You can visit their shadow down at the beach though.#$b#They sell quite a few things, yes.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Mon.3": "In the past one used to visit the king quite a lot.#$b#With the new king that has yet to embrace that title...hm. He shows signs of leadership yet stays too humble to embrace it. Worrisome.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Mon.4": "Days pass. Weather changes. Friendships end.#$b#Natural occurrences, yes. Yet one says it is completely fine to grief over these losses.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Mon.5": "Most exciting. One restored an old book with a spell when all one had were some pages and the spine.",
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Tue.0": "Greetings, seeker.#$b#One has just dusted the bookshelves so feel free to enjoy the books.#$b#With a little bit of magic one can do so without the need to be close by.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Tue.1": "One is always in pursuit of finding more books to add to the library.#$b#These are not all that one owns...quite a few are hidden away as they contain dangerous magical spells and such.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Tue.2": "Have you read any books lately?#$b#One does enjoy all kind of books. Just recently one finished a romance novel with a bittersweet ending.#$b#Very emotional.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Tue.3": "Have you met any other librarians lately?#$b#One has been told one can be quite the oddball. It is beyond ones understanding...since when do all librarians need to be the same?",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Tue.4": "One has restored quite a few books today. Pleasing indeed.#$b#If you are ever in the need of book restoration you can ask for help.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Tue.5": "...ah. It is you.#$b#Greetings, young one. How has your day been so far?",
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Wed.0": "One has many tales to tell about king Llyr.#$b#There are quite a few contained in the books in this library as well.#$b#Feel free to browse the shelves or seek one out any time.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Wed.1": "Yesterday one tested out a few olde spells from a recently discovered tome.#$b#One accidentally worried the young lord who was close-by.#$b#It was a mere explosion but one guesses the young lord just wanted to make sure one is safe.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Wed.2": "One enjoys watching the young lord paint and sculpt.#$b#He is a lot like his father even when he is unaware of that.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Wed.3": "Lately one has started to check all the books in the library.#$b#One still has a lot of work left to do but it is progressing well.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Wed.4": "A wise man gets going while he still can. If he stays too long, even the brave grow fearful.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Wed.5": "The stars have been telling one things...ah, well, not important to you. At least not right now.#$b#Even without understanding them the stars are nice to look at during the night, no?",
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Thu.0": "Be sure to keep your daily luck in mind. One can see certain-...things in your future.#$b#One shall not go into detail though to not disturb the fates.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Thu.1": "Maybe one shall read a romance book today.#$b#Happy ending, sad ending...hm.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Thu.2": "One does enjoy doing something besides being librarian.#$b#There are days one goes to the olde tree at the quarry to play with some monsters.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Thu.3": "Most devious. One found some bugs eating a book today. Now one is in need to fix it AND get rid of those bugs.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Thu.4": "Travel far and wide and you should possess the secrets of man.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Thu.5": "One enjoys when the library is busy with people but it is as much of a joy to be on ones own.",
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Fri.0": "At last...one has found a copy of the memoirs of the last dragon sovereign.#$b#Hm? Oh...this shall NOT get filed under 'fiction', no.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Fri.1": "%Gamayun is distracted deciding where a certain book should go on the shelf...",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Fri.2": "Fortune favors the bold.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Fri.3": "Greetings, seeker. What interesting deeds are you up to today?",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Fri.4": "Sometimes the young lord comes to seek out help.#$b#Most times it is about things like how to make dyes brighter or the structural integrity of certain buildings he has built.#$b#One does enjoy these conversations as much as the talk about weather and such.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Fri.5": "Ones place of origin is bleak and desolate.#$b#One enjoys this island a lot and is quite elevating calling it home.",
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sat.0": "One does not need sleep.#$b#Thus one can go on with work for days without the need to rest.#$b#Yet one still gives in now and then, even if it is just to ease the worry of those around.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sat.1": "Exciting news: One has gotten quite a few books from other islands in the gem sea.#$b#It'll help one to complete the missing bits of history around.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sat.2": "%There are several books in Gamayuns hands. Looks like she cannot decide which to read first.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sat.3": "Do you ever wonder if what you do even matters in the grand scheme of things?#$b#Forget about those thoughts. Trifling things like that are what does not matter.#$b#Enjoy your life without doubts.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sat.4": "%Gamayun looks busy, better to not disturb her.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sat.5": "Bernadette has come to one in search for musical answers.#$b#One has given her quite a few hints on where to look for answers.#$b#She is a bright child and one hopes she will find her place in the world.",
	
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Most pleasing day.#$b#One quite enjoys being around others, despite being in the library most of the time.#$b#Will you be joining the gathering as well?",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sun.1": "When a week is over it feels like a lot of time has passed.#$b#Time is relative, yet one works and works and works...then the week turns and it awaits one even more work.#$b#Be sure to take your well deserved rest.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Our young lord does not condone looting on this island.#$b#One was surprised to find out there are pirates that do not loot every place they stop at.#$b#It has been long since then, but one is always happy to welcome those that mean no harm.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Ah, bright seeker. Another day passes with you it it. A joyous moment indeed.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sun.4": "%Gamayun is distracted by the drink she has in her hands muttering something about certain languages you have never heard of.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.Sun.5": "The stars in the sky, the sparkling pearls in the ocean...this island is full of brightness and light.#$b#Not just to see, but to feel and become part of as well.",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "Ah, is it time for the egg hunt again, right?#$b#Dhu gautar osta, ous il sin grosta...%3#$b#...make sure to have a lot of fun.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "A joyous occasion. It reminds one of the midsommar celebrations long gone.#$b#Maybe one shall dedicate a dance to this exalting day.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "What flavor of mischief will you cause this year?#$b#Or are you behaving this time around?",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "Watching the jellies migrate is a sight to behold. One enjoys it's bioluminescence properties quite a lot.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "Make sure to thank your ancestors for your bountiful harvest. THose of the past walked so one can run in the present.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "The veil of living and deceased is thinner than ever, seeker.#$b#Make sure to not step too far into the unknown if you're ill prepared.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "One used to partake in something like ice fishing in the past.#$b#It was without a rod though and was you diving directly into the icey cold waters though.",
	"Gamayun.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "As winter slowly comes to an end it is important to make sure you show your loved ones that you care.#$b#This is a time to celebrate the return of the light and thank those who have been part of your life.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Gamayun.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "There are a lot of books in this library so it is only natural that one has to sort through them all.#$b#One does not mind though.",
	"Gamayun.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "One always make sure to replace and relight the candles around.#$b#They are all powered by magic so it is a rather simple task.",
	"Gamayun.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "One always makes sure to put the books back that were returned.#$b#One always makes sure to put the books back that were returned.#$b#There were times they got piled up and it took quite a while to sort them away.",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Anette ===================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Anette.Gifttastes.Love": "This is for me?  Oh my, thank you for such thoughtful gift! $1",
	"Anette.Gifttastes.Like": "A gift? This is such nice gesture, thanks.",
	"Anette.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Hm...it's not really my thing but...I appreciate the thought, I guess.",
	"Anette.Gifttastes.Hate": "Ugh...$5",
	"Anette.Gifttastes.Neutral": "...thanks? $3",
	"Anette.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "...not really elegant. I just...gonna ignore this.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Are you serious? $5",
	"Anette.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Um, maybe another time? I'm kind of busy, sorry.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Oh...I've heard about this rain thing.#$b#It shouldn't be an issue, right?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, it's over. Hm, I saw Bernadettes hair having, uh...well, it's sure a look.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "This rain...something feels weird about it.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Oh my! $1#$b#Thank you for such exquisite tea!",
	"Anette.Dialogue.PinkCake": "A whole pink cake just for me?#$b#You're the best!$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Cloth": "Great, more cloth!$1#$b#Thanks, I was running low on it, you're a life-saver, @!",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Broccoli": "Yuck! Get that tiny tree away from me!$2",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Anette.Dialogue.Introduction": "Greetings! The name's Anette, nice to meet you.#$b#A pretty nice day to meet someone new.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Oh?#$b#A birthday gift for me? That's really kind of you to think of me, thank you.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Ah, today is my birthday, isn't it?#$b#Thank you so much for such lovely gift.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thank you for thinking of me.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Oh, thank you. I didn't think I'd get a gift today, hehe.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm...of any day to give me this...you picked today?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "To receive such thing on my birthday...sigh.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Ah, thank you for this gift.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "I'm sure I can put this to use somehow, thanks.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.MovieInvite_Invited_Anette": "Oh! I'd love to watch a movie with you, @!#$b#I wonder what the theater will be showing.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Anette.Dialogue.spring_1": "Spring is such a nice season. It's like when you wake up fresh and rested and everything around you is shining.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.summer_1": "Summer is a season I tend to enjoy a lot. There's the rare moment I don't, like when it gets way too hot and humid, but in general it's very lovely.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.fall_1": "Got your things in order yet? Fall is here and for a lot it's harvest season before winter approaches and everything dies.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.winter_1": "What do you tend to do during winter? I'm lucky to live in a warm climate all year around but I like to visit the valley now and then because playing in snow is just fun! $1",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Anette.Dialogue.0": "Lovely day,isn't it? I think I might go out to ask Bernadette for some music recommendations.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.1": "I am already out of cloth again...I wonder if I can convince the others to make a bulk order for more supplies...I'm sure Willow will find a way to make a good deal for us.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.2": "I heard some people come together to meet for fashion related things. Like...some sort of fashion show?#$b#Do you think there's anything like that around here?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.3": "Today might be a good day to sort my clothes. Maybe...starting with the dresses, I kind of have a lot of those.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.4": "Hey there, good day! Don't let the sharks bite you, hehe.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.5": "I love hanging out with friends. That's why you can always find me at the hangout.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.6": "Hey, it's you again.#$b#It's nice to see you coming around regularly.#$b#I hope you enjoy your stay on the island.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.7": "I do wonder if I should change my hair...maybe a new color?#$b#I've had all the colors of the rainbows already. Hm, maybe another pastel color?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.8": "Usually it's more exciting around here...maybe it's time to rough things up.#$b#I think I'm going to ask Barnabas if he can show me a few local sea shells.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.9": "Hm............... -oh!#$b#Hey, there. Sorry, I was a bit in thoughts. Willow asked me to calculate a few possible orders for some dresses and I've been wondering if I should even bother calculating the cheapest variant.#$b#Nobody wants to wear shiny polyester...",
	"Anette.Dialogue.10": "I've got this song stuck in my head and a specific part just keeps on repeating...you ever had something like this happen?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.11": "I've watched one of those ghost hunter videos online.#$b#It's a bit hard to take seriously when you have literal mermaids living next doors.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.12": "Great timing! I was handing out some candy earlier to the others, do you want some too?#$B#It's just a little something but you might like it, @.$1 [279]",
	"Anette.Dialogue.13": "%Anette appears in thoughts, not noticing you at all. She murmurs to herself as she is scribbling something down into a small notebook.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.14": "I enjoy waking up really early. There's something about watching the sun rise while sipping on your coffee...#$b#...15 I also go out and watch the sun set.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.15": "Oh!$1#$b$#I have been thinking about some new looks lately. You coming here made me think about some sort of harvest type collection, what do you think?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.16": "My coord for my next meet-up isn't doing well...#$b#...I feel like something is missing but I'm not sure what.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.17": "I've eaten a persimmon today. It's sweetness and tanginess was just right!#$b'I do have quite the sweet tooth but simply eating candy all the time just won't do. I'm so blessed to live somewhere an abundant amount of fruits and such grow.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.18": "%Anette notices you with a smile and waves, though does not stop to chat.#%b#Sorry, @. I am kind of in a hurry right now with deadlines approaching! We'll catch up later, promise!$2",
	"Anette.Dialogue.19": "I've been thinking about broadening my collection of dresses and skirts.#$b#I wonder if I should fgocus more on patterns or maybe frills and lace? Hm...#$b#There's no such thing as 'too much frills', right?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.20": "I'd love to ask a few people to be a model for my clothes...#$b#I do wonder if Calliope or Bernadette would be up to it? Maybe even Caitriona...#$b#Hm...I could make a pirate theme or something 'alternative'...",
	"Anette.Dialogue.21": "Oh! I had this amazing idea yesterday! I think I will set up some sort of book for all of my OOTDs with explanations and such and release it online for everyone.#$b#You know, kind of like a fashion magazine but for lolita type of clothes. Hm, maybe I could even get some 'guests' starring in it...",
	"Anette.Dialogue.22": "Have you ever wondered about what mermaids usually wear? Like, the type of clothes and what they are made of.#$b#Some time ago I did ask Calliope and Barnabas. While Calliope gave me some good insight on natural materials and such, um...Barnabas was-...well...#$b#...I guess him saying he just wears whatever he finds washed ashore is some sort of recycled reuse or something? Hm...natural and recycled materials do somehow sound fun...$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.23": "Have you ever wondered if you pursued the right thing?#$b#Well, I do wonder myself sometimes. I know there's no easy answer but sometimes the decisions one makes weight down heavy...#$b#...not that I am unhappy or anything. I guess I was just looking for kindred spirits, haha!$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.24": "I am glad to have a family that supports what I persue. It wasn't always easy but at the end of the I really lucked out, with my friends too.#$b#A stable and strong support system really makes a difference when it comes to one's self-worth and ability to become independent and head-strong, I'd say.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.25": "%Anette gives you a bright smile.#$b#Hey, there, @!$1#$b#I am in such a great mood! Just got a compliment on my latest OOTD and also sold a few dresses. I'm feeling awesome, today's treat is on me! [904]",
	"Anette.Dialogue.26": "How long I've been on this island? Hm....#$b#I think that's more of a question Willow could answer, she's obsessed with numbers. It's been years...but what I CAN say is that I do not regret any minute I spend here! It's a great place, albeit a bit hard to reach your loved ones sometimes, but...well, otherwise...I think only someone who dislikes the summer and coastal areas would hate it here, haha!",
	"Anette.Dialogue.27": "The latest shipment from afar just came in for Willow...I took the chance to get some new make-up and fabric that I wouldn't usually get in this region.#$b#I know for some it's a bit excessive but it is what I love so I am ready to spend a few coins for my creative outlet.#$b#Plus I do make money selling what I sew so it's kind of a win/win, right?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.28": "Recently I've gone through my older fashion magazines to get some inspiration...#$b#...I ended up mapping out past trends and the ones that came back and in what way things changed from the last time they were 'in'.#$b#It's truly fascinating how everything seems to have their revival somehow...even the things that people often wish would 'stay dead'.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.29": "I had a really good dish earlier today. I went out and met Barnabas who was collecting some forage and he asked me if I had anything to eat yet today. Since I admitted that I didn't he whipped something up for me.#$b#Here, he gave me enough leftovers so I can share some with you! [242]",
	"Anette.Dialogue.30": "It's the weekend, you know? A great time to kick back and relax...if I hadn't all these fabric scraps laying around that I need to sort away.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.31": "I've been talking to the others recently and been wondering if us three should start some sort of podcast.#$b#Everyones been doing it nowadays and we could theme it around how to sell the things you make yourself and the hardships that come with having a business...hm...",
	"Anette.Dialogue.32": "Word of advice: Don't wash all your dresses at once and hang them to dry all around your room.#$b#It'll create a wet sort of labyrinth that is hard to navigate when you want to go to the bathroom in the middle of the night...",
	"Anette.Dialogue.33": "Have you heard about the fashion show they tried organizing in Zuzu City?#$b#Looks like it ended in a huge fiasco...something about the seller both being full of clothes with AI generated images...#$b#...what a world we live in...$2",
	"Anette.Dialogue.34": "How do you usually plan your day?#$b#As a farmer I'd think you're probably always very busy but I see you around quite a bit.#$b#Not that I complain. I am simply in awe of your time management. Maybe I can learn from your secrets...",
	
	"Anette.Dialogue.Sun.0": "I made some nice treats for todays hangout.#$b#I hope the others like them!",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Another week has passed. Did you get to do all the things you were planning to do?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Sun.2": "No matter if rain or sun...a Sunday is always somehow such a nice day!#$b#Though it does sometimes feel like it is somehow a weird day compared to the rest of the week.#$b#What do I mean with this? Hm...you ever heard of the backrooms? This kinda eery feeling you get when you're in such a place...just as a weekday, I guess.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Another week comes to an end and another deadline that approaches...#$b#Good thing that I am worlds ahead of my schedule and can relax today!$1#$b#Admittingly, I do get behind sometimes but, well, anyone has those kinda days, right?#$b#.......#$b#...don't tell Willow that I forgot to put the laundry up.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Sun.4": "I need to talk to Gamayun one of these days.#$b#I know there's some hidden gems not shared in that library about magic infused fabric...#$b#...well, I know it's probably off limit for non-magic users for a reason but...doesn't hurt to ask, right?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.Sun.5": "I walked around the coast earlier today and found a few interesting things. Usually shells and such are washed ashore, but this...#$b#...what do you think? [858]",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"Anette.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "The Egg festival is such a nice idea. I love when I have themes I can build my OOTD off of.#$b#Will you attend your towns festivities this year?",
	"Anette.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Back where I am from we have a similar tradition as the flower dance. It's always fascinating to see certain traditions overlap.$1#$b#I've been the flower queen a few years even, heh.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "Ready for a food war?#$b#Heard some are rather chaotic aligned on occasions such as a potluck. Tell me how yours was later.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "I love watching the jellies when they migrate. It's a treat to know that Barnabas can command them so we can watch them more often, hehe.$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "Hmmmm....I am wondering if I should visit my home town soon. There's a fair that's about to happen there and I'd like to partake in it.#$b#I think it's similar to the one in your town, maybe a bit bigger though.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "It's the time of the year where we can be spooky without anyone calling us 'cringe'.#$b#........#$b#...not that I really give a hoot when someone calls me that. Anyway, I think I am going to wear my pumpkin dress!$1",
	"Anette.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "I've heard a lot about ice fishing from my dad.#$b#While fishing in general isn't really my thing I find it fascinating that no matter what season it is people will find a way to do what they love, heh.",
	"Anette.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "Already feeling the festive spirit?#$b#Willow, Esme and I decided on a big gift giving session this year! I even got Esme to show me some dance moves.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Anette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Isn't the island nice? I enjoy sitting out here often because of the beautiful weather.#$b#Even the rain is soft and gentle, hehe.",
	"Anette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Looking for some reading spot? The library has a lot of seats, just pick any you like.",
	"Anette.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "What a nice day, hehe! I've been scribbling down a lot of new ideas, so I am taking the time to relax and chat with the others.",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Willow ==================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Willow.Gifttastes.Love": "Hm, quite an adequate gift, thank you. ",
	"Willow.Gifttastes.Like": "Ah, thanks. I do find this quite pleasing.",
	"Willow.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Well, didn't take you for the type to gift cheap Tat.$5",
	"Willow.Gifttastes.Hate": "Ugh, why are you giving me such Bric-a-brac...$5",
	"Willow.Gifttastes.Neutral": "...#$b#...could be worse.$2",
	"Willow.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": ".....sigh. I know you can get good deal and all but...can you please do it in a less obvious way?$5",
	"Willow.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "I have the money and means to get something that will make you regret doing that. Be warned.$5",
	"Willow.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Ah, maybe another time. I am quite busy with all these orders at the moment.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Ugh, well, there goes my carefully planned shipping schedule. Gotta inform my customers that things might take longer than initially planned...",
	"Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Finally! Now I can resume sending out my goods.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Yet again fate has kicked my right in the shin. Sigh...#$b#..well, can't be helped. Gotta go and calculate the damages from the delay.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Gems": "Oh my, what do we have here?$4#$b#You have such a good eye for these, @! Maybe I should have you work here as an expert.$4",
	"Willow.Dialogue.TreasureChest": "Oh! What a great catch, @!#$b#Wait, it's for me? Wow you really spoil me, but I don't mind.$4",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Book": "Oh! Thanks for the book, now I have my next read for when it's bedtime, hehe.",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Willow.Dialogue.Introduction": "The name's Willow. I deal with all kind of goods. You need something I get it. That is of course if you want something a mere mortal can get, hah!",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Color me surprised, this is quite the gift you got me there, thank you.$1",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Such an exquisite gift, for me? Why thank you kindly.$1",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Remembering the birthday of your dealer...quite the impressive feat, Thank you.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Many thanks. I do quite like this birthday gift.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "%Willow just silently stares at you for a moment.#$b#You come at me. On my birthday. Giving me this birthday gift. Really?$5",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Ugh!$5",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Well.#$b#.......#$b#..Fine. I gonna say thanks. Thanks.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Ah....maybe next year you will get this right.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Willow.Dialogue.spring_1": "Ah yes, a new year...that comes with new resolutions and a want for a clean slate.#$b#The best time to stock a high amount of workout gear and general sports stuff. People always stream towards that during this time.#$b#What's so wrong to make some bucks while helping others try to better themself?",
	"Willow.Dialogue.summer_1": "Hm...I got anything someone who wants to enjoy summer could want...#$b#...wanna scuba dive? Or maybe look for treasures at the beach?",
	"Willow.Dialogue.fall_1": "Oh yes, I do got pumpkin carving sets, spooky decorations and such.#$b#Anything else I should stock up on, hm...",
	"Willow.Dialogue.winter_1": "Ever heard of the word 'Hygge'?#$b#Heard it basically translated to something cozy or whatever. Winter is a good time to get cozy at a fire place and enjoy a cuppa hot choccy.#$b#Well, If you're in cold climate at least.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Willow.Dialogue.0": "I've counted all my stock, have ordered what I am running low on and-#$b#Oh! Hey there, mate.#$b#Got a good start into the week too?",
	"Willow.Dialogue.1": "I am making sure that everything I have been planning to order will arrive at the exact moment I want to.#$b#Hm? Oh, come on...belated delivery? Ever heard of magic?",
	"Willow.Dialogue.2": "The most perfect, pretty number for me is eight.#$b#It may not be a perfect number, but it is a perfect cube.#$b#Either way, you can part it in the middle, horizontal or vertical and it's still mirrored to look like itself.$3#$b#...or if you're really fancy you lay it down to sleep and get the infinity symbol, haha!$4",
	"Willow.Dialogue.3": "Making sure that everything works smoothly and things don't go out of hand...that's what I am known for here.#$b#I help where I can, delegating the routes and such, heh.#$b#Well, sometimes it's hard for non-humans to get their needs across, especially in a corporate world. Everyone deserves an even playing field.#$b#I might be out for the bucks but that doesn't mean I am soulless like a certain corporate entity that is somehow everywhere...$5",
	"Willow.Dialogue.4": "Hm...my books tell me that there's an unknown item somewhere...$1#$b#...I cannot have that! I need to find it and categorize it and look where it came from and and-!#$b#...whew.#$b#...don't spiral, Willow.#$b#I am sure I'll get this done too. Just a little extra thing to do in between the usual work.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.5": "If you ever need something and have no way of getting it...just ask me. I am sure I will find a way to get it.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.6": "Making sure you get your work done on time is important, especially when you know that certain items are in high demand and you need to make sure that it is always in stock.#$b#Otherwise you will risk losing customers and getting bad reviews.#$b#Besides, I hate it when I seem unreliable. I want to make sure I make my customers happy.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.7": "%Willow appears to be distracted, not noticing you.%noturn#$b#34...35...36....hm........if I go towards 50....%noturn#$b#...oh...I don't think that's enough...%noturn#$b#%Doesn't seem like she will be much of a conversational partner right now.%noturn",
	"Willow.Dialogue.8": "I always chime in to offer some of the food that is served Sundays at the hangout.#$b#It's important to be there for your community, even when your main focus is to make money.#$b#While I am a salesperson, I still am a 'person'. So of course I do enjoy being part of things and making friends.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.9": "%Willow has a stack of papers in her her hands, mumbling about numbers and dates.%noturn#$b#....hm? Oh, hey! Didn't see you there.#$b#I was deep in thoughts about this months sales and expenses, sorry.#$b#Things going well for you? Nothing sucks more than to see you've made some losses in your business. Especially when you're dependent on selling your goods and such.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.10": "Been to big cities a lot of times, you know?#$b#Had my fair share of big stores and big sales, big parties and big-...well, everything.#$b#Made me realize something really important...that to me it is not about making the most money or being the biggest player out there.#$b#Yeah, well, making money is THE thing in this line of work but, you know...I would not sell my soul for it.#$b#I'm still a person and I still have needs and those needs just happen to involve wanting to be around people in a genuine way.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.11": "Ah, @. Nice to see you.#$b#Is the life of farming treating you well?#$b#If you ever feel like wanting to talk about the more serious money talk you're free to do so with me. Maybe I even have a few tricks and tips for you.$3",
	"Willow.Dialogue.12": "Anette asked me to order some more fabric for her dresses.#$b#Yeah, maybe I am spoiling her a little but what's the harm in it? I mean, I do have the means and reach to get the stuff for her, so...",
	"Willow.Dialogue.13": "I've tried to get Esme to film a little ad for me but so far she seems not too fond of it.#$b#Guess selling things and mermaid dancing aren't as compatible as I thought.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.14": "Half the weeks over and I still got a lot to take care of.#$b#For some my job might seem boring and monotonous but I find solace and comfort in numbers and all.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.15": "For a moment I felt like I achieved the perfect zen moment the other day...#$b#Boxes perfectly stacked and aligned, nothing out of place....#$b#Then Esme and Anette squabbled over whose turn it was to take out the trash and knocked over one of my boxes, making the rest topple down, sigh...",
	"Willow.Dialogue.16": "It's important to do some things to bind the customer to your business, you know?#$b#Something that makes them come back and keep investing their hard earned money into your store....#$...that said, here, take this. It's a freebie. [StardropTea]",
	"Willow.Dialogue.17": "Don't tell anyone but I got a few leftovers and I think you'll find some use for these, right? [852] [896]",
	"Willow.Dialogue.18": "Hmmm, the fresh air on this island is great and the warm weather makes me always crave some ice cream.#$b#A little treat once in a while should be fine, right? Once work is done I think me and the others will have an ice cream party and watch some videos.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.19": "What businesses I've been a part of?#$b#Hm, well...I don't really feel like listing all of them but let's say I've dabbled in A LOT. Let it be groceries, fashion, lumber...even went and had some place to sell stuff from mines.#$b#That's why I have all of these 'connections'. Can't hurt to keep certain places 'warm' and willing, haha!",
	"Willow.Dialogue.20": "Barnabas came to me the other day and asked if I could get him a few things.#$b#Who am I to deny the king of kings.#$b#Hah! Jokes aside, of course I helped him out. One hand washes the other...he DID help me to establish myself on the island after all.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.21": "Dang, I think I stayed up too long last night...#$b#...tried getting the numbers in order before the next shipment comes in but then it was suddenly 4am...oops.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.22": "Monster, human or anything else...doesn't matter. I do business with anyone.#$b#That doesn't mean anyone can just come in and demand things though, I do have my integrity and pride.#$b#Like when that weirdo joja guy came around asking to buy me out...like, what?$5",
	"Willow.Dialogue.23": "%Willow is checking her phone, she looks occupied with something. There's a small glance and nod but that's all you'll probably get from her for now.%noturn",
	"Willow.Dialogue.24": "Fridays are a good day to check your inventory. People enjoy buying stuff because they want to spend a relaxed and fun weekend. That means higher possibilities on selling stuff!#$b#What's your plan for the weekend?",
	"Willow.Dialogue.25": "I recently got my hands on some skill books and it's fascinating what time they can save.#$b#Neat short cuts like these are great when you got no time and needs things to get done.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.26": "Earlier today Anette showed me a few new ideas for outfits and I was quite intrigued by them.#$b#She is always so creative, I admire her tenacity when it comes to following her dreams.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.27": "%Willow rushes by with a quick nod, but doesn't stop to talk. Looks like she is in a hurry, better not keep her up.%noturn",
	"Willow.Dialogue.28": "Recently I stumbled upon a box full of really old coins.#$b#At first I was thinking of selling it but the coins just-...I don't know, I simply liked them too much, I suppose.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.29": "I may not look like it but I do have other things that I do besides being a salesperson.#$b#There's so much critters to go around, I started bird watching and love it.#$b#Sometimes Barnabas even joins me and tells me about a particular bird that happens to drop by.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.30": "Lovely day, isn't it?#$b#I might even cut my workday short if I get things done quickly. Then I can go and enjoy a good read at the library.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.31": "When I was young I wanted to be an Accountant. Sounds lame but I come from a family of Accountants.#$b#I did like making my own coins a little bit too much though, haha!$4",
	"Willow.Dialogue.32": "I have a little brother who owns a butchery. He is the eccentric one in our family.#$b#At least according to our parents. I just like him the way he is. 10/10.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.33": "Imagine you wouldn't need to pay for anything in the world for a day, what would you do?#$b#For me...hm, it's a bit hard to say. I have the privilege of not needing to turn every penny twice so O kinda already get what I want...#$b#...but...I guess an amusement park does sound kinda neat.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.34": "Hmmm, hey, @.#$b#...I've got nothing much to say today. Been kind of under the weather today, my minds drawing a blank.#$b#Esme insists that I take the day off but a business never sleeps...",
	"Willow.Dialogue.35": "I've been to other countries before. As a salesperson it kinda comes with the trade.#$b#I think there's some beautiful places out there but don't let yourself get blinded by sheer beauty.#$#Sometimes, sometimes appearances are deceiving.",
	
	"Willow.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Ahhh, the end of the week. That means a day of rest and enjoying some good cooking by Barnabas.#$b#%Willow drifts off to imagine the good food that will be served.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Hm! Have you ever tried fried seaweed?#$b#Barnabas offered me some last time we gathered and it was nice.#$b#It's a good snack when combined with some rice and grilled fish.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I thought I couldn't make it to the gathering because of an emergency shipment but luck is on my side...yippie!",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Sun.3": "The island might be small, but we still got a bunch of people here that come around places.#$b#That means some nice juicy small-talk on days like these, heh.$4",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Hope you took the time to relax a little.#$b#Even I can kick back and enjoy a leisurely day like this.#$b#Well, most of the time at least.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.Sun.5": "I remember how I used to grind through every day, working, working, working....$2#$b#...by now I learned to cut back and at least enjoy my Sundays.",
	
	//DIALOGUE SPECIFIC DAY
	"Willow.Dialogue.spring_12_2": "This time of year the egg sales go crazy!#$b#Make sure to collect a lot tomorrow and not let them go to waste.#$b#The only thing I hate more than losing money is for food to go to waste.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.spring_23_2": "Flowers, flowers and more flowers.#$b#The demand is crazy but having unique local variants means being able to make a few extra bucks.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.summer_10_2": "I've partaken in one of these potlucks in the past.#$b#It's a fun thing but only as long as no one is adding a 'secret ingredient'.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.summer_27_2": "Have fun tomorrow night.#$b#The jellies are quite nice to watch but I still got plenty of things I need to ship out so I'll work through the night.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.fall_15_2": "Hm, I never really liked fairs that much.#$b#I appreciate the hussle but it's just throwing out money in the end.#$b#Hm...if the prices were neater and the chances were fairer...",
	"Willow.Dialogue.fall_26_2": "Spooky time means spooky costumes.#$b#And spooky costumes mean...#$b#...more money of course!",
	"Willow.Dialogue.winter_7_2": "Been ice fishing before.#$b#I don't have the patience to sit that long in the cold.",
	"Willow.Dialogue.winter_24_2": "Ah, the time of gift giving...a very busy time for me to ship out things and make more money.#$b#Oh, and of course be ready to have gifts to give as well.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Willow.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Making sure the stock is in perfect condition is very important.#$b#Especially when you have fresh produce and generally anything that has a short shelf life.#$b#How can I pride myself in being a great merchant if I am sloppy with my work?",
	"Willow.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Nice weather to take a stroll, eh?#$b#Oh, me? I am just checking in on everyone if things are going well or if they need something.#$b#It's important to not just keep customers happy but your employees and fellow merchants as well.",
	"Willow.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "Mhm, scrumptious! The others always know how to make the good stuff!",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Ragna ====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Ragna.Gifttastes.Love": "Wow! This is great, thank you so much!$1",
	"Ragna.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you, I like it!",
	"Ragna.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Hm, I don't really have a use for this...$2",
	"Ragna.Gifttastes.Hate": "Uh...is this some sick joke?$5",
	"Ragna.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Hm, I'm sure I can use this somehow.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "I am all in for reusing things that still work and recycling but....maybe not exactly this way.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Nice flowers you got there.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Hm? Oh, you're planning to propose to someone? Good luck!",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Ouch! What the heck?$5",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Sorry, I got no time for suck things. Maybe ask someone else.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Nice! I have been waiting for this to happen!",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Aw, it's over already...oh well. I did gather some interesting data.$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "This is such an interesting event! I want to study it more and see if it happens in other places too.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.FireQuartz": "Oh, that's my favorite gem, @.$1#$b#Quartz might count as not that valuable when it comes to prices but I love them, especially when it*'s a fire quartz!",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Artifacts": "Oh! Look at this!#$b#I cannot wait to unearth what secret story this artifact is trying to tell...$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Gasp! Oh, thank you, @! It's been a while since I hydrated myself.#$b#Wow-! That's such a lovely taste...my taste buds are dancing in joy.$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Gems": "That luster...the color...wow!#$b#No matter what gem it is they fascinate me.#$b#The time it took for nature to create them...the inclusions that are often regarded as bad I find delightful! They tell secret stories not many will ever hear about.$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Minerals": "Oh yes! Little mineral tell me about the place you were found in...the times you've witness...#$b#This is so exciting!$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Introduction": "The name is Ragna, nice to meet you.$1#$b#I'm not from this island originally but moved here to study the environment!",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "A birthday present? Wow, that's such a neat thing, thank you!$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Thank you for such a great gift!$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "That's so nice of you to give me something for my birthday.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Thank you for this gift. I appreciate it.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm, thanks for the gift, I guess.$2",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Um...thanks?$2",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Thanks, I can find a use for this!",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Thank you for the gift.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Ragna.Dialogue.0": "I like studying the environment mainly focused on merfolk areas.#$b#There such a rich history that is forgotten by all and I will try to find connections in our surroundings and discover old and new things.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.1": "One of the main reasons I came here was for the especially rich past of this place.#$b#The sacrifice of the late king and how it still connects to this very day...fascinating!$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.2": "Hm? If I have a specific degree?#$b#Well, I did study a few times. As merfolk I naturally have a much longer lifespan than humans which leaves me with plenty of time for such opportunities.#$b#Unfortunately humans tend to not understand when you look like me but say you are far older than most humans can get.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.3": "Well, back to the topic of before though...I did study oceanography, wildlife conversation and Geomatics.#$b#I am an expert of more topics but those are self-taught.#$b#As I mentioned before, at some time it's hard to explain to humans that you can get much older than them.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.4": "Hm, I admit, I did reel in a few of the others to help with my studies.#$b#Mainly because they are much greater with dealing with unknown factors.#$b#Like Hemlock for example. He is really great in diving down into the depths to collect some interesting data for me and all he needs to do is wear the probe while he swims!$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.5": "It's so exciting to talk to the librarian! She has always so many things to say.#$b#While I do believe she is a respectable source of information I have to test and monitor things myself though.#$b#Her knowledge helps me a lot to nudge me into the right directions though!$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.6": "I had such a long conversation with Gamayun earlier. I just love going to the library.#$b#I am a bit behind on checking on my probes but that's alright. I am my own boss after all.$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.7": "I have been collecting samples all morning already.#$b#The island is rich on things to study, it is like an utopia to me.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.8": "Some places are off limits for me and the humans.#$b#I can get behind why the humans aren't allowed to go there but...maybe I can convince King Barnabas if I prove myself to be reliable and prepared for any risk.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.9": "When I first came to this island I initially thought everyone would keep to themself.#$b#But I guess I was wrong...totally wrong. To be honest...I wasn't left alone at all for the first week, haha!$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.10": "It's great to know that ones interests and studies get respect from others. I can see myself living here, even if I didn't have my job.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.11": "I know that the King has a cave under his house that leads to a hidden passage.#$b#Sadly he doesn't allow me to go down there...something is telling me I could find some really great study material down there.$2",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.12": "I do like to scribble things into my notebooks. It's a fun way to break up all this information that I am gathering.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.13": "Do you think we will ever be able to get rid of all this trash in the ocean?",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.14": "%Ragna is deeply in thought about his studies. He mumbles something about changing tides and sand deposits underwater.%noturn",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.15": "%Ragna mutters something about underwater geysers and tectonic plates. He doesn't notice you as he quickly scribbles down some notes.%noturn",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.16": "Hm...oh, hey, @. Nice to see you. Are you interested to know more about water and it's components in regards to the water around this island?",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.17": "It's odd...sometimes it's as if I am hearing a distant voice to not overstep.#$b#Are our ancestors warning me? I am just studying the environment, not trying to create god...",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.18": "Moss threw a water balloon at me. I was mad for a moment until I smelled something curious in the water.#$b#The face he made when I went after him to know where he got the water from looked rather annoyed, I wonder why.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.19": "Calderon eagerly reminds me daily to be careful where I go and what I do.#$b#Seems like he believes I could anger our ancestors. I wonder why?#$b#I do make sure to bring offerings to the Kings statue.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.20": "It's odd but...I am in a rather good mood and feel like relaxing a bit.#$b#I know this won't last long so I take what I can get, hah.$1",
	
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Ah, I have so many things to prepare but...it's important to take breaks and be a part of the community too.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Hm, well, while the hangout might halt my studies its fine. I do enjoy hanging out with everyone. Plus I can always chat up with Gamayun.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I collected some probes earlier today. The data can process while I go to the hangout. This way I can work while not working.$1",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Well, part of environmentalism does include studying the relationship between the environment and it's inhabitants so the hangout still counts as work.#$b#...this is my way of telling myself it's okay to take a break.",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Sun.4": "It IS true what they say about the King's roast....wow.#$b#...mmh? Oh, sorry. I really ough to think about work and not food but...",
	"Ragna.Dialogue.Sun.5": "I am confident of my progress for today so I have no bad conscience about taking a break.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Ragna.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Hmmm...what will I do today?#$b#There's so many things to study...hm, maybe today I will check how the plants are doing? Or maybe the fish? The minerals? Ohhh, I can't wait! $1",
	"Ragna.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Hello there! Wanna study the ecosystem in this pond with me?#$b#It's always exciting to get to know more about your surroundings, don't you think?",
	"Ragna.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "The flora growing here in abundance is wonderful. At my home there's similar plants and such and I am mapping out the differences and what is shared! $1",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Godwyn ===================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Godwyn.Gifttastes.Love": "For me? That is too kind, my friend.$1",
	"Godwyn.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you dearly.$1",
	"Godwyn.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Hm...I don't know what to say...$2",
	"Godwyn.Gifttastes.Hate": "...what...is...this...?$5",
	"Godwyn.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Thanks.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Oh dear...are you in need of help or why do you resort to such things...?",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "I am sure your crush will like those, friend.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Interesting. I will cheer you on from the sidelines.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "How dare you!$5",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Um...I have no need for such things.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Ah, it is here.#$b#Do not worry, it is just one of nature's little quirks.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, it has already stopped.#$b#Hm, I assume Calderon will be busy for the next few hours then.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Ah, one of nature's little quirks.#$b#Be at ease, it is nothing to worry about.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.StardropTea": "What a delightful treat, thank you.#$b#Ah...this sweet taste reminds me of my youth...back when Llyr was still alive...",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.AncientSword": "This surely has seen better days...#$b#Ah, the stories this sword must tell...I'd love to hear them.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.TreasureChest": "Are you sure you want to give it to me?#$b#Thank you kindly, @.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Introduction": "Greetings! It's nice to see a new face here.$3",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Oh dear! This is for me? Thank you kindly for such a great birthday gift, friend.$1",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Thank you kindly, my friend. It is an honor to receive such nice gift from you.$1",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thank you for this gift, friend.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Such a thoughtful gift, friend. Thank you kindly.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Ah...thank you for the gift.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Thank you...for thinking of my birthday.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "I appreciate you thinking of my birthday, friend.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Thank you fir this gift, my friend.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.0": "Amalthea is the love of my life. I feel very blessed to have her as my wife and having such a responsible son.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.1": "Running around the island again, I see?#$b#If you ever have any worries just come to me and we can talk.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.2": "We are blessed to have such a nice place to life. Nature is an amazing thing, don't you think?#$b#The trees and bushes shelter us, the water cleans us...we are provided with food and resources. Truly a blessing.$1",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.3": "I like to believe we are a tight-knit community and that there's no big secrets keeping us apart.#$b#While some things are best left unsaid I do think that there's no suspicious secrecy on this island.#$e#Sometimes the past is a hard pill to swallow, why chain the youth down to such a fate when it is already over anyway?",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.4": "I went out to the beach the other day with Amalthea.#$b#It was truly a nice stroll and time flew by way too quickly. What a pity.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.5": "Gamayun and I often talk about many things long gone.#$b#While she does not talk too much about her personal past she will eagerly share general information if you will ask her the right questions.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.6": "Hm, I think today is a rather calm day. Maybe I shall visit Barnabas at the orchard and see what he is up to.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.7": "Oh? Here again?#$b#It is always nice to see the new faces return. I hope you're enjoying your stay here.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.8": "I do believe that with time anyone can grow into a great leader.#$b#We just need to not give too much pressure and instead allow time to settle things.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.9": "Many greetings! What brings you here today, my friend? Hope whatever you're seeking will come to you.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.10": "When Calderon brought the slime into our house I admit that I was against him keeping it at first.#$b#Their natural habitat is not a merfolks house after all.#$b#I am glad we kept her though. She is quite the adorable little thing.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.11": "Do not mind Calderon if his words appear rather rude. He is quite the stern individual driven by the need to be responsible.#$b#I do hope he mellows out a bit with age though. It is alright to be silly sometimes.$1",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.12": "The world is a vast and sometimes dangerous place. It is hard to find your own little spot in it.#$b#I hope the sea god will guide your way.$1",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.13": "Being able to rebuilt and rise from the ashes is not something everyone can do. I do admire those who have the tenacity some have to always being able to get up again and continue.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.14": "Ah, nice to see you, my friend. Is everything going smooth for you?#$b#There's days that can be quite tedious and depressing but chin up, the sun will always rise again.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.15": "Sometimes I do enjoy a nice little swim in the morning.#$b#Though the moment I see Hemlock I know I should pick another day to do so. He can be quite the challenge to handle.#$b#I shall leave that to Barnabas.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.16": "You can come to me any time if you want to talk.#$b#People say that I am a good listener.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.17": "I like to read quite a bit so you will see me a lot of times in the library.$1",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.18": "Calderon is out all day so I took the moment to surprise Amalthea with a little pampering.#$b# She beamed with joy when I handed her the bouquet and told her I made her favorite food.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.19": "Ah, the weather is quite nice, don't you think?#$b#I might be outside all day, hoho.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.20": "Oh dear, what time is it? I should check on what Calderon is up to.#$b#He likes to overwork himself so I now and again check in to see if he does take some time off.",
	
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Hm, we have been doing these gatherings for a very long time.#$b#I am not quite sure when exactly, but it has been somehow always been part of the community.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Sun.1": "In busy daily life it is always nice to take some time out of your day to meet up and just hang out.#$b#Growing apart from each other happens rather quickly so this is a nice way to stay close to each other without sacrificing too much.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Sun.2": "You're always welcome to join the hangout.#$b#The more the merrier.$4",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Sun.3": "One of the top talks will always be Barnabas' roast, I think.#$b#Not sure what he does but it's always so juicy and flavourful.",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Great to see you, my friend. Are you here for a task or did you come to hang out?",
	"Godwyn.Dialogue.Sun.5": "Morvenna outdid herself again. All the food she makes for the hangout is such a delight.$4#$b#I just hope she is not overworking herself though.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Godwyn.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Hm, where's Calderon?#$b#Oh, he is out and about again, isn't he? Oh, my boy...when will you learn it is fine to take your time?",
	"Godwyn.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "What a great time!#$b#I got to eat some quite nice food. Seems like things are going well for everyone too. $1",
	"Godwyn.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Melia ====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Melia.Gifttastes.Love": "For real?! I love this!$1",
	"Melia.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you, it's nice.$1",
	"Melia.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Um...what is this...$3",
	"Melia.Gifttastes.Hate": "Ugh...that's, like, really lame...$5",
	"Melia.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Uh, whatever.$2",
	"Melia.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Uh...I wish I didn't see that...$2",
	"Melia.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "What the heckie?$3",
	"Melia.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Can you, like, not do that?2",
	"Melia.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Dang...didn't know you were so lame...$3",
	"Melia.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Nah, lame.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Green is not my color but it's kinda fun to watch the rain.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "It's over. Well, that was fun.#$b#Time to go back to what I was originally doing.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "It's that rain again, huh?",
	"Melia.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Ooohhh, yummy!$1#$b#I love this tea, @! How did you know?",
	"Melia.Dialogue.ElvishJewelry": "Wow, this looks so elegant...are you sure I can have it?$1#$b#It's amazing, thank you so much!",
	"Melia.Dialogue.StarShards": "Look at the glistening colors...it's so vibrant and beautiful...#$b#I will put this on my shelf and look at it everyday!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.RabbitsFoot": "EW! Get that away from me...$2#$b#Why would you think chopping off a poor rabbits foot would be a good idea?$5",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Melia.Dialogue.Introduction": "Melia is my name and being fashionable is my game!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Realsies?! You're hella awesome for giving me this!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "OMG! Like, thank you so much!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "What a nice birthday gift, thanks.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Thank you! It's a cool gift.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "How lame can you get...$5",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Ugh! Like, why even give me this?$5",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Welp, thanks, I guess.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Hm. Thanks for thinking of me, I guess.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Melia.Dialogue.0": "Like, the weather is totally cool right now. Don't you think?$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.1": "I love to sunbathe. Being out and about is nice and getting tanner is too, hehe!$4",
	"Melia.Dialogue.2": "Mhm, I got a lot of friends online. Having this little thing called a 'server' and all.#$b#It's really fun to hang around people who like the same stuff.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.3": "Sometimes it's hella boring here. There's not really many with similar interests.#$b#Like, the only other one who's into a something similar subculture is, like, Anette. I guess.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.4": "I had to do so mans chores today. so lame!$3#$b#Guess it's fine tho. I like mom too much to leave her hanging all alone with that stuff.$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.5": "I like to snack on things so I always have something with me, hehe. You never know when you get hungry.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.6": "That Calderon is always so serious...it's like, totally lame.$3#$b#One time he scolded me for throwing around some fruits with Moss. Called me a bad influence and all.#$b#But throwing fruits was Moss' idea...$2",
	"Melia.Dialogue.7": "Wanna take a pic with me? I love decorating them and putting them into my album.$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.8": "Love to go to Willow and see what new cool things she can get.#$b#Without her I wouldn't be able to get half my stuff like make up or all my clothes.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.9": "Mom is the best! She's, like, my best friend!#$e#Do you think I can ask her if I can buy  more clothes?",
	"Melia.Dialogue.10": "Heyah! What's up?#$b#I'm gonna hang out at Point Melodia for a bit, I think. What about you?",
	"Melia.Dialogue.11": "%Melia is too distracted to notice you. She is taking a lot of pictures with her phone.%noturn",
	"Melia.Dialogue.12": "%Melia is excitingly typing on her phone while giggling, seems like she is having a good time.%noturn",
	"Melia.Dialogue.13": "Like, OMG! My friends online just sent me this totally cute but funny videos with cats!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.14": "Too bad our weather is always warm. I'd love to try out some of these nice winter clothes that I saw online.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.15": "Do you think I should try out some wigs? There's some totally cool ones with real long curly hair and stuff.#$b#I could style even more outfits, hehe!$4",
	"Melia.Dialogue.16": "I got a big collection of perfumes and make up. I enjoy picking out what I gonna wear the coming day. It's like a ritual at this point.#$b#Plus, the perfume bottles are, like, totally cute!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.17": "Sometimes I wonder if I should try out other styles...but this one is, like, totally 'me'.#$b#It just feels 'right'.$4",
	"Melia.Dialogue.18": "I don't know what to do today. My friends online are kinda busy so the server is pretty dead right now...$3#$b#Maybe I will just go to the library and hang out there.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.19": "Mom made my favorite dish today!$1#$b#Like always it was really yummy and I love her so much for always making it! She's the best!$4",
	"Melia.Dialogue.20": "Esme is a great dancer. Sometimes I watch her for a while and she asks if I want to join in.#$b#Well, depending on the dance I might. Though I am not good at it, haha.$1",
	
	"Melia.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Heyah! Mom said she'd make my favorite dish for the hangout today so I am totally excited, hehe!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Moss said he has something cool to show me later. I wonder what it is.#$b#I hope it's not, like, something that makes Calderon scold me again...$3",
	"Melia.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Mom helped Morvenna with the food for today so I tagged along with her to help.#$b#I'm no fan of chores but I know they need to be done. Plus, we do get yummy food so it's a 'win' in my books.",
	"Melia.Dialogue.Sun.3": "I think Barnabas likes funny cat videos. I showed him a few at the hangouts and he always has a big smile when watching them.$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.Sun.4": "I always take a lot of photos at the hangout! There's an extra book I made with pages full of every hangout!$1",
	"Melia.Dialogue.Sun.5": "I slept in so hard today...oopsie. Well, good thing it's just a Sunday.$3",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Melia.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "My Mom's cooking is the best! $1#$b#She always knows what I want to eat which is amazing, don't you think?",
	"Melia.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "...sometimes I wonder if I should leave this island.#$b#There is so much to see in this world and I want to experience something new. But...#$b#...I don't want Mom to feel lonely. $2",
	"Melia.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Esme =====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Esme.Gifttastes.Love": "For me? Oh dear, this is making me so happy!$1",
	"Esme.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you! It's really thoughtful.",
	"Esme.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Hm...this isn't really vibing with me...$3",
	"Esme.Gifttastes.Hate": "....why?! Do you hate me THAT much?$5",
	"Esme.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Eh...well. Thanks for the thought.$4",
	"Esme.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Huh...is there some sort of treasure in there or why are you so eager to rummage through trash?$4",
	"Esme.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Um...this is kind of awkward...$2",
	"Esme.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Oh, I know that one. People say it comes from mermaids or something, right? Well...anyway...good luck on your courting!",
	"Esme.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Ouch! What the heck is wrong with you?$5",
	"Esme.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Hm, sorry. I don't really care for that. I prefer live action performance.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Ah...I've seen humans get scared a lot about this. It's a bit funny.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Hm...it's over already. We could do with a few days of this to be honest. That would be fun!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Ah, do you like this rain? It's really refreshing and fun to watch.#$b#Sadly it doesn't happen that often.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Mhm, what a lovely scent...it draws you right in.#$b#Ahhh, this hit the spot!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Obsidian": "There's just something about obsidian that draws me in.#$b#Plus, it's fun to craft little trinkets out of them!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Book": "Oh, nice! Now I have something to read in between training, thank you!",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Raisins": "I don't know what people have against raisins...I find them delightful!#$b#Thanks for the treat, @!$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Esme.Dialogue.Introduction": "Heyah! The name is Esme and I love to dance!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Oh wow! Are you really giving this to me? This rocks!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "This is great! Thank you so much for such a great birthday gift!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Wow, thank you. I really like this gift.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Thank you, @! I can't believe you're remembering my birthday.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Huh...what is this? This is supposed to be a gift?$3",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Um...you're not really expecting me to accept that, do you?$3",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Hm, thank you. I'm just happy you're remembering my birthday.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "What's important is that you remembered my birthday. Thank you, @.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Esme.Dialogue.spring_1": "Springs here! The birds, the bees and everything else is active and happy and-...#$b#Oh!There's this really famous classical piece about different seasons and the one for spring is really lovely to listen to.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.summer_1": "Already got plans for summer? I will spend it learning new dance moves. Summer is a really 'active' season so the moves will be very lively, hehe!",
	"Esme.Dialogue.fall_1": "Fall is more mature and somber, I feel like.#$b#Slow but powerful dance moves work best during these times.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.winter_1": "When everything sleeps or dies...a time of calmness and secrecy. Though joyfulness is glistering through the thick blanket of snow.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	"Esme.Dialogue.0": "I've been dancing since I was little. It's just something I have always enjoyed!",
	"Esme.Dialogue.1": "If you asked me if I had a favorite type of dance I wouldn't be able to answer#$b#There's just too many to pick from for very different reasons.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.2": "Have you heard of the fighting style that incorporates dance?#$b#I'd love to learn more about it!$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.3": "Sometimes I am far out in other places to perform.#$b#Then other mermaids from all over the world join in and we perform as a group.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.4": "I'd love to travel around more and see what other places have to offer when it comes to dances.#$b#Maybe...I will find some time in between work?",
	"Esme.Dialogue.5": "Heyah, @! Anything awesome happening to you lately?",
	"Esme.Dialogue.6": "My parents always told me to work hard for my dreams and I stick to it!#$b#I do know when to take breaks though so don't worry.$6",
	"Esme.Dialogue.7": "There come a few nice quirks with being a mermaid when it comes to dancing for me.#$b#More stamina, harder to get sick and injuries heal quickly. All good when you need to perform for long periods of time.#$e#Did you know that some dancers dance until their feet bled? That's pretty intense...$4",
	"Esme.Dialogue.8": "I do like the forest a lot. It's lush and has great areas to practice at without being disturbed.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.9": "Hm...Willow seems pretty busy lately. I hope she does take time off and not overwork herself...$2",
	"Esme.Dialogue.10": "I hear Bernadette talk about her dad pretty often. He sounds like a really cool guy.#$b#I don't think I can compete with such a cool dad, haha! Mine is more of a book nerd.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.11": "There's quite a few costumes I amass because of my performances.#$b#Luckily we got the space for them. Plus Anette helps me with the new ones pretty often.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.12": "Would you believe me if I told you I wanted to be an astronaut when I was little?",
	"Esme.Dialogue.13": "Good timezone!$6#$b#Anything cool that happened lately? Life on the island is a bit boring at the moment, I could use some thrill.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.14": "The flowing movements of dance always remind me of swimming, maybe that's why I like dancing so much.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.15": "I am more of a night person, but performances keep me from staying up all night, what a pity.$2#$b#The moon is really beautiful...",
	"Esme.Dialogue.16": "I've seen Moss run around with a big grin on his face more often than I can count.#$b#Each time this happens I later hear about another stunt he pulled. Ah, to be young again...",
	"Esme.Dialogue.17": "I see Hemlock hang out with Barnabas quite often.#$b#For someone who claims that Barnabas is his rival he clings to him rather tight, heh.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.18": "There's not many around anymore. Even less so those who know of the old days...its a bit sad. A lot of things were lost from that time...$2",
	"Esme.Dialogue.19": "Hm, maybe I will go to the library later to see if Gamayun has found some new books about the dances from our ancestors.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.20": "How are you doing,@? Hope the farm life is treating you well. If that endeavor fails you can always come to me and I will show you a few dance moves. Maybe you can become a dancer next?$6",
	
	"Esme.Dialogue.Sun.0": "It's nice that we have a sorta official hangout day.#$b#Then I have an excuse to use the day to relax, heh.$6",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Hmmmm...do you think Barnabas will make his roast this time around?",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Oh, I love catching up on things with the others on Sunday. This makes sure that none of us drift away from each other.$1",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Maybe I will bring a dish today too, hmmm...but what could I make on such small time frame?",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Sun.4": "I slept in a little. Didn't realize I needed it, hah.",
	"Esme.Dialogue.Sun.5": "Oh, I already took a peek at what Morvenna is preparing for the hangout, hehe!#$b#It's looking scrumptious!$1",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Esme.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "%Esme is busy practicing her dancing routine. Better not disturb her right now.",
	"Esme.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "You think there's any reason to this chaos in the world? $4#$b#Hm? Oh...nothing.$4",
	"Esme.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Cecilia =====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Cecilia.Gifttastes.Love": "Oh, how thoughtful! Thanks!$1",
	"Cecilia.Gifttastes.Like": "Thanks for the gift!",
	"Cecilia.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Hm...maybe you will keep that one.$2",
	"Cecilia.Gifttastes.Hate": "Ugh...how come you try getting rid of this by giving it to me?$5",
	"Cecilia.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Hm, thanks.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Um....could you do that somewhere else?",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "...maybe you should give that to someone else.$3",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Nice item. Who is it for?",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Hey! That hurt!$5",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Huh, what?#$b#Sorry, I'm not really interested in such things...$2",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Ah, would you look at that!$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, and there he goes...the rains over so the moss needs to be collected, eh?$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "I can already guess who's going to be busy soon, hehe.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Oh my, just the right thing to quench my thirst.#$b#What a divine taste...ah, I just love this tea. Thank you, @.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.BookQueenOfSauce": "A book overflowing with recipes for any occasion!#$b#I'll put it to good use, @.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Powdermelon": "What a lovely treat on hot days.#$b#I like to lightly salt my melon before eating for an even better taste!$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.QiSeasoning": "Oh, where did you get this?#$b#My, this will surely get used strongly.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Introduction": "Nice to meet you, the name is Cecilia.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "How kind of you! I really like it!$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Thank you, that's such a nice birthday gift.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thanks for the birthday gift, @.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "I like it, thanks for the gift.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm...how could you of all these days...give this to me on my birthday...$2",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Disappointing...why even give a gift when you don't even put any thought behind it?$2",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "....thanks for thinking of me.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Thank you for remembering my birthday.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.0": "I enjoy sunsets a lot. The way the sky is colored in such a deep hue just fills my heart with joy.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.1": "If you're ever in need of some time off you're free to visit us.#$b#I'll make you a cool lemonade to quench your thirst.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.2": "Sometimes I do enjoy rambling about old times with Gamayun.#$b#Things were very different back then and while I do miss that time I don't want to trade 'today' for anything.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.3": "Do you need anything?#$b#Give me a moment and I can help you with whatever it is then.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.4": "Our son is always so serious about everything. Sometimes I wonder if we are expecting too much of him.#$b#But then he sneaks out to meet up in secret at the cave with a certain someone and the flush he gets on his cheeks when he comes back is adorable.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.5": "Do you have a favorite dish?#$b#You know, the one that you always cook and prefer over other dishes and can never get enough of.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.6": "Would you like a bite to eat?#$b#Here, I just made this earlier![731 904 606 240 232 230 215]",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.7": "Can you keep an eye on Calderon? I don't want him to mope about and not enjoy his free time...he always seems so serious.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.8": "Should I show you some baby pictures of Calderon some time?$1#$b#The way he used to flop around with his little fins was so cute!",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.9": "My husband is pretty laid-back.#$b#If you have any issues on the island with someone just talk to him.#$e#People often don't want to bother Barnabas since he is technically our king, so Godwyn tends to step in and offers an ear to listen instead.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.10": "Hm, what dish should I make for dinner today?$2",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.11": "Morvenna came to me the other day to ask about some recipe ingredients.#$b#Poor thing looked exhausted so I offered her to help out.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.12": "What's your favorite part of the island?#$b#There's quite a bit to see here, I hope you're enjoying your stay.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.13": "There used to be a lot more of us here...but things changed.$2#$b#Even Llyr is gone...$2",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.14": "I've watched some really beautiful butterflies earlier.#$b#Their wings were glistening in the sun as if they were made of glitter.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.15": "Would you like some sweets? [203 223 233 243 279 612 731]",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.16": "Hello, @. I was just about to run some errands, do you need anything?",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.17": "There is a lot of history surrounding these lands...a lot is obscured by time. Even most of us who still remain do not remember...",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.18": "Sometimes I like to simply float above water.#$b#Feeling like a piece of driftwood that just sways with the waves.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.19": "I do like to collect and dry flowers. It's quite nice decoration and you can use it for crafts.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.20": "Hm....have you seen Caderon? I'm trying to get him to do some knitting with me but he somehow was gone rather quickly...",
	
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Sunday gatherings are pretty nice. I do enjoy coming together and having a little party basically.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Days like these are great to catch up on things. Don't you think?",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I helped Morvenna with the dishes today. There's plenty to eat and even plentier to clean later.$1",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Maybe I will ask Godwyn later for some time alone so we can watch the sunset.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Sun.4": "When life gets busy it's important to set aside some time to relax. I hope you get to have some light fun too and don't overwork yourself.",
	"Cecilia.Dialogue.Sun.5": "Barnabas' roast is really good! I love eating it with some deep sea fern salad.$1",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Cecilia.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Hi there, @!#$b#I'm just making sure everything is going well here, can't let Barnabas do all the work alone after all. $1",
	"Cecilia.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Haha, today I heard something pretty funny. $1#$b#Oh, don't mind me. Hey, have you tried Barnabas' roast yet?",
	"Cecilia.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "...sigh.$1#$b#Sorry, @. I want to be alone right now...$1",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Morvenna =================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Morvenna.Gifttastes.Love": "Oh my, thank you. This is such a nice gift.$6",
	"Morvenna.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you kindly.$1",
	"Morvenna.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Hm...I am not really fond of this one...$2",
	"Morvenna.Gifttastes.Hate": "Hrm...I'd rather have you keep it. This is just junk.$5",
	"Morvenna.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Hm, thanks...I guess.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Um...do you really HAVE to do that so out in the open...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "...I don't accept that kind of thing from anyone besides my husband.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "...put that away. Fast. Don't let my husband see you do this...$3",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Ouch! That's very rude of you.$3",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Hm, sorry. I don't really have time for such things.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.GreenRain": "You think It'll rain more often like this? Hemlock quite likes this weather.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Aw, it's over...oh well, I do know what my husband is up to for the next few hours, heh$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Hemlock really enjoys this kind of weather. He always jumps around like a little kid, hehe.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Oh, what a lovely aroma...#$b#...for me? Oh my, don't mind if I do!$1",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.MermaidsDelight": "Delightful!$6#$b#These fruits go so well with a cool drink and some salt.$1#$b#Oh, I should get Hemlock some too, he loves them as well, heh.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Emerald": "Oh!#$b#Are you sure?#$b#...it has such a lovely color.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.SeafoamPudding": "What a delightful surprise!$6#$b#Thanks for such a nice treat, @!",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Introduction": "Haven't seen you before, are you new? My name is Morvenna, I live here with my husband and kid.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Oh my! You shouldn't have! This is such a nice gift, thank you.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "For me? Thank you kindly, @. That's very thoughtful of you.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thank you, @. This is a nice gift.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Thank you for such a nice birthday gift.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm...uh....thanks...?$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "........thanks...?$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Thanks, I guess? At least you thought of my birthday?",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Hm, better than nothing, I guess...",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.spring_1": "Ah...it's spring already and I got so much to do!$2#$b#The chores seem to never stop...especially when you have a rather destructive husband and wild child, sigh...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.summer_1": "It's summer and I guess despite it being a new season everything feels the same, oh well.#$b#Time to tackle all the tasks.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.fall_1": "Oh, it's already fall?#$b#Oh dear, time flies by way too fast...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.winter_1": "Winter already, huh...#$b#...I can't believe that a whole year is about to have passed already, wow...$2",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.0": "I always tell myself to take things slow, but then my kid does something stupid and I have to fix everything again.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.1": "I know Hemlock tries his hardest to help but it's like when a whale tries to fit through a needle eye...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.2": "I overslept today and woke up to Hemlock setting the kitchen on fire because he tried making breakfast...$3#$b#Sigh...I know he just wanted to do something nice for me but it took me 2 hours to clean everything.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.3": "Hemlock picked a bunch of flowers for me. He can be romantic at times...#$b#...and in the next moment he chases after some bee that happened to bump into him, sigh.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.4": "It's hard keeping everything in check but someone gotta do it.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.5": "Hey there, anything interesting happening lately?",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.6": "I managed to get everything done earlier than I thought. Now I don't know what to do with all the time I have on my hands now, hm...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.7": "Hemlock suggested taking a little time off. Who will do the chores then? Who will make sure Moss does his homework?$2#$b#Oh, there's just always something to do...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.8": "What a nice day today, don't you agree?#$b#I might go down to the forest to take a little stroll.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.9": "Hemlock is helping Barnabas all the time. He likes to act thought and say that Barnabas is his rival or something but that's just show.#$b#You might even say they're best friends.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.10": "When Moss is at the library and Hemlock is out for a swim I tend to take a quick nap.#$b#I never get to sleep enough so I just take a nap now and again.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.11": "With my husband and child both being eager eaters I have no hard time to come up with something to cook.#$b#Neither is a picky eater so if everything fails I can just prepare some good meat and both will be happy.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.12": "As a farmer you surely have a lot on your mind too, right? Things to do, places to be...It's never enough.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.13": "I sent Hemlock to gather some deep sea fern for dinner today. That gives me enough time to tidy the house while he is gone.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.14": "Sigh....sometimes you wake up and just feel awful. Today is one of those days...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.15": "Moss tried to get out of his schoolwork again...he said that some alligator ate it.$5#$b#What do I do with this child...?$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.16": "Hm, I subscribed to one of these tidy-up type podcasts. I hope with this I can clear out all the clutter in our home.#$b#Hm, maybe I am a bit addicted to those podcasts, this is already the 5th one, but it's just so nice to listen to while you do your chores.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.17": "Oh, hello there, @. I hope %farm is doing alright.#$b#Ah, same old as ever, hm? Honestly, same here.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.18": "Sorry, I am kind of busy. There is so many things going on in my head at the moment...$2#$e#...I'm really busy...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.19": "I like to drop by the library and talk to Gamayun for a while.#$b#She kept me up-to-date on Moss' schooling and has always interesting things to say.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.20": "I know Hemlock can be tough to handle sometimes...$2#$b#...but every time I look into his big beady eyes I just can't be mad at him.$4",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.21": "Nothing says it's going to be a great day than your husband and kid both acting all innocent and as if nothing happened...$5#$e#...yes, they blew up the kitchen.$3",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.22": "Seldom do I have time to even think about something like a hobby...#$b#...now and again I do like to do some crossword puzzles or paint some tableware like mugs or plates.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.23": "As any mother it's natural to me to have a collection of small random trinkets your child often hands to you for unknown reasons.#$b#Moss however always brought the weirdest thing...I couldn't always keep it.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.24": "I'm glad when the boys are out.#$b#THen I can calmly focus on the chores and don't have to keep them from setting the kitchen on fire again.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.25": "Hm, it might be Friday but a mothers job is never done.#$b#The work does get a bit lighter during the weekend though.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.26": "How are you doing, @? Hope things are fine on your end.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.27": "I do not give out chores as a punishment.#$b#How will I ever get Moss to have a positive reaction to chores if I connect them to something bad?",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.28": "Do you thing I should cut my hair? I am unsure about it...#$b#Hemlock loves my long hair but sometimes it just really gets in the way...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.29": "Have a nice day, @. I don't really have much time to talk at the moment but the weather sure is nice, right?$1",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.30": "I prepared all I can for the dishes for tomorrow.#$b#This is going surprisingly well today...something is about to happen, isn't it?$5",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.31": "%Morvenna looks pretty distracted. She mutters something about pulling Hemlock out of an underwater cave...%noturn",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.32": "Ah, hm...hello, @.$2#$b#I am a bit in a hurry because I am still preparing my dishes for tomorrow...do you think 6 are enough?$2#$b#I know the others bring something too, but...$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.33": "I think this week I keep things light.#$b#Maybe some salad and a few side dishes only.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.34": "Gamayun showed me a few dishes that they used to make in ye olde times.#$b#Interesting how taste evolved yet somehow stayed the same too.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.35": "Will you be at the hangout tomorrow?$1#$b#I hope that I cooked enough...$2",
	
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Oh no...I hope I made enough dishes for the hangout today...$2#$b#Hemlock was supposed to cut the deep sea fern but he cut himself and saw red...$5",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Hemlock told me to not sweat it but...$2#$b#Ah...it's just so hard to not worry about things, okay? I just want things to go well.$2",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Hm, actually...today is pretty great.#$b#Maybe my standards are low but...it's quiet, no one is exploding things and I don't have a list as long as the entire island.#$b#I'd say that's a win/win.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Sun.3": "%Morvenna looks pretty tired, better leave her alone for now.",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Barnabas told me he'd make his famous roast today. I am excited.#$b#This took a big load off my shoulders when it comes to cooking for today.$6",
	"Morvenna.Dialogue.Sun.5": "Oh, I am looking forward to the hangout. Hemlock said he and Barnabas already prepared everything.#$b#I was a bit worried, yet I was able to sleep a few more hours than usual.$1",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Morvenna.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "%Morvenna seems pretty busy...maybe come back later.",
	"Morvenna.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "...hm? Oh, @.#$b#Sorry, we're just having something to eat right now, do you want something?",
	"Morvenna.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "Siiiiiigh...$2#$b#...well, despite Hemlock accidentally tripping while carrying the food over everything is fine.#$b#Luckily for us Barnabas was already there and caught it all...well...partly with his face but...still.$1",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Hemlock ==================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Hemlock.Gifttastes.Love": "Heck yeahhhh! This is a really cool thing, thank you!$1",
	"Hemlock.Gifttastes.Like": "Awesome! Thanks, dude!",
	"Hemlock.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Eugh...$2",
	"Hemlock.Gifttastes.Hate": "The heck?! Why are you giving this trash to me?$3",
	"Hemlock.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Eh...I don't know, dude.$2",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "........you better keep this place tidy. Put what you don't use back in there.$5",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": ".....I'm gonna eat that.$5",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "...how dare you. I am a married man.$5",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "You have 5 seconds head start. Make it count.$5",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "The hell is that...can you eat it?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Heck yeah! I love green rain!!$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "I hope the rain returns soon...it's really lovely.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "I met Morvenna in this kind of weather. It was really romantic...there she was, staring at me as I wrestled a shark for my next lunch...$4#$b#...then she suggested to just grab some food together.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Huh, what's this...#$b#....!$1#$b#...thank you! Wow, this tastes great!$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.MermaidsDelight": "Aw, yeah!!!$1#$b#Gosh, I love these! Barnabas grows them too and I always come buy and eat some, hehe!$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Angler": "Friend!!!$1#$b#Oh my gosh, just look at this little smile, isn't it adorable?!$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.MsAngler": "!!!!!$1#$b#Oh!$1#$b#Look at this little one, such a cutie.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.MutantCarp": "........$5#$b#....what the heck are you giving to me?!$3#$b#Look at that thing!!! Such a reminder how our precious nature gets bombarded with what humans discard without remorse!$3#$b#...you better get away from here. Quickly.$5",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Introduction": "Hm, you smell of soil and sustenance...I like that.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Rad! This is really for me? You're awesome!$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Holy smokes! Thanks a lot, dude!$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thanks for the gift!",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Rad, thanks!",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Eugh...you really want me to hate you, huh?$3",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Are you serious?! On my birthday you gift me something that hideous?$3",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Eh...at least you remembered my birthday.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "Better than nothing, I guess.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.spring_1": "Hmh, a new year is here. Time for new resolutions and-....eh, let's skip that and go straight inot already breaking them and it being like it always was.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.summer_1": "So, summer arrived were you live. For me it's like always...anything different for you?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.fall_1": "If you want I can help you scare your fellow mortals.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.winter_1": "If the snow at your place is thick enough, we can eat it!$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.0": "One time I raced with Barnabas around the Gem Sea to see who is faster...#$b#...he had to pick me up halfway because I started to fight a big jellyfish and got stung.#$b#Wait...why were we even racing for again...?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.1": "Ah yes, another great day to go for a 5 hour swimming session.#$b#I love swimming.#$b#I also love hanging out in the old ruins...but it's dangerous because of-...well. Anyway.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.2": "Moss is still too young to go with me further out. He keeps begging me to tag along but Morvenna always says no.#$b#...I know better than to go against her decisions.$2",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.3": "I have the most beautiful wife and you cannot convince me otherwise. Sorry, not sorry.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.4": "Ask me again in, like, 2 hours.#$b#My brain is focused on getting food. Like...fresh, bloody oozing meat kind of food.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.5": "Hm, if you ever need help in draining blood really quickly-...ah, sorry.#$b#Morvenna keeps telling me to not ask random people weird questions.#$b#...I don't consider this weird though, is it? I'm just saying I am really effective in it.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.6": "Please don't get on my bad side.#$b#Barnabas said he can only get me out of things so many times.#$b#......$2#$b#...I'm trying my best here, okay?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.7": "Any time I am angry I go out to swim.#$b#Morvenna says I am swimming more than I sleep nowadays...",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.8": "I see you enjoy this island quite a lot. That is great to hear.$1#$b#However, if you ever try to do anything silly like trying to take this island or sell it out...we will have a problem.$5#$b#...................$5#$b#..well, I don't think you'd do that though, right?$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.9": "...I do like this fermented...something...the funny stuff.#$b#Hm, it's 'beer', right?#$b#Does make me all calm and fuzzy, heh.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.10": "I tend to not go to the library. It's rather boring to me and honestly speaking Gamayun kind of knows exactly how to annoy me.#$b#I also do not like her idea of 'time out'.$2",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.11": "Hm, I think I will go and ask Barnabas for another race. I need to burn my pent-up energy somehow.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.12": "No, my hair is not seaweed, why do people keep asking me that?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.13": "If you want a joyous conversation partner you should rather opt for Barnabas than me.#$b#I prefer talking about kil-...I mean...I like to wrestle.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.14": "Hey, @. You smell really delicious today.#$b#....because you handle crops, haha. Yes, crops.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.15": "Sometimes all I want to do is sit there and stuff my face with food.#$b#Just, like, take my hands and shove it right into my face. Yeah.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.16": "People keep talking about Barnabas here, Barnabas there...#$b#...there's other people here too, you know?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.17": "Sometimes I am overcome with the urge to be violent. They say it's because of my ancestors.#$b#I just go out hunting then. Or, well, sometimes I get too into it, I guess. Been out for days...then Barnabas tends to come and get me.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.18": "I'd love visiting that town of yours one day, but I fear I'd be sticking out like a sore thumb.#$b#Starting with the fact that I am bioluminescent.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.19": "Hm, I guess you can call me kinda antisocial.#$b#If it weren't for the fact I have a family, I think I'd just be out in the sea swimming, wrestling beasts...",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.20": "Sorry, I am out of cool and or unhinged things to say.#$b#Moss kept me up all night rambling about some stuff in the water and how he doesn't want to go study at the library.$2",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.21": "....sigh.$2#$b#...I woke up at the shore again. I don't know how I keep doing this.$2",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.22": "How's your farm going? Any animals you're raising there?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.23": "No thought, head empty....",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.24": "Today I slept great. I dreamt that I would eat a mountain of meat and then just swim around the world.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.25": "You ever have a bad day where you feel like everything goes wrong?#$b#'Off the wrong foot'? Huh...interesting saying...",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.26": "I always bump my head with Barnabas and say that I dislike him but honestly...#$b#...he's alright. I think he's the only one who even dares to get close to me when I'm angry. Guess that counts for something.#$b#......$2#$b#....yeah. He's alright.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.27": "You know how when you want to open some packaging and they got the corner or whatever marked where you're supposed to open it and then you try and it just hecking tears the wrong way?#$b#Yeah, I hate that. Makes me want to throw away the whole thing.$5",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.28": "I tend to scream where no one can hear me.#$b#Somehow, though....Barnabas always finds me. Not sure if his ears are just that good or if he can sense me but...that's a bit eery.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.29": "Yaaaaawn....I slept, like, three hours.#$b#...I think I need an icey cold bath to properly wake up.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.30": "I promised Moss to help him with his homework.#$b#Hm...as I try to make sense of these questions I wonder where he went...",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.31": "I hope that I am a good father and husband. I know I am lacking in many things but I really try my best...$2",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.32": "How is %farm doing? I imagine it's doing great with you running around the island all the time.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.33": "If I manage to bring home a big fish Morvenna will make a big feast!#$b#So I can't talk much, business time. Very important.$1",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.34": "I sometimes help Barnabas with the Orchard. Don't tell anyone though.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.35": "I think I am having a bad day, maybe talk to me later. I just really don't feel in the mood to talk or something.$2",
	
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Morvenna always wants to go all out on the hangout food. That means we all have to help, sigh...#$b#I do tend to help her with chores but I break more than what I provide in help so Morvenna tends to shoo me out most times.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Hm. You will come by at the hangout spot?#$b#Morvenna tried really hard on her dish, so you better like it.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I almost overslept today. Don't tell Morvenna, but I kind of stayed out in the water half of the night when she was already asleep.#$b#...n-no reason. I just, uh, felt like swimming.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Sun.3": "I like to go down into the trench that is near this island.#$b#There's really funky stuff down there, you know?",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Hm, the sea has been pretty rough lately. Seems like something is about to happen, huh.",
	"Hemlock.Dialogue.Sun.5": "The wind is catching up, I am sure it wants to tell us something...who knows.#$b#This kinda vague stuff is more up Gamayuns alley.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Hemlock.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "WHAFf FWYu WFant? I'm EAtign, FOrry.$6",
	"Hemlock.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "I am-! Hrmpf-!$3#$b#No...it's not like I WANTED to help him or something...$2",
	"Hemlock.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "..I-I am sure he will notice me some time...right?$2",
	"Hemlock.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.003": "...and then I fought a really huge squid, can you believe that?$1#$b#Oh! Hey, @! Well, anyway! Barnabas, I tell you!#$b#There's stuff going on down there, I say!",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Moss =====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Moss.Gifttastes.Love": "Huh? This is actually kinda cool, thanks.$1",
	"Moss.Gifttastes.Like": "Hm, looks neat.$1",
	"Moss.Gifttastes.Dislike": "...what is that.",
	"Moss.Gifttastes.Hate": "Ew, get that away from me.$5",
	"Moss.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Eh, it's fine, I guess.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Wow, you actually do that kinda thing?",
	"Moss.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "What the heck? Why are you giving me this?$5",
	"Moss.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": ".............freak.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "I'm the right size to make it hurt really badly when I bite!$5",
	"Moss.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Nah.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Finally! I love this kind of rain.$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Aw, it's already over....why can't it, like, rain like this every day?",
	"Moss.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "It's back! I love this rain, man.$1#$b#I'm SO gonna go and look for all the greenery, hehe.$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Hm? Oh...wow! This is actually pretty tasty.$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.MermaidsDelight": "My Dad got me hooked on these.#$b#Did you know their insides are a really nice yellow color?#$b#%Moss stuffs the whole fruit into his mouth.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.CategoryMilk": "Yuck!$5#$b#Get that stuff away from me!$5",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Dolls": "Cool! Now I can go and place it around the house to scare Mom, hehe!$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Bomb": "Ohhh yeah, now we're talking!#$b#Excuse me, I have something to plan, heh.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Moss.Dialogue.Introduction": "Mom said to not talk to strangers...#$b#...you seem lame enough so I gonna talk to you anyway.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Wow, you actually got me a pretty cool gift, thank you.$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "This is for me? Wow, it's great!$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thanks for the gift, you did pretty alright.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Acceptable, yes yes. Thanks for the gift.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Ew...how dare you give me this junk on my birthday?$5",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Huh...you don't honestly expect me to accept this as a gift, do you?$5",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Hm...fine. I accept it.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "....better than nothing, I suppose.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Moss.Dialogue.0": "I'm gonna go with Dad to dive and get some fish later.#$b#I love going out with him, he always gets so worked up and chases things in the water. It's funny.$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.1": "I played with the ferrets earlier. They all have a devious personality, I love it.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.2": "Mom is always so overworked, I don't know why.#$b#Maybe it's because Dad acts like a wild animal at times or because I like building forts in the house and then they all collapse......#$b#....nah.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.3": "I like to use the pearls I find around the island as marbles and shoot them around.#$b#Sometimes they hit people.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.4": "There's a lot of stuff that gets washed ashore at Point Melodia.#$b#I like to rummage through it to find something to play with.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.5": "The librarian is always so dry when it comes to lesson, it's boring.#$b#But if I don't pay attention she zaps me...$2",
	"Moss.Dialogue.6": "I think I wanna be like my Dad when I grow up.#$b#Running around like a wild animal sounds like no responsibilities.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.7": "Mom scolded me the other day because I made Dad angry.#$b#She said it's not funny to make him think a shark said he was lame.#$b#....Dad is good at wrestling sharks though.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.8": "Whenever Dad is angry he goes off into the water to cool off.#$b#Most times that involves King B finding him and talking to him, not punching things. Boring.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.9": "What are you staring at?#$b#If you don't wanna fight then bugger off.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.10": "The things on this island are quite intriguing, right?",
	"Moss.Dialogue.11": "%Moss ignores you in favor of a bunch of pearls he just found on the ground.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.12": "Sorry, pretty busy. Play with someone else.#$b#Busy with 'what'? Hey now, are you my Mom or something? Stop snooping.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.13": "%Moss throws a few pearls at you when you pass by.#$b#Think fast! [797]",
	"Moss.Dialogue.14": "Hey, look what I found the other day! Isn't it cool? [852 909 848 928 769 768 386]",
	"Moss.Dialogue.15": "If you ever get lost here on the island...make sure to not call for my name. I won't help you.#$b#There's things out there a kid can't do anything against.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.16": "Do it like the bees and buzz off.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.17": "You look rather...energetic.#$b#Good for you. How about you help me paint these big round rocks like soccer balls?",
	"Moss.Dialogue.18": "I've been skipping stones at the lake earlier. My Dad came by and tried it too but straight-up threw the rocks into the water...",
	"Moss.Dialogue.19": "Hm, maybe I will go down to the shore and just kick crabs back into the water. This island is pretty boring most of the times...",
	"Moss.Dialogue.20": "King B offered me a gem once when he asked if I was hungry and I said yes.#$b#Not sure what he's seeing in them....I couldn't even bite a chunk off.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.21": "Just imagine I have something really cool to say, because....hm. I just can't think of anything right now.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.22": "I tried skipping class today and got instantly teleported straight into the library....dang it.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.23": "...I've got nothing to say. Made the mistake to stay awake half of the night so I am really tired, ugh.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.24": "Mom told me to clean my room but I just stuffed int all under the bed and got scolded.#$b#Cleaning isn't one of my favorite things, sigh.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.25": "Do you think I can trick my Dad into doing my homework?",
	"Moss.Dialogue.26": "I'm gonna go and jump off of the cliff into the water.#$b#It's fun, I do it with Dad all the time!$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.27": "%farm...that's yours?#$b#Interesting...Mom looks at these 'home living' kinda magazines and stuff all the time and I've seen that name in there often. I'm impressed.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.28": "I am kind of bored...what do you usually do when you're bored?#$b#...no, I don't wanna go to your farm and hoe your dirt for you.$2",
	"Moss.Dialogue.29": "%Moss lets out a big yawn as he stares at you.#$b#Hm? Oh, it's you. How do you manage to function with such little sleep all the time, I could never...",
	"Moss.Dialogue.30": "I got Bubblegum to shoot pearls with me. Who knew she could shoot them out like bullets, cool!$1",
	"Moss.Dialogue.31": "Not today, @. I got extra homework because I tried tricking Dad into doing my homework for me and Gamayun found out.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.32": "I might just slip out later and hide somewhere underwater. I really don't wanna help Mom clean out the pantry...",
	"Moss.Dialogue.33": "Dads out to do his thing again. I don't know what his thing is but King B said to not worry.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.34": "I was suggested to meditate with Dad once.#$b#I don't have anger issues, I see no reason to uselessly sit around and do nothing.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.35": "Tag, you're 'it'.",
	
	"Moss.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Mom made me help cook the food for todays hangout...I ate some of it when she didn't look.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Sun.1": "I ran out towards the Orchard before Mom could rope me into helping her cook again...",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Hm...maybe I will skip the hangout today. I wanna explore the underwater cave I found the other day.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Dad grabbed me the moment I wanted to run out of the house...man, no way I can escape helping Mom today, huh.",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Today I decided to be a good kid.#$b#Well, maybe I was bribed with some delicious treat but hey...",
	"Moss.Dialogue.Sun.5": "%Moss sticks his tongue out at you.#$b#Bet you can't catch me, your big boots are foll of mud.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Moss.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "....#$b#....#$b#........can't you see that I am reading?",
	"Moss.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "...hm. The grown-ups always talk about things they tell me I don't understand yet.#$b#...when will they understand that leaving me out on things makes me feel weird too?",
	"Moss.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "It's alright today. Everyone's busy chatting so I can do what I want, hehe!",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Calderon =================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Calderon.Gifttastes.Love": "Hm? Interesting...that's quite useful. Thanks.",
	"Calderon.Gifttastes.Like": "Appreciated. Thanks.",
	"Calderon.Gifttastes.Dislike": "...ugh.$5",
	"Calderon.Gifttastes.Hate": "Am I a joke to you?$5",
	"Calderon.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Hm, adequate.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Hrm...can you do that somewhere else...$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Uh...what's this?",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "...why are you giving me this...$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "There will be a time and a place and you will not see it coming, fool.$5",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "I have to pass on that.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Nothing out of the ordinary here.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Well, time to go and hunt for the moss. Goodbye.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "The rains always quite the spectacle.#$b#Loaf likes the moss so I will be busy once the rain is over.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Moss": "You...give me...moss?#$b#.......#$b#Hm, quite adequate. Good job.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Huh...this is strangely...delightful. Thank you.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.MysticSyrup": "The properties of this syrup....ah, never mind.#$b#I humbly accept this gift, @.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.MossSoup": "Oh! Well, if you excuse me...I got to go somewhere while this is still hot.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.MossySeed": "!!!#$b#With this....I could grow...$4#$b#Ahem...I shall humbly accept this gift. Now, if you'll excuse me...I shall tend to grow this seed into a great tree.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Dried": "Eugh...#$b#....no....$2#$b#...how devious of you to give this to me.$2",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Introduction": "Hrm...so you're that new guy everyone keeps mentioning...#$b#...well, the name's Calderon.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Hm...giving me a birthday gift on my birthday...well done. I like it.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Quite nice, @. This is a good birthday gift.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Acceptable. I am impressed you even got me something.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Alright. I do like it, I shall accept your gift.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "This is like a hit straight to the face, disgusting.$5",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Get out of my face, @. How dare you present me such utter trash for my birthday!$5",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "....at least you got me 'something'...",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "...well, hm. Interesting what you deem acceptable as a gift...",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Calderon.Dialogue.spring_1": "Judging by how you look you're already knee-deep in the mud to get ready for the season, huh?",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.summer_1": "Melons are a summer favorite. I admit I do like them too.$1#$b#Barnabas does grow some underwater breed of them that taste quite nice.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.fall_1": "We do enjoy weaving corn dolls during this season to present to the almighty sea.#$b#Our King would usually get some too but he declines offerings and prefers sharing among us.#$b#I do quite like that idea myself.$3",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.winter_1": "I have been in the cold waters in other regions before.#$b#I do not mind it at all. The water is quite refreshing.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Calderon.Dialogue.0": "I am quite busy, what do you want?#$b#I have my schedule all figured out, is that so surprising?",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.1": "I do help out mother quite a lot. Chores are quickly done when the workload is shared.#$b#Father does not want any help however, while I want to help him too I do accept his decision.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.2": "I often accompany Barnabas when I have time. I admit, it is not as much as I would like to but he told me he appreciates it nonetheless.$1#$e#Hm? What we do?#$b#Well, I help him with all kind of things. Like...fixing stuff. And uh...well, stuff.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.3": "I've set myself a goal for the week and I plan to reach it.#$b#Well, it's set up  of different things like chores, duties and the like.$1#$b#No, relaxing is not part of that list.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.4": "I have no time to waste.#$b#If you want to talk to me you have to do so while I walk, @.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.5": "Great pleasure befalls me when I get a lot of work done.$1#$b#Being busy is better than being bored.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.6": "I have my life figured out. Plans are in action, decisions are being made.$1#$b#...well, I do squeeze in some time for uh...Loaf...sometimes...but that is within my expectations!$4",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.7": "If something is possible or not is for me to decide, not the laws of nature.$1#$b#No, I have not 'almost died' in the past because of that mindset.$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.8": "My mother often tells me to slow down, but there is no rest for the wicked.#$b#Not that I am wicked...but you catch my drift.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.9": "Hm...I wonder if I should get Bubblegum more toys...$1#$b#She deserves only the best, my little cute-...$1#$b#.....$4#$b#....you did NOT hear that just now, got it?$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.10": "Do you have set yourself some goals for the season?#$b#It's important to keep yourself engaged and eager to do things so everything will progress.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.11": "Hm, while I do not share Barnabas' eagerness to consume inedible matter I am quite impressed.$1#$b#He is quite the interesting person, isn't he?",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.12": "I usually swim five laps around the island in the early morning.#$b#It brings my blood in action and calms my nerves.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.13": "Sigh....what do you want?$2#$b#...I am not really the talkative type, why do you seek me out?",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.14": "Hrm...#$b#...what is it?$2#$b#I am on an important mission right now so I cannot talk. I need to collect moss for-...#$b#..n-never mind.$4",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.15": "%Calderon is busy checking off his list of errands and just passes you by.%noturn",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.16": "People keep trying to tell me jokes to make me laugh.#$b#It's not that I don't find things amusing...the jokes are just too bad.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.17": "I'm spending a fair amount of time in the library.#$b#I enjoy reading up about the past and educating myself on it.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.18": "I've got no time for fun activities. There's a lot of things that need to be done and a responsible adult will of course work before enjoyment.#$b#What? I'm being serious here.$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.19": "I talked to Gamayun quite a bit lately. Do you know anything about shadowfolk?#$b#Hm...well, I'm just asking...for no reason...$4#$b#...just to understand better. Or something...$4",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.20": "Well, who do we have here? How's %farm doing?#$b#I'm sure with all the time you run around here you have it all figured out.#$b#Is it some kind of magic you use to get so much done in a day?$3",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.21": "I do enjoy putting things in order. Fold my clothes the right way. Color coordinate. By choice. By choice.#$b#Of course, by choice. I don't have to, I just...find it calming.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.22": "What are your plans for today? Forage the island? Mine some nodes? Maybe you're here to help Barnabas with his work?$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.23": "Abhorrent to think about that there's people out there who just spontaneously decide on things.#$b#Where is the structure? The bullet points? How can I stay calm without my list?",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.24": "Weekends hold little meaning to me. I always keep busy so there is no day off.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.25": "I almost ran out of things to do today. Luckily Barnabas came by and asked me for help. Crisis averted.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.26": "I, too, indulge in things sometimes.#$b#Like sorting my pens by what color they write in or pencils by size.$1",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.27": "Hrm...#$b#...nothing is wrong. I just don't feel like talking.$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.28": "You're actually out and about to get things done? Impressive.#$b#I'm not against having fun but I do believe that work needs to get done first.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.29": "Hrm...what?#$b#Ah, it's you, @.#$b#...hm, maybe I'm just feeling under the weather but-...oh, never mind. I shouldn't bother you with it.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.30": "If you ever need help getting your things in order just ask me.#$b#I greatly enjoy doing these kind of things.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.31": "I went out and got Bubblegum a few new toys. She really likes them.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.32": "Hrm...what it is?#$b#I've got some errands to run but I guess I can talk to you for a moment.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.33": "I had a dream last night that I had no list ready to tackle and I was not a mess? Actually, I was pretty calm.#$b#Dreams are really odd, hm.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.34": "Hm, if I switch a few things around I can make room for another task...maybe gather some more moss for Loaf...#$b#......oh. Huh, @, I didn't notice you there.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.35": "%The scent of something sweet and savory hits your nose. You see Calderon stuffing his face with some sort of filled bun as he quickly walks past.%noturn",
	
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Sun.0": "......the hangout. Right, that is today.#$b#Of course I took note of that, it's nothing new. Besides, Loaf is g-....#$b#......$4#$b#...get lost.$4",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Hm...I do have the hangout on my list, yes.#$b#...well, just standing around doing nothing seems, uh, wasteful but...#$b#.....$4#$b#...never mind.$2",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I've got things on my plate.#$b#Hrm...well...$4",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Don't look at me like that.#$b#I won't hit you with another one liner about productivity.",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Sun.4": "%Calderon seems to be in deep thoughts, he doesn't notice you.%noturn",
	"Calderon.Dialogue.Sun.5": "If I could just....hm...%noturn#$b#%Calderon looks flustered in some way, not noticing you.%noturn",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Calderon.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Hush!$2#$b#L-leave me alone...I uh...I...I-I can talk to them if I want to, okay?!$4",
	"Calderon.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "%Calderon isn't noticing you. He is too busy trying to not be too nervous while talking to Loaf.",
	"Calderon.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Amalthea =================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Amalthea.Gifttastes.Love": "For me? That is really kind of you.$1",
	"Amalthea.Gifttastes.Like": "Thank you kindly, dear.$1",
	"Amalthea.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Ah...hm.$2",
	"Amalthea.Gifttastes.Hate": "Oh..uhm...you shouldn't have...$3",
	"Amalthea.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Thanks.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Oh, dear...if you're that desperate for some food, just tell me.$2",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Don't make this old gal all flustered.$1#$b#Thank you, but I am not on the market, my dear.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "I am sure you will find some lucky person who you can give this too, dear.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Hm.$5$#$b#Be careful or else...$5",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Oh, I am deeply regretful to inform you of this but I am otherwise occupied already. Maybe next time.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.GreenRain": "I have heard this rain is good for your skin.#$b#Who knows? It does make the foliage even greener for a while though.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, it's over...a true pity.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Hm, I see the kids running around eagerly every time this happens.#$b#There's also the quirk of getting a lot of moss. Nature is truly kind.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Why thank you, dear.#$b#I really enjoy this tea, it's quite sweet but in a good way.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.CookingCategory": "What a great dish! You've done such a good job cooking, dear.#$b#Quite scrumptious.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.FaveMinerals": "Look at the colors on this one! It's quite lovely, dear. Thank you for giving it to me.#$b#I will put it in my room as decoration.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Introduction": "Greetings, dear.$1#$b#I am Amalthea and I live here on the island. Nice to meet you.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Oh! I cannot put into words how much you move me...a birthday gift? Thank you so so much!$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "Aw, you're such a sweet thing. Thank you so much for such a great birthday gift.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "Thank you for remembering my birthday, my dear.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "A birthday gift? Thank you kindly, dear.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Hm...well, thank you for the gift, I guess...$2",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Oh...um...I'm not sure what to say...$2",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "It's the thought that counts so I gladly accept this gift.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "I appreciate you thinking of my birthday, dear.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.spring_1": "Spring is such a quaint and serene season. There's this feeling in your chest where you know things wake up and everything gets bright and lively again.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.summer_1": "Well, this island is always in a tropical climate so I might be biased but Summer sure is a happy and lovely season.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.fall_1": "Fall tends to be the favorite season of many. I can understand that. The leaves get extra colorful and the air has this crispiness to it that no other season brings.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.winter_1": "When everything slumbers then we know it is Winter. Many see it as a 'dead' season but I think everything has it's meaning so surely this season does as well.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.0": "A lovely day on a lovely island.#$b#This just calls for a nice little stroll around the island, don't you think?",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.1": "Ah, there you are.$1#$b#It's lovely seeing you here. I hope this island fills you with as much joy as it does for me.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.2": "Ever took a little stroll underwater?#$b#At this time of the day it's really lovely!$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.3": "Do you prefer big communities or small ones?#$b#Lately I've heard a few stories about cities like Zuzu that are really big but I can't imagine living there.#$b#Maybe it's just because all I know is this island, hm.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.4": "Maybe it's a bit cliche but I do enjoy cooking a lot.#$b#Back when more humans visited this island I often cooked for many people.#$b#Now it's not so many but I still like it.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.5": "Thanks to Bernadette I found myself owning a mobile phone.#$b#There are a lot of 'blogs' out there that share their favorite recipes and I love it.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.6": "Barnabas often gives me some of the fruits in his orchard. I then turn them into curd or jam and the like and share them with the others.#$b#This way the whole community gets a taste of it.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.7": "There is no grocery store on the island but that's fine by me.#$b#All we need either grows right on the island of Willow will order for us.#$b#You should visit her some time, she's a nice kid.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.8": "My daughter is often out and about.#$b#I can see her yearning for the Deep but she is still so young...$2#$b#...besides, there's nothing there anymore.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.9": "I love when my daughter and I have one of those pampering days.#$b#She got the idea from the internet where you basically just have something like your very own Spa day.#$b#Well, it might just be an excuse to loaf around and indulge ourselves but I see it as a time where I can bond with her.$1#$e#What's bad about indulging ourselves once in a while anyway?",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.10": "Do you have a favorite dish you always fall back to?#$b#I admit, I have a few. They just always work, you know?#$b#I never mess them up and they always taste great, teehee!$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.11": "Lovely weather, right?#$b#I might just go down to the shore and lay in the sun for a while.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.12": "How is your day going? I hope it's great!$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.13": "Gamayun is quite the wise figure in our community. A pillar of many you might say.#$b#She has been around the longest now, already serving under our late King...",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.14": "Ah, I still remember when Melia was a little baby...she was so cute!$1#$b#Ah, don't tell her I said that, oops.$3",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.15": "Hm, oh? Wait, it's %time already?#$b#Oh dear, I really gotta get going then. Still got a few errands to run.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.16": "Sometimes it feels like the household chores are never ending...but they do end.#$b#Heh, it's just an endless cycle of rind-and-repeat.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.17": "Hm...what do I make for dinner today? Oh...$2#$b#...maybe I'll go and ask what Melia feels like.#$e#If all things fail I can just go and make one of my fall-back recipes.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.18": "Having a family is nice. There's been hard times and struggles but just as many good times.#$b#When I held Melia in my arms for the first time I cried a lot, hah, a bit embarrassing, yeah.#$b#It just fills me with so much joy seeing her grow up and going her own way.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.19": "I like having my little recipe cards.$1#$b#I know in todays times you can have everything digital and what-not but I see it as a little hobby to collect them.#$b#It's soothing to sort them and add more, I even write my own ones.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.20": "Hello, my dear. How's life treating you lately? I hope good things will come your way.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.21": "My husband has been gone for years but I still miss him.#$b#He sadly got sick and died way too soon.$2",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.22": "Melia told me about some new trend among the younger crowd.#$b#Do you think it would be weird if I tried it too? Is it still considered 'cringe' when parents try to fit in with their children?",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.23": "I tend to wake up pretty early usually, but there's times where even I sleep in.#$b#Good thing Melia is so independent that she can just carry on when that happens.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.24": "Weekends approaching but here I am juggling the household like always.#$b#Oh well, I know how to handle it. Would just be nice to be able to just loaf around and do nothing.#$e#Then again I cannot stand looking at an untidy place so I just naturally start doing what needs to be done.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.25": "Hey there, @. Anything planned for the weekend?#$b#I'm sure as a farmer you have quite a lot to do all the time, eh?",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.26": "Do you need anything, my dear?#$b#I'm glad to help out if you do.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.27": "Anything on your mind?#$b#I'm here if you want to talk about it, it's always good to get it off of your chest if something is bothering you.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.28": "Lovely day, isn't it?#$b#I think I might go ask Barnabas if he wants to collect some seashells with me.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.29": "Hm, I somehow ended up staying awake way too long...$1#$b#The book I read was just so good...oopsie.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.30": "Things need to get done even if you don't like them.#$b#The best thing is to have some work-around that tricks you into doing that pesky task you hate so much.#$b#I found myself that mere reward-based ways don't work on me...my brain just knows that I can get what I want even without doing the task. Sigh.$2",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.31": "Today I decided to take things slow.#$b#Well, I will still do my chores but I will go at a slow pace and take moments to relax.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.32": "I like a simple breakfast.#$b#Maybe some fried egg on toast with some sausage and seaweed.#$b#Or...scrambled eggs and some cooked fish...hm.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.33": "%Amalthea seems pretty lost in thoughts, better not disturb her.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.34": "Oh hey, @. Good to see you. Here, have this. [201 204 205 197 210 202 211 225 235 242]",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.35": "I think I will drop by the library later.#$b#Gamayun said she'd pick some new books to read and so far it was always worth the troubles going.$1",
	
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Hmmm, maybe I will cook some nice hearty bean hotpot for the gathering...",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Oh, I have so many ideas for some dishes but so little time to try them all out.#$b#Maybe I will take the hangout as an excuse to cook them.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I've heard you have an author in your town?#$b#Hm, What was the name...I'd love to read some book of them.$1",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Sun.3": "%Almathea seems to be distracted by something, not noticing you at first.#$b#...hm...ah!#$b#Oh, it's you, @. How are you doing?#$b#Sorry, I was just thinking about a few things...",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Sun.4": "We have a quite rich and active ecosystem here around the island.#$b#Barnabas often tells me about it, teehee. I'm sure some marine biologist or something would be happy to come study it.",
	"Amalthea.Dialogue.Sun.5": "You think it would be a good time for a little nap?",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Amalthea.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Heh, look at her go.#$b#It fills my heart with joy when I see her happy like this.$1",
	"Amalthea.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Cecilia came to me earlier and told me about something funny-..oh?#$b#Hey, @! What a nice day we have, right?",
	"Amalthea.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Loaf =====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Loaf.Gifttastes.Love": "Aw, thank you! I love it!$1",
	"Loaf.Gifttastes.Like": "Thanks! I'll find a good use for it.",
	"Loaf.Gifttastes.Dislike": "Huh...?$2",
	"Loaf.Gifttastes.Hate": "Why, uh...are you giving me this...$2",
	"Loaf.Gifttastes.Neutral": "Hm, I guess I can do something with it...$3",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Oh? Found something useful yet?",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.RejectBouquetNotDatable": "Uh, why are you giving me this? Can I eat it?",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.RejectMermaidPendantNotDatable": "Funny, my kind has something that looks kinda like this for-...#$b#....$2#$b#...welp, gotta go.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Ouch!$2#$b#Why are you doing this to me?$2",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.RejectMovieTicket": "Movie...ticket? Um, I'm not so sure about that...sorry.$3",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Hm, I find this rain a bit odd but nothing too bad.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "It's over...nothing really happened besides there being a lot of delicious moss.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Well, it's not the first time I've seen this rain. I know I don't have to worry about it.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.StardropTea": "Wowzah! This tastes great, thank you!#$b#Hm...I wonder if I could get my hands on more so I can-...uh! I gotta go!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Moss": "Moss!$1#$b#Moss is so versatile, I love it! You can eat it just as-is, make soup, cook  it into a stew...$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.MossSoup": "Yummy! Thank you for the treat!$1#$b#This is one of my favorite dishes!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.RainbowShell": "Woooow! Look at the pretty colors!$1#$b#I know it's called a 'rainbow shell' but these strong blue hues always remind me of C-...$4#$b#....um, forget that last part.$2",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Slime": "Uh....$2#$b#I'll pass on that...there's just something about slime that, uh, doesn't sit right with me...$2",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Introduction": "Hello!!$1#$b#The name is Loaf! Um! You're not scared of me, are you? I haven't seen you around on the island so I was just making sure.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayLoveA": "Gasp! Is this really for me? It's so nice of you to think of my birthday!$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayLoveB": "A birthday gift!$1#$b#Thank you so much! I will treasure it!$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayLikeA": "You remember my birthday? Thank you!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayLikeB": "Thank you so much for this birthday gift. It's so nice that you thought if me.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeA": "Aw...to get this on my birthday...$2",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayDislikeB": "Why...are you giving me something like this on my birthday?$2",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralA": "Hm, not sure what to do with it yet but I appreciate that you thought of me!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.birthdayNeutralB": "...hm. Thank you for remembering my birthday, @.",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Loaf.Dialogue.spring_1": "Ready for a new harvest season? I heard you got quite some farm going!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.summer_1": "Summer is up ahead. Will you grow a lot of melons this year?",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.fall_1": "Hm...pumpkin soup sounds good right now.#$b#Will you have pumpkins on your farm this year? I heard you can carve funny faces into them!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.winter_1": "Brrr...I've come to dislike winter. There's not much around and it's so desolate outside with all the snow...#$b#What does a farmer do when it's winter and no crops thrive?",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Loaf.Dialogue.0": "Eureka! Here I was thinking if I will have a good or bad start of the week and there you come and greet me!$1#That totally means this week will be awesome!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.1": "A new week and a lot of unknown variables waiting for me...#$b#...I might be the only of my kind on this island but I feel very welcome here.#$b#Though I still feel anxious at times...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.2": "Do you think the plastic bag drifting in the wind ever got asked if it was alright to write about their life?",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.3": "I tend to just spontaneously decide what I want to do during the day.#$b#One time I was just walking around and King B asked me if I wanna go down into the dungeon.#$b#I wasn't really sure at first but he's really strong so I went with him and we found a lot of cool stuff!$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.4": "I like collecting little trinkets.#$b#A lot of things get washed up ashore so I pick and choose what to keep.#$b#The rest of the stuff I bring to King B to see if he can find any use for it.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.5": "Gamayun taught me how to write and read human language.#$b#...dwarven language too. And something about the basics of magic circles. And, uh...my brain was about to get fried if King B hadn't distracted her.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.6": "The other day when I sat down at the pier of Point Melodia I stared into the water and swore something was looking back at me.#$b#When I told the others they checked but found nothing.#$e#Maybe I am seeing things. I'm sure King B would know if someone was hiding in the water to be all shady or something...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.7": "Hm, I think today I won't do anything...#$b#...or moreover I don't plan to do anything. If something happens to happen then, well, I WILL do something.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.8": "Thick books aren't my thing.#$b#Though I did find out I like to write little poems! Gamayun tried to find some books that might interest me after all and while doing so I stumbled upon a book about poems and really liked it!$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.9": "I went to check if there were other caves around like mine but so far nothing.#$b#It's not like I want to move or anything, I was just curious.#$e#Maybe some more shadow people will move in if there were nice caves like mine.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.10": "I was thinking about getting a pet...but I don't think I am ready for such a serious commitment.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.11": "I like it when you come around and say hello.$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.12": "What is a good word that rhymes with 'existential dread'?#$b#...I already used 'torn to shreds' a few lines before, hm.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.13": "Besides poems I do like to paint.#$b#King B showed me how to make paint with things from nature so half the time I don't even actually paint but just mix colors.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.14": "You ever crave something specific and cannot make any compromises? Yeah, that's me with sleep.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.15": "I tried sorting out my trinket collection but just like last time I cannot part with anything...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.16": "Those little ferrets that run around the island like to steal my food when I am not looking.#$b#They're cute, but full of mischievous thoughts.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.17": "I found a really round pebble today!#$b#It's really smooth and nice to hold in your hand.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.18": "I've heard there's other shadows like me out there that go against the old traditions and biases.#$b#I wonder if they found people to lean onto like I did...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.19": "Even when I don't follow the generic shadow people route of occupation I can still hold a weapon and fight.#$b#I was raised in that kind of environment but it wasn't really anything for me.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.20": "It's not that I am a pacifist or anything but I am generally a type of person who prefers talk over action.#$b#I do not hesitate to defend what I deem important just so you know. Let it be property or people I care for.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.21": "I am glad that I slipped into that random boat in the night to take a nap.#$b#I was pretty devastated when I woke up and found myself in the middle of the ocean though.#$b#While I drifted there for Yoba knows how long I was found by King B and he took me to the island.#$e#He offered to build me a house but as the shadow that I am I still prefer dark, cold places....so he found this cave for me!$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.22": "Looking good today, @!$1#$b#Hope you have a really great day!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.23": "Dot, dot, circle, circle...#$b#.................#$b#...oh! Hey there, @! Sorry, I was a bit in thought and didn't notice you.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.24": "I really love this island!#$b#I've seen a few over-world places already and some beaches but this island is still something else.#$b#Plus, there's almost no litter. Everyone does their best to fish out what little there sadly does swim around...#$e#...It's insane how much waste humans tend to mindlessly throw away. The ocean has so much of it...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.25": "A lovely day, isn't it?#$b#I really like sun bathing! Oh...if I had to fully live underground again I think I'd shrivel up like a raisin...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.26": "Man, I've spend my entire day at the forest the other day.#$b#I just wanted to get some flowers and maybe sit at the shore for a bit but then Calliope came by and soon after King B too and we somehow ended up chatting all day!#$b#The food Calliope had brought was really nice too, hehe!$1",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.27": "Hm, do you think I should add more stuff to my cave? I am not really an interior designer person or whatever but...there's really a lot of unused space, huh.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.28": "I love the sound of the soft waves hitting the shoreline.#$b#It makes for great background noise to sleep and settle down in general.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.29": "I do enjoy the rain just as much as sunny days.#$b#The possibility of rain means there maybe even be some 'special' rain coming...#$e#...what can I say? I do love me some moss soup.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.30": "I don't really have any specific plans or some sort of job so weekends are like any other day to me.#$b#I DO like the hangouts on sundays thought.#$b#Lovely food everyone is always cooking, hehe.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.31": "%Loaf is rubbing their hands together as they carry around a bundle of mushed up moss.#$b#Hm? Oh, @! Would you like something too? I was planning to make some soup for later.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.32": "Moss soup...mashed moss...fried moss balls...#$b#%Loaf is in food heaven thinking about what they can make out of moss. Better to leave them be.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.33": "Ah, sorry, @. Surprisingly enough I am kinda occupied with something else. King B asked me to check something out underground so I'm planning to take it seriously.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.34": "Would you like a peanut?#$b#A packing peanut.#$b#Oh, humans don't usually eat those, huh...",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.35": "Ohhh....I really wanted to say something cool to Calderon and somehow it all just ended up in stutters...$2",
	
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Sun.0": "I wonder if I should bring moss soup to the gathering...#$b#...or maybe a moss dip?",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Sun.1": "I had a really good grilled fish the other time I went to the hangout.#$b#That's the great thing about communities...there ought to be some that are really good in cooking!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Sun.2": "You wanna come to the hangout?#$b#If not that's ok, we meet up every Sunday.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Hmmm...how does King B always pull it off doing so many thing at once?#$b#Even the hangout...he just managed to naturally rally everyone up to come and hang.#$e#...and the other day I heard him wonder if he's good enough. He is! And I am sure the others think that as well.",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Any plans for today? Hope your Sunday is going to be great!",
	"Loaf.Dialogue.Sun.5": "I woke up several times during the night....man, I hope I don't sleep in too hard next time.#$b#It's enough to sleep bad one single night to just go and mess up your sleep schedule...",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Loaf.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "%Loaf fidgets around as they try to talk about something cool with Calderon.",
	"Loaf.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Hm...do you know of any pick-up lines?#$b#Oh! Um! ...$2#$b#Well...I heard from the others you need to say something cool to impress your crush, so...$2",
	"Loaf.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== LadyMidday ===============================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "...you ought to control yourself more...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "....foolish.$3#$action AddBuff 27 -2",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.GreenRain": "...ah, everyones worries...hm. Unneeded, yet enticing.",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Once again...the world continues.",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Maybe...you should go out and work either way...#$b#...what is there to worry anyway?",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.Introduction": ".................#$b#.................#$e#..............$2#$b#..............$5#$action AddBuff 13 -2",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.spring_1": "There's a lot of work to be done...sow your seeds...hoe your dirt...chop down trees...#$b#...better do it all...better do it fast...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.summer_1": "This is the best time to get all work done...when noon strikes...go out and work...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.fall_1": "No use in waiting...don't slow down...work...your crops needs to be taken care of...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.winter_1": "Do not approach me. This season is vile.$3#$action AddBuff 14 -2",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.0": "...hoe your dirt..all of it...tear out the pesky weeds...don't stop...#$b#...don't stop...work...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.1": "Work more...the seeds you don't sow today...will be too late tomorrow...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.2": "...no need for a break...continue.#$e#Go work...hours upon hours upon hours...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.3": "Why are you...looking like that?#$b#You're...way too relaxed...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.4": "If you don't want to work...then dance with me...#$b#...dance...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.5": "...a shed full of food...at the very least...then you can rest...#$b#...there's work to be done...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.6": "Dancing...dancing...dancing...#$b#...why won't you dance?",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.7": "%Poludnitsa takes a swing at you with her sickle before stepping away after you managed to dodge.#$b#Hm...lucky one...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.8": "You...haven't done enough...#$b#...it's never enough...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.9": "Look at the sun...bright and warm...#$e#...set ablaze...work...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.10": "I have seen your crops...where is the rye...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.11": "There's work to be done...#$b#...you...why are you not tending your crops?",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.12": "Too much to do...why not skip your break?#$b#You can...still rest later...much later...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.13": "Only a hard worker...is a good worker...#$b#Breaks should be used to dance...so, let's dance...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.14": "So many who do not work...#$b#This island...is too calm...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.15": "Do you...have any children...#$b#...make sure...they don't run around the fields...#$e#..Your children...trample the grain...unacceptable...$3",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.16": "The grain...needs to be processed...what are you waiting for?#$b#I shall take it then...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.17": "Scorching, scorching...scorching...#$b#...let your fields be scorched from the suns heat...#$e#You...do not perturb me...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.18": "Sundays...full of sun...#$b#Do not take it as a day...to rest...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.19": "To have....girls...dance with me...#$b#A delight...let us dance...",
	"LadyMidday.Dialogue.20": "From afar....I see a lot.#$b#Why have you slacked off...and let the crops wither...",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"LadyMidday.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "WORD",
	"LadyMidday.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "WORD",
	"LadyMidday.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Alkonost =================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Are you struggling that much having to resort to such things...poor you.$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Be glad I am not my older sister or else you'd have a bad time right now.$5",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Delightful! I love when nature does it's little abnormal things like this.$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Aw, it's over so quickly...let's hope that the rain will return soon!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "More green rain! It's such a refresher when nature does it's little abnormal things like this.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Introduction": "Hey there! Nice to meet you, I am Alkonost.$1#$b#How is your day? Do you like the island? YOu're not from here, right?",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.spring_1": "Yippie! I love spring!$1#$b#Everything wakes up and it gets so lively!",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.summer_1": "Summer is a lovely season!$1#$b#Will you kick back and enjoy the warm weather or work just as hard?",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.fall_1": "Fall is here and with it the lovely change of leaves!$1#$b#At some point the veil between life and death will also get thinner so be wary of that.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.winter_1": "Winter is when everything dies or sleeps.#$b#It's not my favorite season but I do like the occasional snow.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.0": "I love the little gems Barnabas keeps bringing in.#$b#He just comes to people sometimes and offers a gem without any context.#$b#Naturally, I always accept the shinies, hehe!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.1": "Sirin is sometimes hard to deal with. She doesn't really do the whole 'getting along' thing but she has her reasons.#$b#I however are always happy to talk! So just hit me up if you wanna talk about all kind of things, I will never say no!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.2": "Hm, despite being a bird of bad omens I do enjoy being around people.#$b#I try to not dwell on things and just enjoy the moment.#$b#I know my sisters aren't like that but...well, everyone is their own person. Just because I am cheerful doesn't mean things won't affect me...$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.3": "I do enjoy being all out and about.#$b#Sometimes I visit Gamayun in the library but soon enough get asked to leave because I can't stop talking.#$b#I don't really mind, I mean, I am not out to make anyone have a bad time so I rather leave.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.4": "...when a train passes through the sky and shoots through clouds we will know what the future brings.$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.5": "Hm! Do you think people would like it when they get told their futures?#$b#I mean in an honest, possibly gruesome way.#$b#Never understood the ones that say they brave themself and then attack you when you tell them their future...",
	
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.6": "Oh, I am so excited! I have planned so much for today and hopefully I will get Sirin to help me out as well!#$b#Wish me luck!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.7": "The other day I got some smoked fish from Caitriona and I really liked it.#$b#She put some sorta sauce onto it and it was really good. I ought to ask her for more next time!",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.8": "I went down to the Quarry with Barnabas the other day to look for more shinies.#$b#Look what I found![60 62 64 66 68 70 72 74 80 82 84 86]",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.9": "Do you think I can get Barnabas to make me some jewelry out of the shinies I have? It would be so nice to wear them!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.10": "How are you on this bright and happy day?#$b#I went and gathered some flowers to dry earlier today.#$b#I like to gather a bunch so I can dry and grind them into fine dust for Gamayun!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.11": "I love meeting new people. There's always so much to talk about!#$b#Like, where do you come from? What is the earliest childhood memory you have? Do you ever feel that deep existential crisis where everything you thought mattered actually has no meaning at all and you know you will end up being forgotten?$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.12": "When it comes to cooking I am usually the one doing it.#$b#Both my sisters are rather, uh...let's say they're pretty occupied with their jobs.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.13": "Sometimes I do wonder if I should spread my wings and travel around the world.#$b#I like it too much here though so I never end up leaving, haha!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.14": "I asked Gamayun once if she could bottle up the islands scent for me.#$b#When I said it was to take it with me I just got the reply that I'd never leave the island anyway so where would be the use.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.15": "How is the farm life treating you?#$b#I think by now enough time has passed to properly evaluate your life choices. So...did you make the right choice?$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.16": "A little birdie told me that you play the harp, is that true?#$b#I do play it too!$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.17": "I am not that good with magic.#$b#Well, it's not that I don't have talent for it but...I guess I just lack focus.#$b#I just can't sit still enough.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.18": "Do you want to have a little tea party at some point?#$b#I am trying to find enough to have afternoon tea but most times they're all too busy...$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.19": "Hm...I like a good wine.#$b#Most of all ancient...there has to be enough dust settled on the bottle that you have a coughing fit. Then the age is perfect.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.20": "Sometimes few words spoken are better than many.#$b#..............$2#$b#That doesn't mean that talking a lot is a bad thing though.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.21": "You wanna hang out some time? I know a good spot in the nether realm-#$b#...oops, forget what I said. Gamayun told me to stop mentioning that place to mortals...$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.22": "%Alkonost looks pretty distracted right now, not noticing you.%noturn",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.23": "Hm...ah...$2#%b#...oh?#$b#It's you! Hello there, how's it going?$1",
	
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.24": "Do you ever find yourself wondering what your life would be like if you made different choices?",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.25": "Waking up early is such a waste, but having to actually sleep is also a waste...unless I can't sleep then I want nothing more than to sleep.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.26": "Gamayun tried to explain all the rules of magic to me before but I couldn't listen to it. It was just too much...",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.27": "Oh...I was so distracted with my previous thought I don't even know what to say to you, huh...",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.28": "Barnabas gave me another shiny!$1#$b#My collection is growing and soon it will be very sparkly!",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.29": "I walked down the shore today so I could collect some pearls and sea shells.#$b#The amount of them that you can find here is amazing!#$b#Barnabas has shown me how to get the pretty insides of the shells out without breaking too much of it.$1",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.30": "Ah, what a lovely day!$1#$b#I think I might take a stroll to the beach and lay in the sun.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.31": "Please don't ask me if I'd still like you if you were a worm...#$b#...I am a bird creature...worms are yummy, can you blame me?$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.32": "I have been called soft in the past. They really tried to tell me that would make me weak.#$b#Have they ever met Barnabas? He's the sweetest guy around yet could bite through diamond and any metal one could find.#$b#...not to mention what he does with melons...$2",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.33": "Hm...I don't have any plans for the future.#$b#I just take it one step at a time and spontaneously decide if I wake up at 4am or 3pm.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.34": "Life would be boring if everyone was the same.#$b#How would I be able to keep my shinies safe from others?",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.35": "Sometimes the best thing you can say is nothing at all.#$b#...and sometimes 'nothing' depends on your perspective and can mean a 500 page essay.$1",
	
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Sun.0": "The hangouts are always nice.#$b#Time to catch up and maybe even gossip a little, hehe.#$b#Though the island is so serene and calm I haven't heard much gossip, hm.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Sun.1": "I know our community is rather small compared to most places but that means we are even more tight-knit!#$b#I really look forward to meeting up with everyone today.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Sun.2": "I don't know where they get it from but the others always bring some really good wine to the hangout.#$b#It's usually not ancient but it tastes really nice!",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Sun.3": "I was on BBQ duty before!#$b#In my opinion my cooking is pretty great and I never saw anyone making faces when eating my food so I count it as a win.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Sun.4": "I don't really have any reason not to go to the hangout. I've a fairly flexible schedule and it's a rare time where I get to meet everyone at once.",
	"Alkonost.Dialogue.Sun.5": "Sirin had to wake me up today.#$b#I kind of stayed up all night again, why do I keep doing this?",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Alkonost.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "WORD",
	"Alkonost.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "WORD",
	"Alkonost.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Sirin ====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Sirin.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "..........$2#$b#...It's that bad, huh?$1",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "You really out there thinking you're such an untouchable guy, hm?$5#$action AddBuff 27 -2",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Nature sure is amazing...magic even more so.#$b#'Don't worry, everything will be fine.'$1#$b#...that's something you want me to say, right? Hm. Who knows...maybe you actually should worry.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Ah, there you are. All in one piece. Interesting.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Once again, I am not one you should lean on during this time.#$b#Either way, to me this rain is delightful.$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Introduction": "Interesting....#$b#...you certainly are...coming farther than one would expect.#$b#It does not look like you bow down to fate, hm?$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE 1ST OF SEASON
	"Sirin.Dialogue.spring_1": "The birds and the bees...plants growing, nature waking up...#$b#...this too shall pass. Better make every day count, @.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.summer_1": "You sure are experienced with bringing out the best of %farm. Maybe take a dip in the ocean or something to enjoy life a little while you still can.#$b#You deserve it.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.fall_1": "Hm, my favorite season approaches.#$b#There is just something about this time of the year...",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.winter_1": "Yet again the world dies or goes into slumber.#$b#Yet again soon after it will come back to life or wake up.#$b#What a boringly simple cycle.$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Sirin.Dialogue.0": "Be careful on who to trust.#$b#There's nothing as bittersweet as the moment when someone you care for betrays you because you foolishly trusted them.$1",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.1": "This is the end...#$b#...the end of a peaceful, unbothered day where I was all alone relaxing.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.2": "The way the world is set up is weird, complex and if you ask me quite unfair.#$b#People try to make the best out of things but I just see all the misery and destruction that will be caused.#$b#It leaves quite a bitter taste in one's mouth.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.3": "Have you ever thought about dropping off the face of the earth?#$b#I can help you with that.#$b#Because right now your impending doom-...$1#$b#you know what? never mind.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.4": "Those who deliver prophecies are most often misunderstood and mischaracterized.#$b#Often seen as taking joy in others misfortune and such...#$b#...Schadenfreude might be a prominent thing but I'd never take joy in truly hideous fates.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.5": "Lord Barnabas approached me the other day...#$b#...he said something about needing some help and while I wondered why he did not ask any of my sisters I obliged.#$b#He has such a radiant approach how could I say no?$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.6": "Ever got stuck in a perpetual cycle of remembering the worst moments of your life?#$b#Interesting...$1#$b#...couldn't be me.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.7": "Would you look at the time? I think it's totally time for me to go to a very specific and not made-up appointment I really have to go to.#$b#...seriously tho, I wish it was made up then I could at least just disappear.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.8": "I see you've been running around the island for quite a bit already.#$b#Enjoying what you see? Lord Barnabas tries hard to make this a great place, so appreciate it.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.9": "%Sirin ignores you as she passes by. Doesn't look like she is interested in any conversation right now.%noturn",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.10": "Maybe I should try to be a bit more like my sister in being approachable.#$b#Then again I love my sanity...$1",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.11": "I really thought for a moment to ignore you but I guess doing that too often would make me look like an asshole.#$b#...I'm just not interested in watching train wrecks that are about to happen.#$b#At least not bad ones.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.12": "Middle of the week means it's half over. Middle of the week means you still have half of it left.#$b#Always seeing the middle ground in things is boring, average and plain.#$b#It's just not enough. It's never enough.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.13": "When you get to see what will happen to a person all the joy of wanting to spend time with them gets sucked out.#$b#I often get called a loner because I do not like engaging in what will be lost anyway.#$b#Once you see it happen often enough, when you try changing it too many times you will get to understand why it's better to not feel at all than to get your heart broken over and over.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.14": "%Sirin shoots you a glance and then walks past you, not interested in small talk.%noturn",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.15": "I've had a vision earlier today so I am not really up for some talk, @.#$b#No, I won't share what it was about.$1",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.16": "The smell of dirt and hard work...good job.#$b#Is your life full-filling compared to your previous one?",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.17": "The void beckons...but I always ignore it.#$b#Not my job. At least not for another millinia.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.18": "%Sirin looks at you for a moment, though does not speak. She decides to continue on with her day in silence.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.19": "I've seen many fates and seen countless lives played out...#$b#...it's too hard to bear for most. I won't lie and say that I remain unaffected.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.20": "He may not be convinced himself but Lord Barnabas is quite a lot like his father.#$b#It's natural to think that the big hole left by your parent is something you cannot fill, but he will surely learn to accept that he is indeed enough.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.21": "Apologies, @, but I do not feel like talking today. You can go and talk to Alkonost instead, she always loves to ramble.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.22": "Gamayun is always so busy with the library.#$b#Always been like, sigh.$1#$b#%Sirin looks away from you, not elaborating further.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.23": "As any respectable bird-aligned being I do appreciate a nice amount of shinies. I won't deny that.#$b#How can you NOT like shinies?",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.24": "%Sirin stares up into the sky, only after a moment finally turning to you.#$b#Hm? Oh...#$b#...@, you ever felt like not being in your own body? Like you stand beside yourself?",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.25": "You got me there. No quirky comment or snide remark to offer today.#$b#I am quite-...hm...$1#$b#...I guess nostalgic.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.26": "The calm and peaceful vibe os this island is sometimes misleading.#$b#Maybe not for most, maybe not for this moment in time but...#$b#...well, there's danger up ahead. There has been danger in the past. With a heavy price paid....I do not want to imagine the next price.$1",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.27": "I do have a long chat with the merchant when they are located at Point Melodia.#$b#Hm, they say many cryptid things and are a rather odd individual but...they do have something that draws one in. I admit that.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.28": "%Sirin gives a long sigh when she walks past you, not shooting you any glance.%noturn",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.29": "Would you like a peek into your future?#$b#Hm, people always agree way too easily stating they can bear the heavy burden even if their future is bleak.#$b#I do not believe there is anyone out there quite understanding this question to begin with.$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.30": "The week is almost over, yet it all feels the same to me.#$b#It's an endlessly repeating cycle in one way or another.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.31": "%Sirin stares at you for a moment, then turns around and leaves.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.32": "The deeper you go into a rabbit hole the lesser your chance to get out of it.#$b#'Information' can be as much of a curse as anything else, you know?#$b#The curse to remember something, to have partaken in something, to 'be' something...$3",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.33": "Hm, the day sure has been...perceived in one way or another.#$b#......$3#$b#...yeah, I don't really feel like talking, how did you figurethat out?",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.34": "Been busy lately? Surely farm life is keeping one quite occupied.#$b#Unless you're like Lord Barnabas who has a seemingly endless fountain of strength and endurance.$1",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.35": "...I lack a good conversation topic today, apologies.#$b#It has been quite uneventful with no sort of premonition or anything so I just took the chance to do nothing all day.",
	
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Yes, I do partake in the hangout today.#$b#I may be a loner but I am not a hermit.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Sun.1": "I may be less approachable than my sisters but I do talk to others.#$b#Case in point, this conversation right now.#$b#Either way, wanna hang out today at the cliff?",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Sun.2": "%Sirin either ignores you or does not notice you. Either way she stares into the sky in silence before carrying on with her day.%noturn",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Hm...I guess hanging around people sometimes is not too bad.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Sun.4": "I was asked to bring something to the hangout.#$b#Not really sure what so I left it to my sister.",
	"Sirin.Dialogue.Sun.5": "I am not doing any readings for 'how will next week be for me'. I keep getting asked about those.#$b#...this is not by choice. I am forced to have these visions...$3",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Sirin.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "WORD",
	"Sirin.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "WORD",
	"Sirin.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Bubblegum =====================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "Fun can! You got something cool?",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Ouch!....why hurt friend...$2",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Yum! Green rain tastes funny!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Aw...it's over...#$b#Me wanted more...",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Me like! Yummy rain!$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Introduction": "Bubblegum! That is me!$3#$b#Hello, friend!$1",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.0": "Me thinks to go to plant friends today.#$b#Bubblegum is happy with plant friends!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.1": "Papa always brings me delicious food. Yummy!#$b#It's lotsa different things!$1",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.2": "Me loves Papa! Papa has serious face, but also very lovely!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.3": "Papa! Papa!$3#$b#Oh, where did Papa go? Bubblegum will find Papa!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.4": "@, friend!$3#$b#Bubblegum rolled around is grass all day!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.5": "Bubblegum tried books before. Me thinks it's too hard with no arms...",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.6": "You like dance? Bubblegum dances a lot!#$b#Papa showed me how to dance!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.7": "Papa looks stern but is really nice.#$b#Papa always holds Bubblegum!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.8": "Me played hide and seek with Papa once.#$b#Me hid so well, Papa said we won't play anymore. Papa was too scared.",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.9": "%Bubblegum hops around happily, humming loudly.%noturn",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.10": "Friend!$3#$b#You having fun today? Anything happening?",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.11": "Me got some funny new things from Papa!#$b#Me likes playing with my toys!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.12": "%Bubblegum hops around in a circle, turning upside down in the process.#$b#Me bouncing! Look, friend!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.13": "Yippie! Yippie!!!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.14": "Papa allowed me to drink coke and play with the ferrets! Yippie!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.15": "Hello, friend! Bubblegum loves you! Happy, happy!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.16": "%Bubblegum tries really hard to whistle but nothing happens.%noturn",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.17": "Me no like fire...got burnt once.#$b#Papa did his best to fix, me love Papa!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.18": "Love cheese. Love cheese a lot! Yummy cheese!#$b#%Bubblegum hops around happily.",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.19": "You come here often? Me like when you're here.#$b#Papa said new people around is a good thing!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.20": "Bubblegum went around the island! Found a lot of things!#$b#Here! Have this! [MossySeed]",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.21": "Me ate ore before. Not that yummy.#$b#King Banana..King Bandana...King likes it though!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.22": "Happy day! Bubblegum got extra food!#$b#Yippie!!!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.23": "Me love them ferrets!#$b#Fun to play with!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.24": "Merchants that come once a month are fun!#$b#Bubblegum always gets treats from merchant!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.25": "Me thinks that Papa works too much.#$b#Stay more home, me wants to cuddle.",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.26": "Me no talk with other slimes.#$b#Most are mean, me just wants to make friends.",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.27": "Me no have slime family.#$b#Papa got me as egg, Papa is my Papa!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.28": "Friend! @!#$b#Me found this![386 446 797 848 909]",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.29": "Everyone loves Fridays.#$b#Me likes every day. Me gets to do lots of fun things!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.30": "Not much to do today. Me bored.#$b#You anything fun to do?",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.31": "%Bubblegum wobbles around without any thoughts in her head.%noturn",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.32": "All work and no play makes Bubblegum a dull girl.$2",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.33": "Me tried fishing again.#$b#Not much fun, no arms make Bubblegum bad with fishing.#$b#But Papa got me fish! Made fillet! Yummy!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.34": "So tired...maybe sleep all day, hmhmhm...",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.35": "Do you have a sword?#$b#Is it poke-y?",
	
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Slept a lot today! Now me wanna play a lot but Papa is busy...",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Sun.1": "%Bubblegum tries to put pebbles all around the ground in a specific pattern.%noturn",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Hangouts are fun! Bubblegum always gets lots of food!$3",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Sun.3": "Me have fun today. Lotta people come to cliff and talk!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Sun.4": "Make sure to visit cliff! Maybe friend will get free food too like Bubblegum!",
	"Bubblegum.Dialogue.Sun.5": "Me no sleep today. Very tired, but kept thinking about food...",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Bubblegum.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "WORD",
	"Bubblegum.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "WORD",
	"Bubblegum.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "WORD",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//=== Armand ===================================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	// GENERAL
	"Armand.Dialogue.DumpsterDiveComment": "You're all about recycling and reuse, eh?",
	"Armand.Dialogue.HitBySlingshot": "Ah...I know your kind, bud. Lemme just hit you back and we call it even, eh?$5",
	"Armand.Dialogue.GreenRain": "Ever cooked with water like this?#$b#This tea's getting real funky...hm$2#$b#%Armand laughs and chugs down his mug of tea either way.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.GreenRainFinished": "Dang, already finished, huh?#$b#I found it quite funny seeing ol' Berns hair change to green during the rain.#$b#You think I should try out green hair as well?$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.GreenRain2": "Hm, 'green rain' doesn't roll off the tongue just like 'purple rain' does...#$b#...any chance you know some wizard that can make it rain purple?$1",
	
	// DIALOGUE EXTRA
	"Armand.Dialogue.Introduction": "Yo! Armands the name, nice to meet'cha!#$b#I'm the old man of Bern, the one with the pink hair.",
	
	//DIALOGUE 
	
	"Armand.Dialogue.0": "I'm here to meet my daughter, Bernadette.#$b#She's quite the wild child and I love her to bits.#$b#You met her? Great! Then I don't need to say no more, Hahaha!$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.1": "You ever feel like...#$b#%Armand shreds it heavily on an air guitar.#$b#Y'know?#$b#Oh, sorry, Hah! I was visiting Bern' earlier and maybe we jammed out too hard cuz right now my minds all over the place.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.2": "Hm, what a great place...#$b#I can get why Bern' decided to live here. Never knew my heart could smile like that.$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.3": "I hope your day is as nice as your smile.$1#$b#My day surely is delightful, I cannot complain.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.4": "Someone once said 'Love is when you meet someone who tells you something new about yourself.' and I think that's very true.#$b#I've loved in many ways and found many people who taught me more about myself...#$b#...I am always open to more insight though, keep it coming, Haha!$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.5": "%Armand hums some lyrics to himself, deeply in thoughts.%noturn'#$b#Hm? Oh! Didn't notice you there!$1#$b#I was thinking about a few more lines to my latest song that I am working on.#$b#'When you're lonely in the dark of the night...'...hm...well, either way!#$b#'A cascade of many eyes' is the name, thought it's just a working title, maybe.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.6": "For all the things my hands have held, the best by far was Bern'.#$b#It might sound a little sappy but having a lil kid of your own just does something to you, I think.$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.7": "Just like the sunshine makes the flower grow, gaze into the stars and sit together down below...#$b#Hm...$7#$b#...ah, whats up, bud? I'm just out here thinking bout some lyrics.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.8": "Sometimes all the things I want to say can find no voice...then I just sit outside and stare at the night sky.#$b#Do you ever get like that?$7#$b#Times like these I tend to write. Not songs or anything, just words that pour out of my heart and bleed onto the paper. Ramblings, wild words...maybe even something that makes sense sometimes.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.9": "Man, this island is such a vibe. Makes me want to strip off my clothes and swim a few rounds...#$b#Hm? Oh, don't worry, I know how to control myself.#$b#Well, most of the time.$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.10": "Bern' is such a sweet child. Any time I see her something wells up in my chest...I just know we did everything right with raising her.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.11": "I don’t need a hairstylist. My pillow is doing a good job styling it for me, Haha!#$b#Just kidding! I just throw it around myself and lop it off whenever I feel like it.$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.12": "Yo, how's it hangin'?#$b#Met up with Bern' earlier and we're gonna go on a lil trip later. What's your Friday plans?",
	"Armand.Dialogue.13": "Been into traveling around for quite a long time already.#$b#I love meeting new people and making new connections.#$b#Funnily enough fans always seem to find me, Hah!$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.14": "I've been getting along well with the other people on the island.#$b#That Barnabas guy really knows quite a lot about everything. Bern' said he's kind of a big deal here, but he seems down to earth to me.#$b#He said he'd show me a few great spots later.$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.15": "I originally wanted to name my kid something like 'Hendrixx', 'Diesel', 'Scourge' or, y'know, 'Hellslinger Riot'...#$b#...but her mother was against it. Saying something bout the hospital not accepting that as names, what a pity.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.16": "I've had a pet in the past, really loved her to bits. A cat by the name of 'Anthrax'.#$b#She was always chillin' on my shoulder when I was walking around.$1#$b#Maybe I'll get another pet at some point, hm...",
	"Armand.Dialogue.17": "Oi, ain't it a great day to stride around? Suns out and the sands warm...$1#$b#...might even check out that library at the cliff later.",
	
	"Armand.Dialogue.Sun.0": "Heard there's a gathering on Sundays. Been eager to check it out for a while.",
	"Armand.Dialogue.Sun.1": "Bern' said to come by later at the cliff so I'm gonna prep my guitar to play a few tunes.$1",
	"Armand.Dialogue.Sun.2": "Been seeing you here a lot. It's a lovely island ain't it?$1#$b#It's always fun seeing you run around, @.",
	
	// SCHEDULE DIALOGUE
	"Armand.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.000": "Yo @! How's it groovin'?$6#$b#I just took a little walk and felt inspired by the nature here so I decided to play some chords.$6#$b#What do ya think, eh?$8",
	"Armand.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.001": "Ah, what lovely place to hang out at!$1#$b#Sometimes you just wanna hang around and chill a bit.#$b#Doing absolutely nothin' is totally radical too sometimes.",
	"Armand.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.002": "Dude, this painting is rad. You can feel each brush stroke...#$b#...it's like the person in the painting is actually alive.",
	"Armand.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.003": "Hm...I know some art comforts the disturbed and disturbs the comfortable...#$b#...I think this is such case, don't you think?",
	"Armand.Schedule.Dialogue.lostisland.004": "Yo, my friend!$1#$b#Bern asked me if I wanna hang out with the others today and I thought why not?$1#$b#Everyone seems pretty chill, it's really nice, hah.$1",
	
	//==============================================================================================
	//==== A N T I S O C I A L S ===================================================================
	//==============================================================================================
	
	"Ferret.Sound.Squeak1": "Squeak!",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.0": "%The salty scent of the oceans hits your nose. Algaelica seems to give you a nod.",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.1": "%The sun reflects on Algaeica's wet self.",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.2": "%It's unclear if Algaelica is looking at you or somewhere else.",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.3": "...greetings, farmer friend. Have you had enough water to drink?",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.4": "Lord Barnabas is making sure everything is in order. He is a very kind being.#$b#I hope you can see his value too.",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.5": "I like soggy spots and damp corner...#$b#...how is your basement faring?",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.6": "......soup?#$b#I have heard some do eat that...with algae. Very strange...",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.7": "Hm...do you have some salt on you?#$b#I'd like to season my water.",
	"Plant.Algealica.Dialog.8": "%There is a moment of hesitation as Algaelica looks at you, but she ultimately turns around and leaves.",
	
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.0": "%The scent of summer and floral fragrance...",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.1": "%Watching Sunny for a while reveals her often moving her head towards where the sun is going...",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.2": "%You are given some sunflower seeds to sow. Sunny eagerly watches you.",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.3": "I love this island, it has a lot of sunny days.#$b#Algaelica might like dark and damp spaces but I prefer the sun.",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.4": "Would you like to sow some flowers?#$b#There is a chance one like us might grow.",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.5": "%Sunny waves you over and eagerly shakes your hand.",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.6": "I heard your farm is called %farm.#$b#Do you grow flowers there?",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.7": "The lord of these lands is quite kind and benevolent.#$b#We had nothing, yet he gave us time and a place to stay.",
	"Plant.Sunny.Dialog.8": "....oh...I thought you were beaming like the sun. So radiant...",
	
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.0": "%Fern waves at you. There seems to be a soft hum coming from her.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.1": "%Her delicate leaves move in the soft wind...an herbal scent is coming towards you.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.2": "%Fern gives a nod, handing you a gardening tool to help take care of the orchard.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.3": "Do you know of special rainy days?#$b#Sometimes on those days I grow quite big...not sure why.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.4": "I like to watch Hemlock frolic around when Barnabas gives him attention.#$b#He always states that they are rivals but I think he actually sees Barnabas as his best friend.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.5": "Hm...how are you doing, @?#$b#I hope this day, too, will bring you a lot of interesting moments.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.6": "%Fern is handling some small tools to take care of some weeds.",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.7": "...ah, apologies. I am a bit distracted.#$b#Barnabas was talking about something in the water, I was quite curious but water isn't really my element.#$b#I am so light I just float on top sadly...",
	"Plant.Fern.Dialog.8": "Do you think something exciting will happen on this island?",
	
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.0": "%You try to look at her face or...where you think it is.",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.1": "%You observe Violetta sow some seeds around. Looks like she wants to help Barnabas.",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.2": "%A sweet floral scent hits your nose as you come closer.",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.3": "Barnabas and Hemlock are quite close...I'd love to have someone like that too, one day...",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.4": "You are a farmer, right? Do you know much about flowers?",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.5": "%Violetta dances around as she sows more seeds, you are hit by some of them.",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.6": "Do you want to help sowing seeds? Barnabas said it's a good deed!#$b#Keeping the island alive and pure.",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.7": "Don't ask me how old I am, I don't know.#$b#I think Barnabas keeps track of these kind of things. I wonder why...",
	"Plant.Violetta.Dialog.8": "Sometimes Barnabas looks quite sad. He writes down a lot of things then.",
	
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.0": "%Teana waves excitingly at you.",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.1": "%Teana twirls around in her little dress as she sows more seeds.",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.2": "%As you bump into her she loses some seeds she had been carrying around.",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.3": "Would you like some tea? The others say I can brew a quite good one.",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.4": "How is it like being you? I like being me.#$b#Not everyone likes being themself, why?",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.5": "I see some dance in the forest sometimes.#$b#Do you think I can dance with them?",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.6": "Lord Barnabas is really cool. He does so many things and swims so much.#$b#Does he ever get tired?",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.7": "What is your favorite thing? It tells a lot about your character, you know?#$b#%favorite? That's it, huh...interesting.",
	"Plant.Teana.Dialog.8": "%Teana is unmoving like a regular bush. That is until you got closer...she quickly turns towards you and waves excitingly.",
	
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.0": "%There's a name stitched onto the shirt: Roseanne. A peculiar name.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.1": "%You get hit by some seeds as you look at her. Roseanne quickly hops away.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.2": "%Roseanne observed some bugs on the ground. She points at them when she notices you.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.3": "%Unlike the others, Roseanne does not seem to be very talkative. She happily points out random things to you though.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.4": "...@.#$b#%She quickly turns away after saying your name, focusing on some bugs on the ground.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.5": "%As you approach her she hands you some seeds and threw the rest all around on the ground.#%b#...sow, yes?",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.6": "..............#$b#%She tugs at your sleeve, pointing over to a butterfly.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.7": "I like...bugs...#$b#%As quickly as she seemed more approachable she reverts back to her silent self, showing off a stag beetle.",
	"Plant.Roseanne.Dialog.8": "There are several bugs crawling around on her clothes, they seem pretty chill.",
}